msgstr "你把西方的洞穴裡那隻大老鼠殺掉了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_crossglen_odair.json:odair_continue:0
msgid "Yes, I have killed the large rat."
msgstr "是的，我已經宰了那隻大老鼠。"

