#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_10:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_10:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_10:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_10:1
msgid "The scroll of water"
msgstr "水之卷軸"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_10:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_10:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_10:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_10:2
msgid "The scroll of earth"
msgstr "大地卷軸"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_10:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_10:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_10:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_10:3
msgid "The scroll of wind"
msgstr "風之卷軸"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_10:4
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_10:4
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_10:4
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_10:4
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave2_k1_10:1
msgid "None"
msgstr "無"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_20
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_20
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_20
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_20
msgid "The scroll still lies on the table."
msgstr "卷軸仍然放在桌上。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_20:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_20:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_20:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_20:0
msgid "I take back my scroll of fire."
msgstr "我收回我的火焰卷軸。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_20:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_20:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_20:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_20:1
msgid "I take back my scroll of water."
msgstr "我收回我的水之卷軸。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_20:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_20:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_20:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_20:2
msgid "I take back my scroll of earth."
msgstr "我收回我的大地卷軸。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_20:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_20:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_20:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_20:3
msgid "I take back my scroll of wind."
msgstr "我收回我的風之卷軸。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k1_20:4
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_20:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k3_20:4
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_20:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k5_20:4
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_20:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k7_20:4
msgid "I let it be."
msgstr "我任由它去。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_10
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_10
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_10
msgid "What do you want to put here?"
msgstr "你想放什麼在這裡？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_10:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_10:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_10:0
msgid "The red globe"
msgstr "紅色球體"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_10:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_10:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_10:1
msgid "The green globe"
msgstr "綠色球體"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_10:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_10:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_10:2
msgid "The blue globe"
msgstr "藍色球體"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_10:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_10:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_10:3
msgid "Nothing"
msgstr "無物"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_20
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_20
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_20
msgid "The globe still hovers over the table."
msgstr "地球儀仍懸浮在桌上。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_20:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_20:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_20:0
msgid "I take back my red globe."
msgstr "我收回我的紅色球體。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_20:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_20:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_20:1
msgid "I take back my green globe."
msgstr "我收回我的綠色球體。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k2_20:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k4_20:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_k6_20:2
msgid "I take back my blue globe."
msgstr "我收回我的藍色球體。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_kx_open
msgid "A loud rumbling fills the air!"
msgstr "空氣中傳來一陣巨響！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_kx_close
msgid ""
"You hear a low but intense noise.\n"
"What is happening now?"
msgstr ""
"你聽到低沉而強烈的聲響。\n"
"現在發生了什麼？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_kx_hint1
msgid "Maybe I have to find out the correct order?"
msgstr "也許我得找出正確的順序？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_kx_hint1_2
msgid "I wish there would be a placement order map somewhere here."
msgstr "真希望這裡有個排列順序圖。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_kx_hint2
msgid "I am sure there is a placement order map somewhere here."
msgstr "我確信這裡某處有一張排列順序圖。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_kx_hint3
msgid "I even think I have already seen that order map down here."
msgstr "我甚至覺得我已經在這裡看到過那張命令地圖。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:island_4_cave1_key
msgid "You feel somebody staring at your back."
msgstr "你感覺有人在盯著你的背後看。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_jhaeld1
msgid "$playername - good that you are here! I need your help urgently."
msgstr "$playername - 很高興你來了！我急需你的幫助。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1:0
msgid "Why? Do you have a little problem in your basement again?"
msgstr "為什麼？你地下室又出點小問題了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_10
msgid "Iiiek! Don't remind me!"
msgstr "哎呀！別提醒我！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_10:0
msgid "So how can I help you?"
msgstr "那我能怎麼幫你？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_20
msgid "A friend of mine is captured, here, deep in the cave."
msgstr "我的一位朋友被困在這裡，洞穴深處。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_22
msgid "You know him very well by the way. We have to help him!"
msgstr "你其實很了解他。我們必須幫助他！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_22:0
msgid "Of course I'm happy to help."
msgstr "當然，我很樂意幫忙。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_22:1
msgid "Who is this friend?"
msgstr "這位朋友是誰？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_30
msgid "To free him I would need to go for some items all over the isle. But these nasty centaurs wouldn't let me."
msgstr "要救他，我得去島上各處找些物品。但那些討厭的半人馬不讓我過。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_30:0
msgid "Well, first I am going downstairs to talk to our friend and find out who he is."
msgstr "嗯，我先下樓去跟我們的朋友談談，看看他是誰。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror1_40
msgid "Do that. But hurry."
msgstr "照做。但要快。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_jhaeld1:0
msgid "Why? Don't coming around on your own anymore?"
msgstr "為什麼？你不再自己過來了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2
msgid "$playername, what have you done?"
msgstr "$playername，你做了什麼？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_10
msgid "Now we are all locked in here! We will all starve to death!"
msgstr "現在我們全都被困在這裡了！我們都會餓死的！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_20
msgid "It is all your fault!"
msgstr "這全都是你的錯！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_20:0
msgid "Hey - I did nothing!"
msgstr "嘿——我什麼都沒做！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_30
msgid "Our only chance of survival lies in that stairway over there."
msgstr "我們唯一的生存機會就在那邊的樓梯。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_30:0
msgid "What is down there?"
msgstr "下面是什麼？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_30:1
msgid "You didn't try it yourself yet?"
msgstr "你自己還沒試過嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_30:2
msgid "Why did all that gold disappear for a few moments?"
msgstr "為什麼那些黃金會消失幾秒鐘？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_32
msgid "Did it? You must have dreamed that."
msgstr "真的嗎？你一定是做夢了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_32:1
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_42:0
msgid "Hmm ..."
msgstr "嗯…"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_50
msgid "We can't use those stairs. Some invisible force holds us back. But maybe you can do it?"
msgstr "我們無法使用那階梯。有股無形的力量阻擋著我們。但也許你能做到？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_50:0
msgid "OK you weaklings - I'll show you."
msgstr "好吧，你們這些弱者——我來教訓你們。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror2_50:1
msgid "Well, I could at least try."
msgstr "嗯，我至少可以試試看。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_10
msgid "Surprised to see me here?"
msgstr "沒想到在這裡見到我？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_12
msgid "You should see your face! Hahaha!"
msgstr "你應該看看你的臉！哈哈哈！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_20
msgid ""
"Of course we are not what you think you see. Ever heard of posers?\n"
"You were great, that was really fun."
msgstr ""
"當然，我們並非你所見的那般。聽過冒牌貨嗎？\n"
"你表現得很棒，真的很有趣。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_22
msgid "Even the many gold is all fake. We had a lot of fun decorating this ugly room as a treasure trove."
msgstr "即使這麼多金幣全是假貨，我們還是很享受把這醜陋的房間裝飾成寶藏庫的樂趣。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_24
msgid "Making rocks look like piles of gold and stuff like that."
msgstr "讓石頭看起來像一堆金子之類的東西。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_24:0
msgid "And the walls? The element scrolls and the globes?"
msgstr "牆壁呢？元素卷軸和魔法球呢？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_26
msgid "The point of all this was just to lure you down here to our master Dorhantarh without you becoming suspicious."
msgstr "這一切的目的只是為了引你到我們的主人多漢塔爾這裡，而不讓你起疑心。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_28
msgid "So it couldn't be too easy for you. That's why I came up with the idea of the scrolls and glass balls."
msgstr "所以不能讓你太輕鬆。這就是我想出卷軸和玻璃球的原因。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_28:0
msgid "Does that mean this complex mechanism doesn't work at all?"
msgstr "那是不是代表這個複雜機關根本無法運作？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_30
msgid "Oh yes, of course it works. Why do you think the wall closed again?"
msgstr "喔，當然有效。你以為牆壁為什麼會再度關閉？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_30:0
msgid "Yes, why did it?"
msgstr "是的，為什麼會這樣？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_32
msgid "Well, because I brought a scroll from the table here with me. That's why."
msgstr "嗯，因為我帶了桌上的卷軸來。就是這樣。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_32:0
msgid "What?! You ..."
msgstr "什麼？！你…"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_34
msgid "Hahaha!"
msgstr "哈哈哈！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_40
msgid "Now go ahead, you'll be a tasty dinner for our master Dorhantarh tonight."
msgstr "現在去吧，今晚你將成為我們主人多蘭塔爾的美味晚餐。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_42
msgid "You're so speechless. Hahaha! Go now."
msgstr "你啞口無言了。哈哈哈！現在走吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_42:0
msgid "Well wait - attack!"
msgstr "等等——攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_50
msgid "No no no. It is not proper to draw a weapon in the presence of our Master."
msgstr "不不不。在師父面前拔刀是不禮貌的。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_100
msgid "NO! What have you done to our master?!"
msgstr "不！你對我們的主人做了什麼？！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_algangror3_100:0
msgid "The same that I'll do to you now."
msgstr "現在我也會對你做同樣的事。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_2
msgid "Are you trying to get out of the affair by faking death? Shame on you!"
msgstr "你想藉假死逃避這場風波？真可恥！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_10
msgid "Who is there? Declare yourself!"
msgstr "誰在那裡？表明身分！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_10:0
msgid "I know that voice ... Andor, is it really you?"
msgstr "我聽到那聲音了……安多爾，真的是你嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_10:1
msgid "Calm down, Andor. It's me."
msgstr "冷靜點，安多爾。是我。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_30
msgid "At last, $playername. What kept you so long?"
msgstr "終於等到你了，$playername。你怎麼這麼久才來？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_30:0
msgid "What?! "
msgstr "什麼？！ "

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_40
msgid "OK. We have no time for that. Let's come to business."
msgstr "好。沒時間浪費了，開始正事吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_42
msgid "I entered this room to find a powerful weapon against the enemy, when suddenly the walls closed around me."
msgstr "我進入這個房間尋找對抗敵人的強力武器，卻突然被牆壁包圍。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_42:0
msgid "Too curious again?"
msgstr "又太好奇了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_44
msgid "Oh, shut up."
msgstr "喂，閉嘴。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_44:0
msgid "Who is locked up here - you or me?"
msgstr "這裡被關的是你還是我？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_50
msgid "Sigh. Open the wall and come here."
msgstr "嘆。打開牆壁過來。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_50:0
msgid "How can I do this? The walls look rather massive."
msgstr "我該怎麼做？這些牆看起來相當厚重。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_52
msgid "It's very easy."
msgstr "這很簡單。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_52:0
msgid "Oh dear. You always said that when things got tricky."
msgstr "哎呀。你總是在遇到麻煩時這麼說。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_54
msgid "You just have to find the elemental scrolls and the colored globes. Somebody must have taken them and hidden them all over the island."
msgstr "你只需要找到元素卷軸和彩色球體。一定有人把它們拿走，藏在島上的各處。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_54:0
msgid "Can you be a little more specific?"
msgstr "你能說得更具體一點嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_60
msgid "There are four scrolls and three globes. Get them here and place them around this room."
msgstr "這裡有四卷卷軸和三個球體。拿取它們並放置在這個房間裡。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_60:0
msgid "Around this room?"
msgstr "這個房間周圍？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_62
msgid "Of course around this room. Don't always be so stupid."
msgstr "當然是在這個房間裡。別總是這麼笨。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_70
msgid "Hurry now!"
msgstr "快點！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor1_72
msgid "And bring something to eat!"
msgstr "還要帶點吃的！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave_kd
msgid "Hey, don't run away. Talk to us!"
msgstr "嘿，別跑。跟我們說話！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave2_k
msgid "Did someone follow me? I thought they couldn't go down here?"
msgstr "有人跟蹤我嗎？我以為他們不能下來這裡？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_andor3
msgid "You really believed I was your brother? Hahaha!"
msgstr "你真的相信我是你兄弟？哈哈哈！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:final_cave2_k1_10_f
msgid "A loud rumbling fills the air! - At the same time the scroll of fire explodes."
msgstr "空氣中傳來一陣巨響！——同時火焰卷軸爆炸。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_plant
msgid "Crap, the plant didn't grow tall enough."
msgstr "糟糕，植物長得不夠高。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_fc1_key
msgid "You see nothing special."
msgstr "你什麼也沒看到。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_fc2_s1_6
msgid "You hear a loud rumbling from above. Seems to be the walls are opened up again."
msgstr "你聽到上方傳來巨響。看來牆壁又被打開了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_fc2_s1_10
msgid "You call back upstairs that there was no problem going down."
msgstr "你從樓上喊回來說下樓沒問題。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_fc2_s1_12
msgid "But something is very wrong here."
msgstr "但這裡有些非常不對勁。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_island_boss
msgid "Ah, my dinner at last."
msgstr "啊，終於吃晚餐了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_island_boss_10
msgid "And no horse meat this time. My servants promised me a delicious surprise tonight."
msgstr "這次沒有馬肉。我的僕人們答應我今晚有美味的驚喜。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_island_boss_10:0
msgid "We'll see. Attack!"
msgstr "我們拭目以待。攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur_10
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_20
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_20
msgid "You are not wanted here."
msgstr "你在此不受歡迎。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur_20
msgid "We have an eye on you."
msgstr "我們盯著你。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_1
msgid "You there, human."
msgstr "你那邊的人類。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_2
msgid "Our leader wants to see you. Now."
msgstr "我們的首領現在要見你。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_2:1
msgid "Who is your leader?"
msgstr "你的領袖是誰？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_3
msgid "Don't ask questions. Just do as you're told."
msgstr "別問問題，照指示做就對了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_3:0
msgid "Fine. Lead the way."
msgstr "好。帶路吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_3:1
msgid "And if I refuse?"
msgstr "如果我拒絕呢？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_4
msgid "Then you'll regret it. Trust me, you don't want to anger our leader."
msgstr "那你會後悔的。相信我，你不想惹怒我們的首領。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_4:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_5:1
msgid "It's okay, calm down. Where is this leader?"
msgstr "沒關係，冷靜點。這位首領在哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_5
msgid "I have better things to do than play tour guide to useless intruders."
msgstr "我有更重要的事要做，不想當沒用入侵者的導遊。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_5:0
msgid "Then just tell me where he is."
msgstr "那就告訴我他在哪裡。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_8
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_8
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_8
msgid "Thalos, our wise guide, is currently in the northeast of the island."
msgstr "薩洛斯，我們的智慧嚮導，目前在島嶼的東北方。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_8:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_5:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_8:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_8:0
msgid "Fine, I'll go see him."
msgstr "好吧，我去見他。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_8:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_8:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_8:1
msgid "Hopefully this Thalos will be a little more accommodating."
msgstr "希望這次薩洛斯能更通融一點。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur1_10
msgid "Hurry up now. And don't try anything stupid."
msgstr "快點。別做傻事。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_1
msgid "What brings a human like you to our island?"
msgstr "像你這樣的人類，來我們島上有何貴幹？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_1:0
msgid "Just passing through. No need to get defensive."
msgstr "只是路過，別太防備。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_2
msgid "Defensive? Ha! We have every right to be wary of your kind. Humans have brought nothing but trouble to our land."
msgstr "防禦？哈！我們完全有理由對你們這種人保持警惕。人類只給我們的土地帶來麻煩。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_2:0
msgid "I'm not here to cause trouble."
msgstr "我不是來找麻煩的。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_2:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_2:1
msgid "I'm just looking for..."
msgstr "我只是想找..."

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_3
msgid "That's what they all say. But mark my words, human, if you step out of line, you'll regret it."
msgstr "他們都這麼說。但記住我的話，人類，若你越界，必將後悔。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_3:0
msgid "I assure you, I have no intentions of causing any harm."
msgstr "我向你保證，我無意造成任何傷害。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_4
msgid "We'll see about that. Just remember, you're not welcome here."
msgstr "我們拭目以待。記住，你在這裡不受歡迎。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_5
msgid "We will have to decide what happens to you. You must therefore go to our leader now."
msgstr "我們必須決定你的命運。你現在必須去見我們的首領。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur2_10
msgid "Don't think about trying anything funny. We'll be watching you."
msgstr "別想耍什麼花招。我們會盯著你的。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_1
msgid "What do you want, human?"
msgstr "你想要什麼，人類？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_1:0
msgid "Just passing through. No need to be hostile."
msgstr "只是路過，無需敵對。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_2
msgid "We don't take kindly to your kind here. You humans always cause trouble."
msgstr "我們這裡可不歡迎你們這種人。你們人類總是惹麻煩。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_2:0
msgid "I'm not looking for trouble. Just trying to explore."
msgstr "我不想惹麻煩。只是想探索。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_3
msgid "Well, you're not welcome here. Keep moving before you cause any problems."
msgstr "嗯，你在這裡不受歡迎。快走，別惹麻煩。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_3:0
msgid "I don't mean any harm. Can't we just talk?"
msgstr "我無意傷害。能不能先談談？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_4
msgid "Talking won't change anything. You humans are all the same. You should have just left us alone."
msgstr "說再多也沒用。你們人類都一樣。你們本該直接放過我們。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_4:0
msgid "Fine. I'll go. But I won't forget how unwelcoming you've been."
msgstr "好吧。我會去。但我不會忘記你們的冷漠。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_4:1
msgid "Enough now. I want to speak to your boss."
msgstr "夠了。我想和你的老闆談談。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_5
msgid "We don't care what you think. Just leave our island and never come back."
msgstr "我們不在乎你的想法。離開我們的島，永遠別回來。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur3_10
msgid "Go talk to Thalos. Although I'd rather you just disappear altogether."
msgstr "去找薩洛斯談談。雖然我寧願你乾脆消失。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur8
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_2b
msgid "The stars are bright tonight."
msgstr "今晚星光燦爛。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1
msgid "I am Thalos. Human, you are not welcome here."
msgstr "我是薩洛斯。人類，你在此不受歡迎。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1:0
msgid "I know by now."
msgstr "我現在知道了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1a:0
msgid "I am just looking for my brother, Andor. Have you perhaps seen him?"
msgstr "我只是在找我的兄弟，安多爾。你有沒有見過他？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1a:1
msgid "I mean no harm. I come in peace, seeking to understand your ways."
msgstr "我無意傷害。我帶著和平而來，尋求了解你們的方式。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1:3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1a:2
msgid "May I try riding one of your centaurs?"
msgstr "我可以試騎你們的半人馬嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1a
msgid "What business do you have on our island?"
msgstr "你來我們島上有何貴幹？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1b
msgid "Understand our ways? Humans have never cared to understand us. They see us as nothing more than beasts of burden."
msgstr "了解我們的方式？人類從未想過要了解我們。他們只把我們當作役獸。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1b:0
msgid "Half breads you mean."
msgstr "你的意思是半人馬。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1b:1
msgid "I'm not like other humans. I respect your kind and wish to prove it."
msgstr "我與其他人類不同。我尊重你們，並希望證明這一點。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_1z
msgid "You better leave now."
msgstr "你最好現在離開。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_2
msgid "This Andor, does he look a bit like you?"
msgstr "這個安多爾，他看起來有點像你嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_2:0
msgid "Yes, yes. Have you seen him? Where is he? When?"
msgstr "是的，是的。你有看到他嗎？他在哪裡？什麼時候？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_2a
msgid "Who can be sure?"
msgstr "誰能確定呢？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_2b:0
msgid "Never, ever try to elicit a straight answer from a centaur."
msgstr "千萬別試圖從半人馬那裡得到直接的答案。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_8
msgid "Words are cheap. Actions speak louder."
msgstr "說得容易，行動才有力。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_10
msgid "If you truly wish to prove yourself, you must complete a task for us."
msgstr "如果你真心想證明自己，必須為我們完成一項任務。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_10:0
msgid "What task do you require of me?"
msgstr "你需要我完成什麼任務？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_10:1
msgid "I won't clean out your stable."
msgstr "我不會幫你清理馬廄。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_12
msgid "There is a foul creature that lurks in the cave to the west. It resembles a human but is far more savage."
msgstr "西邊洞穴中潛伏著一隻邪惡的生物。它看似人類，卻更加兇猛。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_12a
msgid "It attacks my people and threatens our way of life."
msgstr "它攻擊我的族人，威脅我們的生活方式。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_12b
msgid "[with ominous voice] It is deadly."
msgstr "[以不祥的聲音] 它致命。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_12b:0
msgid "It is deadly? Then I'll make sure it's dead."
msgstr "致命的？那我就確保它死透。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_12b:2
msgid "Eh, well - I'm out."
msgstr "嗯，好吧——我退出。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_30
msgid "Go and slay this beast. Then I will reconsider your intentions."
msgstr "去斬殺這頭野獸。然後我會重新考慮你的意圖。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_32
msgid "We centaurs have difficulty walking up stairs and fighting monsters in caves."
msgstr "我們半人馬走樓梯和在洞穴中與怪物戰鬥都很困難。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_34
msgid "Here you humans are exceptionally advantageous."
msgstr "你們人類在這裡特別有利。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_35
msgid "Go and free us from the bane of all centaurs."
msgstr "去解救我們，擺脫所有半人馬的禍害。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_35:0
msgid "Consider it done. I will rid your island of this threat."
msgstr "就交給我吧。我會幫你清除島上的威脅。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_36
msgid "Do not underestimate the danger, human. This creature is formidable."
msgstr "別小看危險，人類。這生物相當強大。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_38
msgid "But if you succeed, your efforts will be rewarded."
msgstr "但若成功，你的努力將獲得回報。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_100
msgid "What news do you bring?"
msgstr "有何消息？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_100:0
msgid "I met acquaintances in the entrance to the cave."
msgstr "我在洞穴入口遇到了熟人。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_100:1
msgid "I have found my brother Andor, locked in a room down in that cave."
msgstr "我找到我兄弟安多爾了，他被關在那個洞穴裡的一間房間裡。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_100:2
msgid "The creature has been slain. Your island is safe once more."
msgstr "生物已被擊殺。你的島嶼再次安全。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_110
msgid "Even more people. Terrible - does it never end?"
msgstr "更多人。糟糕——這永遠沒有盡頭嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_110:0
msgid "I'll continue looking for the monster"
msgstr "我會繼續尋找那隻怪物"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_112
msgid "Do that"
msgstr "去做吧"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_130
msgid "Is that so?"
msgstr "是這樣嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_130:0
msgid "Yes. I'll go free him now."
msgstr "是的。我現在去救他。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_132
msgid "Do that if you must. Although I am not glad with even more humans on our island."
msgstr "如果你非做不可。雖然我並不歡迎島上多了更多人類。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_134
msgid "After all, humans are a useless nuisance to centaur society."
msgstr "畢竟，人類對半人馬社會來說只是無用的麻煩。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_300
msgid "Impressive, human. Yes, I can feel it."
msgstr "令人印象深刻，人類。是的，我能感受到。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_300:0
msgid "And this heart does prove it."
msgstr "而這顆心正是證明。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_300:1
msgid "I wanted to prove it with the monster's heart, but I seem to have lost it. Just a minute ..."
msgstr "我本想用怪物的心臟來證明，但好像弄丟了。等一下..."

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_302
msgid "That foul creature is no more. A great burden is lifted from my heart."
msgstr "那惡獸已不復存在。我的心頭重擔終於卸下。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_310
msgid "You have proven yourself to be more than just another ignorant human."
msgstr "你已證明自己不只是另一個無知的人類。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_310:0
msgid "Very good."
msgstr "非常好。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_390
msgid "Alas, you have earned our gratitude."
msgstr "唉，你贏得了我們的感激。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_centaur9_392
msgid "You are free to roam our island as you please. And know that you will always have a friend in the centaurs."
msgstr "你可以自由在我們的島上漫遊。記住，半人馬永遠是你的朋友。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew4a
msgid "You know that stuff is illegal and that you can get in serious trouble just for possessing it?"
msgstr "你知道那東西是違法的，光是持有就可能惹上大麻煩？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew4a:0
msgid "What can I say? I like to go rogue."
msgstr "我能說什麼呢？我就是喜歡當盜賊。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew_korhald_cop_30a
msgid "I don't know anything about it. Which makes me want it even more. Can I have it? I will reward you handsomely for it."
msgstr "我一無所知，這反而讓我更想要它。可以給我嗎？我會慷慨獎勵你。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_korhald_41
msgid "OK, but don't keep this coin collector waiting too long. I want that coin."
msgstr "好，但別讓這個收集者等太久。我想要那枚硬幣。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:korhald_cave_hidden_basket_examine_loot_f2
msgid "you have just found a coin and a shield. You should bring this coin back to Forenza."
msgstr "你剛找到一枚硬幣和一面盾牌。你應該把這枚硬幣帶回佛倫札。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:korhald_cave_hidden_basket_examine_loot_g2
msgid "you have just found a coin and a shield. You should bring this coin back to Gylew."
msgstr "你剛撿到一枚硬幣和一面盾牌。你應該把這枚硬幣帶回給Gylew。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:script_open_korhald_tomb_door_no_pendant
msgid "You do however notice that the keyhole is oddly shaped, but you have no key that will fit."
msgstr "你注意到鑰匙孔形狀奇特，但你沒有合適的鑰匙。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:script_open_korhald_tomb_door_has_pendant
msgid "But before dispair sets in, you notice that the keyhole is oddly shaped."
msgstr "但在絕望降臨之前，你注意到鑰匙孔形狀異常。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:script_open_korhald_tomb_door_has_pendant:0
msgid "Use the Mysterious Korhald 'pendant' as a key."
msgstr "使用神秘的科哈爾德「墜飾」作為鑰匙。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:moriath_history_6a
msgid "They admired Korhald because without him the city of Remgard would not exist, but he was not well liked. He ruled the city like an oppressive king. When he died the cityfolk built a tomb in his honor, but well away from Remgard. Somewhere to the south."
msgstr ""
"他們敬佩科哈爾德，因為沒有他，雷姆加德城不會存在，但他並不受歡迎。他像暴君般"
"統治著城市。他死後，城民為他建造了一座陵墓，但遠離雷姆加德，在南方某處。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:script_open_korhald_tomb_door_unlocked
msgid "Is it really locked?"
msgstr "真的鎖著嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:script_open_korhald_tomb_door_unlocked:0
msgid "[Push it open.]"
msgstr "[推開它。]"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew_defeated_5
msgid "You've killed the defenseless coin collector."
msgstr "你殺死了手無寸鐵的收錢人。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_korhald_gylew_not_dead
msgid "You wimp! Get me my brother's key now."
msgstr "你這懦夫！現在就把我兄弟的鑰匙給我。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew_korhald_25
msgid "You did? Oh, yes, I remember now."
msgstr "你做了？喔，對了，我現在想起來了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew_korhald_25:0
msgid "You're a crazy old man."
msgstr "你真是個瘋狂的老頭。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew_korhald_27
msgid "There are two locks! How can this be? Do you know anything about a second key?"
msgstr "有兩把鎖！這怎麼可能？你知道第二把鑰匙的事嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laerothbasement2_korhald_notice_sign
msgid "As you approach these crates, a sign on the wall catches your eye and something tells you to take a look at it first."
msgstr "當你走近這些箱子時，牆上的一個告示吸引了你的注意，直覺告訴你先看看它。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laerothbasement2_korhald_sign_10
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laerothbasement2_korhald_sign_nope
msgid "Not paying attention, you fall flat on your face. Damaging your chin and forehead."
msgstr "因不專心，你跌倒在地，傷及下巴和額頭。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laerothbasement2_korhald_sign_10:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laerothbasement2_korhald_sign_nope:0
msgid "Oops, that's really going to cost me."
msgstr "哎呀，這可真讓我損失慘重。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laerothbasement2_korhald_sign_read
msgid "You have already examined the nearly illegible sign hanging on the wall."
msgstr "你已經查看過掛在牆上的幾乎無法辨識的告示牌。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew_attack_2
msgid "My trusty henchman will take care of you."
msgstr "我可靠的手下會處理你的。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gylew_attack_2:0
msgid "Oh, you need someone to help you?"
msgstr "喔，你需要人幫忙嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:mysterious_map_stop_and_review_west
msgid "Let's stop once again and look at the 'Mysterious Korhald map'."
msgstr "讓我們再停下來看看「神秘的科爾哈德地圖」。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:mysterious_map_stop_and_review_korhald_cave_outdoor1
msgid "According to the map, I'm really close now and I should continue head west."
msgstr "根據地圖，我現在非常接近，應該繼續向西前進。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:stop_henchman_key
msgid "If you come back here, I will kill you!"
msgstr "如果你再回來，我會殺了你！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:script_close_cave_door_scared
msgid ""
"As the heavy doors of the cave swing shut with a resounding slam, a sudden wave of fear grips you as the rush of wind hits your back.\n"
"The echoing sound reverberates through you, sending shivers down your spine. This leaves you visibly shaken with a sense of uneasiness, casting a temporary shadow over your courage."
msgstr ""
"當洞穴厚重的門轟然關上，一陣風猛然襲向你的背脊，恐懼感瞬間湧上心頭。\n"
"回聲在你體內迴盪，令你脊背發涼。你明顯感到不安，勇氣暫時籠罩在暗影之中。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:script_close_cave_door_not_scared
msgid "Oh, that was the door closing. No big deal now."
msgstr "喔，那是門關上了。現在沒什麼大不了的。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_10:0
msgid "[Show the coins]"
msgstr "[顯示硬幣]"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_20
msgid "[The coin collector eagerly examines the pilfered coins, eyes gleaming with fascination.]..."
msgstr "[硬幣收藏家急切地檢視被偷的硬幣，眼中閃爍著著迷的光芒。]..."

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_30
msgid "Ah, these coins tell a tale of clandestine dealings and shadowy alliances."
msgstr "啊，這些硬幣訴說著秘密交易與暗影聯盟的故事。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_35
msgid "These bronze pieces bear the mark of the Lunar Whisper, an infamous thieves' guild that once ruled the underground markets. Legend has it, these coins were minted in secret, their alloy infused with fragments of moonstone to enhance the guild's stealthy endeavors"
msgstr ""
"這些銅幣刻有月語者的印記，這是曾經統治地下市場的臭名昭著盜賊公會。傳說這些硬"
"幣是秘密鑄造的，合金中摻入了月光石碎片，以增強公會的隱匿行動。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_40
msgid "These silver coins hold the captivating history of a nomadic people, a seafaring tribe whose exploits were as boundless as the horizon. Born from the hands of skilled minters among the maritime wanderers, these coins tell the tale of the Ocean Nomads, a group of sailors, pirates, and free-spirited adventurers."
msgstr ""
"這些銀幣承載著一個遊牧民族的迷人歷史，一個航海部落，他們的事蹟如地平線般無垠"
"。由海上流浪者中技藝高超的鑄幣師打造，這些硬幣述說著海洋遊牧者的故事——一群水"
"手、海盜與自由奔放的冒險者。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_45
msgid "The silver pieces depict a mighty ship sailing under the moonlit sky, capturing the essence of the Ocean Nomads' freedom and unity. Legends speak of these coins being crafted during the tribe's grand gatherings, where sailors from various corners of the seas exchanged not only goods but also these tokens, forging connections that transcended the vastness of the ocean."
msgstr ""
"銀幣上刻有一艘在月光下航行的強大船隻，象徵海洋遊牧民的自由與團結。傳說這些硬"
"幣是在部落盛會中鑄造，來自海域各方的水手不僅交換貨物，也交換這些象徵，締造超"
"越大洋的聯繫。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_45:0
msgid "So they are priceless?"
msgstr "所以它們是無價之寶？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_50
msgid ""
"[The collector pauses, his gaze lingering on the coins.] These pieces are not merely currency; they are artifacts of a hidden past,\n"
"a glimpse into the underground world where alliances were forged in secrecy. I'd be willing to make you an offer for these intriguing\n"
"tokens of history, should you be interested in parting with them."
msgstr ""
"[收藏家停頓，目光停留在硬幣上。]\n"
"這些不僅是貨幣；它們是隱秘過去的文物，窺見地下世界中秘密締結的同盟。\n"
"如果你願意出售這些引人入勝的歷史象徵，我願意出價收購。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_50:0
msgid "So you want to buy them all?"
msgstr "所以你想全部買下嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_55
msgid "Well, yes. But not all of them. Afterall, who needs 110 of these?"
msgstr "嗯，是的。但不是全部。畢竟，誰需要110個這種東西？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_55:0
msgid "OK, so what do you want to buy?"
msgstr "好的，那你想買什麼？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_60
msgid "Well, let's talk price first. You see, the silver coin is worth 11 gold in weight and the bronze is worth 5 gold in weight. But, to a collector they are worth more. Let's make this simple. I will pay you double those values for each coin and I'll take 5 of each."
msgstr ""
"好，先談價格。你看，銀幣按重量值11金，銅幣按重量值5金。但對收藏家來說，它們更"
"值錢。簡單說，我願付雙倍價錢買每枚硬幣，且各收5枚。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_60:0
msgid "So how much total than?"
msgstr "那總共是多少？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_65
msgid "110 gold for the silver and 50 for the bronze coins."
msgstr "銀幣110枚，銅幣50枚。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_65:0
msgid "That little? No, thanks"
msgstr "那麼少？不用了"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:coin_collector_thief_coins_65:1
msgid "Well, something is better than nothing."
msgstr "嗯，有總比沒有好。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_brimhaven_11
msgid "Oh, yeah. Let's look in that chest now."
msgstr "喔，對了。現在我們去看看那個箱子吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured
msgid "Hey, you. I need your help!"
msgstr "嘿，你。需要你的幫忙！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured:0
msgid "What? Who are you? How did you get in here?"
msgstr "什麼？你是誰？你怎麼進來的？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_need_help:0
msgid "What kind of help?"
msgstr "需要什麼幫助？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_need_help
msgid "Nerver mind that now. I am injured and I need your help!"
msgstr "先別管那些了。我受傷了，需要你的幫助！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_explained
msgid "Seriously?! Can't you see that I am bleeding and weak?"
msgstr "認真嗎？！你沒看到我正在流血且虛弱嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_explained:0
msgid "Well, I have this ointment for stopping wounds. Take it."
msgstr "嗯，我有這個藥膏可以止血。拿去吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_explained:1
msgid "What do you want? A healing potion maybe?"
msgstr "你要什麼？要一瓶治療藥水嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_ointment
msgid "Oh, that's wonderful. Thank you."
msgstr "喔，太好了。謝謝你。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help
msgid "Please. I'll take whatever you have that could heal me."
msgstr "拜託。只要是能治療我的東西，我都願意拿。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help:0
msgid "Well I have a bonemeal potion. It's yours now. Take it."
msgstr "我這裡有一瓶骨粉藥水。現在是你的了，拿去吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help:1
msgid "Well I have a special bonemeal potion. It's yours now. Take it."
msgstr "我有一瓶特製的骨粉藥水。現在是你的了，拿去吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help:2
msgid "Here, take it. It's a really strong potion of healing."
msgstr "拿去吧。這是一瓶非常強效的治療藥水。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help:3
msgid "I have this really special potion of healing that I got from a very wise old man. Take it!"
msgstr "我有一瓶非常特別的治療藥水，是從一位非常睿智的老人那裡得到的。拿去吧！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help:4
msgid "I have an ordinary potion of health for you. Take it!"
msgstr "我有一瓶普通的治療藥水給你。拿去吧！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help:5
msgid "I have an little health potion for you. It's all I have. Take it!"
msgstr "我有一瓶小型治療藥水給你。這是我唯一的了。拿去吧！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help:6
msgid "I'm so sorry, but I have nothing that can help you."
msgstr "非常抱歉，我沒有任何能幫助你的東西。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help_bm
msgid "Oh, this stuff is great!"
msgstr "喔，這東西真棒！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help_mph
msgid "This stuff tastes nasty, but I swear I can feel it helping already."
msgstr "這東西味道難聞，但我發誓我已經感覺到它在幫助我了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help_lph
msgid "Oh, now this stuff feels like its healing power will last just a little bit longer."
msgstr "喔，這藥感覺療效會持續久一點。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help_rph
msgid "Oh, this should help. Thank you."
msgstr "喔，這應該有幫助。謝謝你。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help_minor_ph
msgid "Oh, this should help. I guess."
msgstr "喔，這應該有幫助吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:forenza_island_injured_help_not
msgid "You are a disappointment. Anyways..."
msgstr "你真讓人失望。總之..."

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:Remgard_jetty_sign
msgid "From this jetty you have an excitingly beautiful view of the mighty Lake Laeroth."
msgstr "從這個碼頭你可以欣賞到壯麗的萊洛斯湖美景。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:Remgard_jetty_sign:0
msgid "What a lot of water!"
msgstr "真是好多水！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:Remgard_jetty_sign_2
msgid "You can clearly see the neighboring group of islands and the old buildings on them."
msgstr "你可以清楚看到鄰近的群島及其上的古老建築。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:Remgard_jetty_sign_2:0
msgid "That ruin over there will probably be called \"Laeroth Manor\"."
msgstr "那邊的遺跡大概叫做「萊羅斯莊園」。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:Remgard_jetty_sign_3
msgid "You'd like to get over there, but you realize it's not possible from here."
msgstr "你想過去，但發現從這裡無法到達。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:Remgard_jetty_sign_3:0
msgid "I'LL FIND A WAY!!"
msgstr "我一定會找到方法！！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:Remgard_jetty_sign_4
msgid "You hear the echoes of your shout - then silence."
msgstr "你聽見自己的呼喊回聲——隨即寂靜無聲。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:Remgard_jetty_sign_4:0
msgid "So close yet so far."
msgstr "近在咫尺，卻遙不可及。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_spider
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_centipede
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_1
msgid "As you approach the hole, you notice something inside and are intrigued."
msgstr "當你靠近洞口時，注意到裡面有些東西，感到好奇。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_spider:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_centipede:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_1:0
msgid "[Bend down and take a look.]"
msgstr "[蹲下來看看。]"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_spider:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_centipede:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_1:1
msgid "No, I don't think so. I'm not that intrigued enough to risk my life."
msgstr "不，我不這麼認為。我沒那麼好奇到願意冒生命危險。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_spider_2
msgid "Ugh, spiders!"
msgstr "噁，蜘蛛！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laeroth_barn_basement_centipede_2
msgid "Ugh, centipedes"
msgstr "噁，蜈蚣"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:korhald_cave_hidden_locked_chest_no_key
msgid "This chest is locked and you don't seem to have the key."
msgstr "這個箱子被鎖住了，你似乎沒有鑰匙。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:korhald_cave_hidden_locked_chest_not_looted
msgid "The chest is locked, but you can try that \"Mystery Laeroth key\" you found."
msgstr "箱子被鎖住了，但你可以試試你找到的「神秘萊洛斯鑰匙」。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:korhald_cave_hidden_locked_chest_not_looted:0
msgid "Let's get this thing unlocked."
msgstr "讓我們把這東西解鎖。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:korhald_cave_hidden_locked_chest_not_looted:1
msgid "This might be a mistake. I should leave before it's too late!"
msgstr "這可能是個錯誤。我應該趁還來得及離開！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:korhald_cave_hidden_locked_chest_loot
msgid "Inside the chest, you find a book with an ancient leather cover, a helmet and some valuables."
msgstr "在箱子裡，你發現一本古老皮革封面的書、一頂頭盔和一些貴重物品。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:odd_coin_collector_ask_about_locked_chest
msgid "A locked chest you say? Well, I'm not really sure, but logic tells me to look back in the Laeroth Manor."
msgstr "你說有個鎖著的箱子？嗯，我不太確定，但理智告訴我應該回去萊洛斯莊園看看。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:odd_coin_collector_ask_about_locked_chest:0
msgid "Oh, yeah. That makes sense."
msgstr "喔，對啊。這就說得通了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:odd_coin_collector_ask_about_locked_chest:1
msgid "Oh, come on! I don't want to go back there again."
msgstr "拜託！我才不想再回去那裡。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gwendolyn_1
msgid "Hello, stranger. What are you doing down here?"
msgstr "你好，陌生人。你在這裡做什麼？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gwendolyn_1:0
msgid "I'm looking for my brother Andor. Have you seen him? He kind of looks like me."
msgstr "我在找我哥哥安多爾。你有看過他嗎？他長得有點像我。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gwendolyn_1:1
msgid "What are you doing down here?"
msgstr "你在這裡做什麼？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gwendolyn_2
msgid "Well, unless he looks like one of these books, I will say \"no\"."
msgstr "嗯，除非他看起來像這些書中的某一本，否則我會說「不」。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gwendolyn_3
msgid "You see, I've been down here all day looking for a book for Skylenar as he really needs it."
msgstr "你看，我整天都在這裡找一本書給斯凱雷納，他真的很需要那本書。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gwendolyn_3:0
msgid "Well, maybe I could help you? What is the name of this book?"
msgstr "嗯，也許我可以幫忙？這本書叫什麼名字？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gwendolyn_4
msgid "Oh, how nice of you to offer. It's called \"The Tome of Veiled Truths\", but I don't think you will have much luck finding it."
msgstr ""
"哦，真是太好了，你願意幫忙。它叫做《隱秘真理之書》，但我覺得你不太可能找到它"
"。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:gwendolyn_4:0
msgid "Oh, OK. I will let you be then."
msgstr "喔，好吧，那我就不打擾你了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison1a
msgid "Please help us!"
msgstr "請幫幫我們！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell1:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell2:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell3:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell4:0
msgid "Unlock."
msgstr "解鎖"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell1:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell2:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell3:1
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell4:1
msgid "Unfortunately the lock is now broken."
msgstr "很不幸，鎖已壞掉。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell1:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell2:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell3:2
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell4:2
msgid "You have no matching key."
msgstr "你沒有相符的鑰匙。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell1_unlock
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell2_unlock
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell3_unlock
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_cell4_unlock
msgid "Click."
msgstr "點擊。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_01a
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_02
msgid "Please, can you help us?"
msgstr "請問，您能幫助我們嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_01b
msgid "Please open the other cells and free us all! Hurry! Then come back to me."
msgstr "請打開其他牢房，救我們所有人！快點！然後回來找我。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_01b:0
msgid "OK, just a second ..."
msgstr "好的，請稍等一下..."

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_02a
msgid "The prison torturer died, but he took the life force of us prisoners in the hope to live again."
msgstr "監獄酷刑者死了，但他奪取了我們囚犯的生命力，希望能重生。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_02b
msgid "It didn't work, because we had so little life left anyway."
msgstr "沒用，反正我們的生命已經所剩無幾。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_02c
msgid "But now we cannot rest in peace, because he is still here, somewhere in the lower caves. He needs to be destroyed, but we cannot do it because he has control over us."
msgstr ""
"但現在我們無法安息，因為他仍在下層洞穴的某處。他必須被消滅，但我們無法做到，"
"因為他控制著我們。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_02c:0
msgid "OK. I'll do it. I am not afraid of a few monsters!"
msgstr "好，我來做。我不怕幾隻怪物！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_02c:1
msgid "No thanks. Seems dangerous, and there's nothing in it for me."
msgstr "不用了。看起來很危險，對我沒好處。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_03
msgid "Thank you! But beware! He has guards that are like him. They may appear to be human at first glance, but they are not!"
msgstr "謝謝你！但要小心！他有和他一樣的護衛。乍看之下他們像人類，但其實不是！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_3a
msgid "Ohhh! What will become of us?"
msgstr "喔喔！我們該怎麼辦？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_end_10
msgid "Oh, the kid is back. Just look!"
msgstr "喔，孩子回來了。快看！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_end_10:0
msgid "You can finally find peace. Kotheses, the torturer is dead."
msgstr "你終於可以安息了。酷刑者科塞斯已死。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_end_20
msgid "Ooooh! We are eternally grateful!"
msgstr "喔喔！我們永遠感激不盡！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_prison_end_30
msgid "Everything is in order now. The prisoners are back in their cells, and the Demon guards are on duty again."
msgstr "現在一切就緒。囚犯已被送回牢房，惡魔守衛重新值勤。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_2
msgid "Why do you kill my precious demons?! I told you to stay here beside me!"
msgstr "你為什麼要殺我珍貴的惡魔？！我叫你留在我身邊！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_2:0
msgid "They have attacked me!"
msgstr "他們攻擊我！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_3
msgid "Do as you are told, and there will be no harm."
msgstr "照命行事，必無大礙。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_3:0
msgid "[softly] Gna gna gna."
msgstr "[輕聲] 嘎嘎嘎。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_key
msgid "Stop, kid! Not a step further!"
msgstr "站住，孩子！不准再往前一步！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_10
msgid "Hello, child."
msgstr "你好，孩子。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_10a
msgid "Would you like to learn the trade of a torturer?"
msgstr "你想學習酷刑師的技藝嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_10a:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_152
msgid "Tell me more about it."
msgstr "告訴我更多細節。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_10a:1
msgid "I'm sorry, I don't have time for that. I have to look for my brother. Do you perhaps know where he is? He looks something like me."
msgstr "抱歉，我沒時間理會這個。我得去找我哥哥。你知道他在哪裡嗎？他長得有點像我。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_10a:2
msgid "You stole the life force of your captives."
msgstr "你偷走了俘虜的生命力。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_10a:3
msgid "Very gladly. I always like to learn new things."
msgstr "非常樂意。我總喜歡學習新事物。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11
msgid "I seek a young apprentice to train in our essential duties."
msgstr "我尋找一位年輕學徒，來學習我們的重要職責。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11a
msgid "You will start by observing and assisting me during interrogations, learning the delicate balance of inflicting pain."
msgstr "你將從旁觀察並協助我進行審訊，學習施加痛苦的微妙平衡。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11b
msgid "While keeping the prisoner alive, of course."
msgstr "當然，要活著留下囚犯。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11b:0
msgid "Oh, makes sense."
msgstr "喔，說得通。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11c
msgid "Your education will include mastering various torture devices and understanding their effects."
msgstr "你的訓練將包括掌握各種酷刑器具及了解其效果。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11d
msgid "Over the years, you will gradually take on more responsibility, eventually conducting interrogations on your own once you have proven your skill and steadiness."
msgstr ""
"隨著時間推移，你將逐漸承擔更多責任，當你證明了自己的技巧與穩定後，最終將獨自"
"進行審訊。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11d:0
msgid "Interrogations you call it?"
msgstr "你稱之為審訊？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11e
msgid "Sure. We only want the truth. Nothing more. It is a very prestigious work."
msgstr "當然。我們只想知道真相。別無他求。這是一項非常崇高的工作。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11e:1
msgid "Then why do you wear a mask at public executions?"
msgstr "那你為何在公開處決時戴著面具？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_11f
msgid "Enough questions."
msgstr "夠了，別問了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_12
msgid "No, I don't know where Andor is now."
msgstr "不，我不知道安多爾現在在哪裡。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_12:0
msgid "Oh, how do you know his name?"
msgstr "哦，你怎麼知道他的名字？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_14
msgid "Well, he was here a while ago and was shown a few tricks."
msgstr "嗯，他剛才在這裡，已經被示範過幾招了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_14:0
msgid "So he was here too?"
msgstr "所以他也在這裡？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_16
msgid "Andor was a very eager student. It's a shame he didn't stay."
msgstr "安多爾是個非常熱心的學生。可惜他沒留下來。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_18
msgid "Yes. So?"
msgstr "是的。那又怎樣？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_20
msgid "You are sure you don't want to learn the art of a torturer?"
msgstr "你確定不想學習酷刑師的技藝嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_20:0
msgid "That is no job for me."
msgstr "那不是我的工作。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_20:1
msgid "Well, I could try at least."
msgstr "嗯，我至少可以試試。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_30
msgid "OK, then let's get started. This is a very important job, you know?"
msgstr "好，那我們開始吧。這是一項非常重要的工作，你知道吧？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_32
msgid "You get people to tell you the truth you want to hear."
msgstr "你讓人說出你想聽的真相。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_34
msgid "Like these dangerous captives in the cells above. They all confessed. Luckily they are in safe custody."
msgstr "就像上面牢房裡這些危險的囚犯。他們全都招供了。幸好他們被妥善看管著。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_36:0
msgid "I opened the cells and released them."
msgstr "我打開牢房，放了他們出來。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_40
msgid "Not again! You need to wake up the Demon Guard and send them upstairs. That way you will quickly get the problem under control."
msgstr "又來了！你需要喚醒惡魔守衛並派他們上樓。這樣你才能迅速控制局面。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_40:0
msgid "Demons? That doesn't sound safe."
msgstr "惡魔？聽起來不太安全。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_42
msgid "You screwed up, you have to fix it."
msgstr "你搞砸了，必須修正。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_42:1
msgid "Sigh. I know."
msgstr "嘆氣。我知道。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_44
msgid "Here take this Oegyth crystal."
msgstr "拿去這顆奧吉斯水晶。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_45
msgid "Take this precious Oegyth crystal to that small room to the south and continue through the corridor."
msgstr "將這顆珍貴的奧伊斯晶體帶到南邊那間小房間，然後繼續穿過走廊。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_46
msgid "Then throw the crystal with all your might into the dark abyss."
msgstr "然後用盡全力將水晶投進黑暗深淵。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_46:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_odilia_explain_capture_2:0
msgid "What?!"
msgstr "什麼？！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_48
msgid "Do it. Then run for your life back to me so that I can protect you from them."
msgstr "去做吧。然後拼命跑回我這裡，讓我保護你免受他們傷害。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_50
msgid "You hear me? Don't wait for the demons. They are deadly."
msgstr "你聽到了嗎？別等惡魔來，他們致命無比。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_52
msgid "Now. Move."
msgstr "現在。動作。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_60
msgid "What a pity. At least let me warn you about the prisoners above."
msgstr "真可惜。至少讓我警告你上方的囚犯。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_60:0
msgid "What is with them?"
msgstr "他們到底怎麼了？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_62
msgid "They are devious. They are highly dangerous."
msgstr "他們狡詐且極度危險。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_64
msgid "They must be imprisoned for all reasons."
msgstr "他們必須因各種理由被囚禁。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_66
msgid "Their lies influence you to have mercy. But turn your back to them they pierce you cruelly."
msgstr "他們的謊言讓你心生憐憫。但當你背向他們時，他們殘酷地刺穿你。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_70
msgid "Believe it or not."
msgstr "信不信由你。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_70:0
msgid "Not."
msgstr "不是。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_74
msgid "At least I play fair. I do not come from ambush, but rather announce my attack."
msgstr "至少我公平競技。我不會伏擊，而是會先宣告攻擊。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_74:0
msgid "OK ..."
msgstr "好的 ..."

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_76
msgid "... which is now!"
msgstr "... 就是現在！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_76:0
msgid "How gross."
msgstr "真噁心。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_100
msgid "Now you can talk to the demons. To all of them. Tell them what they have to do."
msgstr "現在你可以與惡魔交談。與所有惡魔。告訴他們該做什麼。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_100:0
msgid "All of them?"
msgstr "全部嗎？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_101
msgid "To all of those that you have left alive. But please, stay close to me this time."
msgstr "對所有你留下的活口。但這次，請靠近我。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_102
msgid "But stay close to me."
msgstr "但要靠近我。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_110
msgid "I see it in your eyes - you want to leave too. Like your brother."
msgstr "我從你眼中看見——你也想離開。就像你的兄弟一樣。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_torturer_110:0
msgid "Yes. Thank you for your lessons."
msgstr "是的。謝謝您的教導。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call
msgid "An icy cold breeze hits your face."
msgstr "一陣冰冷的寒風撲面而來。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call:0
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call_10:0
msgid "Let's throw an oegyth crystal down there."
msgstr "我們把一顆奧蓋斯水晶丟下去吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call:1
msgid "I would like to throw an oegyth crystal down there, if I only had one."
msgstr "我真想丟一顆奧蓋斯水晶下去，可惜我只有一顆。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call:2
msgid "Let's try to throw a rock."
msgstr "試著丟一塊石頭吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call:3
msgid "What an eery place. I better leave this alone."
msgstr "真是個詭異的地方。我還是別管它比較好。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call_10:1
msgid "I better leave this alone."
msgstr "我還是別管它比較好。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call_20
msgid "You hear an uproar from far away. But coming nearer and nearer."
msgstr "你聽見遠方傳來喧囂聲，卻越來越近。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon_call_20:0
msgid "Well, let's hurry from here - now."
msgstr "那麼，我們現在就快點離開這裡。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon4
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon5
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon7
msgid "Command us!"
msgstr "指揮我們！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon4:0
msgid "You go and watch over the prisoners in the cells."
msgstr "你去看守牢房裡的囚犯。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon5:0
msgid "You stand guard in the hall under the cell block."
msgstr "你在牢房樓下的走廊守衛。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon7:0
msgid "You protect Kotheses in case the prisoners get here."
msgstr "你保護科塞斯，以防囚犯到達這裡。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon9
msgid "[hollow voice] Take back your glass ball, brave little human."
msgstr "[空洞的聲音] 拿回你的水晶球吧，勇敢的小人類。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon9:0
msgid "Th ... thanks."
msgstr "那個... 謝謝。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:lae_demon
msgid "We are legion. Fear us."
msgstr "我們是軍團。畏懼我們。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:hungry_pig_upset_stomach
msgid "[Squeal] Please, stop feeding these to me. They're making my stomach hurt."
msgstr "[哼哼] 拜託，別再餵我這些了。我的肚子痛了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:hungry_pig_upset_stomach:0
msgid "What? You can talk?"
msgstr "什麼？你會說話？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:hungry_pig_upset_stomach:1
msgid "More eating and less talking."
msgstr "多吃少說。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:hungry_pig_upset_stomach_2:0
msgid "Here. Have another piece of rotten meat. It's good for you."
msgstr "給你。再吃一塊腐肉，對你有好處。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:hungry_pig_upset_stomach_3
#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:hungry_pig_sick
msgid "[Squeal]"
msgstr "[哼哼]"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:hungry_pig_feed:0
msgid "Hungry? Here, have a piece of rotten meat."
msgstr "餓了嗎？來，吃塊腐肉吧。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:smuggler5_pig
msgid "Yeah, I'm sure you didn't. Why don't you go have another one of \"Lowyna's special brews\"?"
msgstr "是啊，我相信你沒有。要不要再來一杯「洛伊娜的特製釀酒」？"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:guard_dog
msgid "[Grrr]"
msgstr "[嗚嗚]"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest2_beware_dogs
msgid "Beware of dogs! Trespassers are not tolerated."
msgstr "小心狗隻！禁止擅入。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man
msgid "What were you doing in my house!"
msgstr "你在我家裡做什麼！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man:0
msgid "I've come a long distance in the persuit of my brother Andor. So I peeked inside to see if he was in there."
msgstr ""
"我為了尋找我的兄弟安多爾，走了很長的路。所以我偷看了一下，想知道他是否在裡面"
"。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man:1
msgid "I am looking for someone that could explain why that land over there [pointing west] is poisoned."
msgstr "我正在尋找能解釋那邊[指向西方]土地為何被污染的人。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man:2
msgid "I was looking for help in getting into that cave just west of here."
msgstr "我正在尋求幫助，想進入就在這裡西邊的那個洞穴。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man_5
msgid "Do you really think that I believe that? Who are you?! What do you really want?!"
msgstr "你真的以為我會相信嗎？你是誰？！你到底想要什麼？！"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man_5:0
msgid "I don't care what you don't believe because that's the truth."
msgstr "我不在乎你不信，因為那就是事實。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man_5:1
msgid "Can you just answer my question now or I will go back in your house?"
msgstr "你現在能回答我的問題嗎？不然我就回你家去了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man_dog
msgid "Well, with that attitude, you better get out of here now before I unleash my hounds on you."
msgstr "既然你這麼說，最好現在就離開，否則我就放我的獵犬追你。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:waterway_forest_isolated_man_dog:0
msgid "OK, calm down. I'm leaving."
msgstr "好了，冷靜點。我走了。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:hungry_pig_dies
msgid "The hungry pig dies due to the rotten meat."
msgstr "飢餓的豬因腐肉而死。"

#: conversationlist_laeroth.json:laerothbasement2_cannot_examine_chest
msgid "As you approach these crates, you quickly develop an appreciation for their age. You also notice the vast amount of nasty cobwebs surrounding them. Outside of all that, you are bored and decide that it's time to move on."
msgstr ""
"當你靠近這些箱子時，立刻感受到它們的年代久遠。你也注意到周圍纏繞著大量骯髒的"
"蜘蛛網。除此之外，你感到無聊，決定繼續前進。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:sign_feygard_wexlow
msgid "North: Feygard"
msgstr "北方：妖境"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:guynmart_fog
msgid "You can't get through this dense fog here."
msgstr "你無法穿越這裡的濃霧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster_startquest_10
msgid "This fog seems to be very unnatural."
msgstr "這霧氣似乎非常不自然。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster_startquest_20
msgid "Let's look for the source of it. Maybe we can find out how to lift the fog."
msgstr "我們去找找霧的來源。或許能找到解除迷霧的方法。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster1_heart_10
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster2_heart_10
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster3_heart_10
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster4_heart_10
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster5_heart_10
msgid "The fog vanishes completely as soon as you touch its heart."
msgstr "當你觸碰到它的核心時，霧氣立即消散。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_5
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_10
msgid "Me and my brothers watch over the ruler of the swamp."
msgstr "我和我的兄弟們守護著沼澤的統治者。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_1:0
msgid "Not for long, some of your brothers have all left the area already. Attack!"
msgstr "不久了，你的一些兄弟已經離開這裡。攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_1:1
msgid "So I'm going to talk to your remaining brothers."
msgstr "那我就去跟你剩下的兄弟們談談。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_5:0
msgid "Your brothers have all left the area already. Now to you ..."
msgstr "你的兄弟們都已經離開這個區域了。現在輪到你了..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_5:1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_10:1
msgid "So I'm going to talk to your brothers."
msgstr "那我就去跟你兄弟們談談。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_10:0
msgid "Not for long. Attack!"
msgstr "不會太久。攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_20
msgid "You can't defeat me as long as my brothers stand their ground."
msgstr "只要我的兄弟們堅守陣地，你就無法打敗我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_fogmonster9_20:0
msgid "Well, in that case stay here. I'll be back in a minute."
msgstr "那麼，你就在這裡等著。我馬上回來。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering
msgid "\"Pay homage to Elythara, radiant queen of the world!\""
msgstr "向世界的光輝女王艾莉薩拉致敬！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering:0
msgid "Homage - and above all gold ..."
msgstr "致敬——最重要的是黃金……"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20
msgid "Below the statue you see an offering bowl."
msgstr "在雕像下方你看到一個供品碗。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:0
msgid "Place 1 gold coin in the bowl."
msgstr "將1枚金幣放入碗中。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:1
msgid "Place 10 gold coins in the bowl."
msgstr "將10枚金幣放入碗中。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:2
msgid "Place 100 gold coins in the bowl."
msgstr "將100枚金幣放入碗中。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:3
msgid "Place 1000 gold coins in the bowl."
msgstr "將1000枚金幣放入碗中。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:4
msgid "Place 10000 gold coins in the bowl."
msgstr "將10000枚金幣放入碗中。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:5
msgid "Take 1 gold coin."
msgstr "拿取1枚金幣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:6
msgid "Take 10 gold coins."
msgstr "拿取10枚金幣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:7
msgid "Take 100 gold coins."
msgstr "拿取100枚金幣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_20:8
msgid "Take 1000 gold coins."
msgstr "拿取1000金幣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_30_100_heal
msgid "You hear a bodyless voice: \"Thank you.\""
msgstr "你聽到一個無形的聲音說：「謝謝你。」"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_30_1000_heal
msgid "You feel good. Very good, in fact."
msgstr "你感覺很好。事實上，非常好。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_30_10000_heal
msgid "You feel good. Extremely good, in fact."
msgstr "你感覺很好。事實上，非常好。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_34_1
msgid "Your gift will be viewed favorably."
msgstr "你的禮物將獲得好評。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_34_2
msgid "Thank you, in the name of Elythara."
msgstr "謝謝你，以艾莉薩拉之名。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_34_3
msgid "Let your name be praised in the halls of Elythara!"
msgstr "讓你的名字在艾莉薩拉的大廳中被讚頌！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_34_4
msgid "For the greatness of Elythara, our Godess!"
msgstr "為了我們的女神艾莉薩拉的偉大！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_34_5
msgid "Long live Elythara!"
msgstr "艾莉薩拉萬歲！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_36
msgid "You can not undo your evil theft."
msgstr "你無法撤銷你的邪惡盜竊。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_40_1a
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_40_10a
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_40_100a
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_40_1000a
msgid "Stealing from the goddess Elythara - are you sure?"
msgstr "從女神艾莉薩拉那裡偷東西——你確定嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_40_1a:1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_40_10a:1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_40_100a:1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_40_1000a:1
msgid "Hm, better not."
msgstr "嗯，還是算了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_offering_44
msgid "Elythara is known for her thirst for revenge. Fear her wrath!"
msgstr "艾莉薩拉以復仇心切聞名。畏懼她的憤怒！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:feygard_swamp_sign
msgid "Go away - while you still can!"
msgstr "快走——趁你還能逃！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:godoe
msgid "Hello, strange kid. Wanna pass?"
msgstr "你好，奇怪的孩子。想通過嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:godoe_2
msgid "Gimme 5 red glassy stones, and I'll open the path for you."
msgstr "給我5顆紅色玻璃石，我就幫你開路。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:godoe_2:0
msgid "Sure, I have plenty of them."
msgstr "當然，我有很多。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:godoe_2:1
msgid "Are 5 shiny gold coins OK too?"
msgstr "5枚閃亮的金幣也可以嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:godoe_4
msgid "Did I hear 500?"
msgstr "我聽到是500嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:godoe_4:0
msgid "Eh, sure. 500 shiny gold coins."
msgstr "嗯，好吧。500枚閃亮的金幣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:godoe_10
msgid "Good, good! Here you go. But don't waste time."
msgstr "好，好！給你。但別浪費時間。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:guynmart18_k_10
msgid "Coming back soon - Godoe"
msgstr "很快回來 - Godoe"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:guynmart18_s3_11
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:guynmart18_s3_12
msgid "I think I said: Don't waste time, did I not? Hee hee."
msgstr "我想我說過：別浪費時間，是不是？呵呵。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:guynmart_roadguard_12
msgid "The fog over there is very dangerous."
msgstr "那邊的霧非常危險。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:guynmart_roadguard_12:0
msgid "Which fog? Do you ever look up?"
msgstr "哪一層霧？你有沒有抬頭看過？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:guynmart_roadguard_30
msgid "Oh ... Forget it. I feel rather stupid now. Bye."
msgstr "喔……算了。我現在覺得自己很蠢。再見。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20
msgid "Who dares disturb my solitude? Be gone, or face my wrath!"
msgstr "誰敢打擾我的寧靜？離開，否則迎接我的怒火！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20:0
msgid "Sorry. I got lost in the fog."
msgstr "抱歉，我在霧中迷路了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20:1
msgid "I am not afraid of you. (You grope for your weapon)"
msgstr "我不怕你。（你摸索著武器）"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_10
msgid "Oh, how touching. The brave little hero got themselves lost, did they?"
msgstr "喔，真感人。這位勇敢的小英雄迷路了，是吧？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_12
msgid "And now you expect me to help you? Ha!"
msgstr "你現在還指望我幫你？哈！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_12:1
msgid "No. I can handle myself as always."
msgstr "不，我一向能應付自己。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_12:2
msgid "I managed to defeat the fog monsters that caused it."
msgstr "我成功擊敗了引起霧氣的怪物。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_20
msgid "Defeated my fog monsters, did you? Meddlesome brat!"
msgstr "你打敗了我的霧怪，是吧？多管閒事的小鬼！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_22
msgid "Those creatures were my only protection from unwanted visitors like you!"
msgstr "那些生物是我唯一抵禦像你這種不速之客的防護！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_22:0
msgid "I didn't know. The fog was disorienting ..."
msgstr "我不知道。霧氣讓人迷失方向..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_22:1
msgid "I'm sorry, I didn't mean to disturb you."
msgstr "抱歉，我無意打擾你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_22:2
msgid "Not much of a protection, were they."
msgstr "他們算不上什麼保護。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_24:0
msgid "And I just wanted to find my way to Feygard."
msgstr "我只是想找到通往妖境的路。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_24:1
msgid "I just want to find my way home."
msgstr "我只想找到回家的路。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_30
msgid "[Grumbles] Lost, you say? It's your own fault for wandering where you don't belong. I prefer to be left alone, away from the meddling of outsiders."
msgstr "[嘟囔] 迷路了？那是你自找的，亂闖禁地。我喜歡獨處，不受外人干擾。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_30:0
msgid "I understand, and I'm really sorry. I promise I'll leave as soon as you point me in the right direction."
msgstr "我明白了，真的很抱歉。只要你指引方向，我保證立刻離開。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_40
msgid "[Grinning wickedly] That is easy. Go outside and far away. As fast as possible."
msgstr "[邪惡地咧嘴笑] 這很簡單。快點走到外面，越遠越好。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_40:0
msgid "Thank you! You're really kind ..."
msgstr "謝謝你！你真好..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_42:0
msgid "... despite what I have always heard about witches in the swamp."
msgstr "……儘管我一直聽說沼澤裡的女巫。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_50
msgid "[Gruffly] Kind? Bah! I simply don't want the likes of you lingering around here."
msgstr "[粗魯地] 親切？哼！我只是不想讓你這種人在這裡徘徊。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_60
msgid "Now, listen carefully, child. I will wait a few minutes before I create fog again."
msgstr "現在，仔細聽著，孩子。我會等幾分鐘再製造霧氣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_62
msgid "Be sure to be out of the area."
msgstr "務必離開該區域。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_62:0
msgid "I appreciate your help. I promise I'll be away for good. But can I ask you something else before I leave?"
msgstr "感謝你的幫助。我保證我會永遠離開。但在我走之前，我還能問你一件事嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_70
msgid "[Sighs] Make it quick, then. I don't have all night."
msgstr "[嘆氣] 那就快點說吧。我可沒空等一整晚。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_70:0
msgid "Why do you live all alone in this swamp? Don't you ever get lonely?"
msgstr "你為何獨自一人住在這沼澤？難道不會感到寂寞嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_80
msgid "Men used to laugh at me. They threw stones at me and finally tried to burn my house."
msgstr "人們曾嘲笑我，朝我丟石頭，最後甚至想燒掉我的家。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_82
msgid "All I want is peace and to enjoy my lovely garden outside."
msgstr "我只想要和平，享受我外面美麗的花園。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_82:0
msgid "You mean the swamp?"
msgstr "你是說那個沼澤？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_82:1
msgid "Eh, yes, your garden is beautiful."
msgstr "嗯，是的，你的花園很美麗。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_82:2
msgid "You want peace and loneliness?"
msgstr "你想要和平與孤獨？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_90
msgid "Yes, it is. At least one person who knows beauty when they see it."
msgstr "是的，確實如此。至少有人一眼就能識美。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_92
msgid "Well, I shall spare you... this time. Now leave my sight and never return!"
msgstr "好吧，我這次就饒了你。現在離開我的視線，永遠別再回來！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_92:0
msgid "It was sort of nice to meet you."
msgstr "很高興認識你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_100
msgid "Loneliness is a price I'm willing to pay for my solitude."
msgstr "孤獨是我願意為寧靜付出的代價。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_102
msgid "People fear me because of my powers, and I grow weary of their endless superstitions and suspicions. Here, far from any village, I can be myself without interference."
msgstr ""
"人們因我的力量而畏懼，我也厭倦了他們無盡的迷信與猜疑。在這裡，遠離村莊，我可"
"以自在做自己，無需干擾。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_104
msgid "Here I have found peace at last."
msgstr "我終於在這裡找到了安寧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_104:0
msgid "I'm sorry people treat you that way. But maybe if they got to know you, they wouldn't be so afraid."
msgstr "很抱歉別人那樣對待你。但也許如果他們了解你，就不會那麼害怕了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_110
msgid "Bah! Humans will always fear what they don't understand."
msgstr "哼！人類總是害怕他們不懂的東西。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_110:0
msgid "Maybe you are right. Let me think ..."
msgstr "也許你說得對。讓我想想..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_110:1
msgid "Right. And now you should fear me - attack!"
msgstr "沒錯。現在你該怕我了——攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_120
msgid "Hmph, fine. But be quick about it."
msgstr "哼，好吧。但要快點。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_120:0
msgid "Shrink the fog in the north."
msgstr "縮小北方的霧氣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_120:1
msgid "Release the fog."
msgstr "散去迷霧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_130
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_140
msgid "[Eyeing you suspiciously] What?!"
msgstr "[懷疑地盯著你] 什麼？！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_130:0
msgid "People have trouble that the way to Feygard goes through your fog. If you make your fog a little smaller in the north, nobody will bother you anymore."
msgstr ""
"人們因為你的霧氣阻擋了通往妖境的路。如果你把北邊的霧氣縮小一點，就沒人會再打"
"擾你了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_132
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_142
msgid "Hmm. Sounds reasonable."
msgstr "嗯，聽起來合理。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_134
msgid "Agreed. Here child, take these sweets and now begone!"
msgstr "同意。孩子，拿著這些糖果，現在快走吧！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_134:1
msgid "[grumbling] Sweets - I am no kid anymore."
msgstr "[抱怨] 甜食——我已經不是小孩了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_140:0
msgid "People have trouble that the way to Feygard is barred by your fog. No fog on the road, no reason to visit you."
msgstr "人們困擾於通往妖境的路被你的霧氣阻擋。路上無霧，便無理由拜訪你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_142:0
msgid "And being a witch, you can certainly put a spell around your swamp that will distract people from wanting to come here."
msgstr "作為女巫，你當然能施法在你的沼澤周圍，讓人們不想來這裡。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_144
msgid "Swamp! what did you name my beautiful peace of land??"
msgstr "沼澤！你竟然給我這片美麗的土地取了什麼名字？？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_144:0
msgid "Well, what else is it?"
msgstr "那還會是什麼呢？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_144:1
msgid "Uh, garden, I meant."
msgstr "呃，我是說花園。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_150
msgid "A distraction spell. That I didn't think of it myself ..."
msgstr "一個分心魔法。真沒想到是我自己沒想到的……"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_160
msgid "Great. You deserve a reward for that. You may choose one thing from these:"
msgstr "太好了。你值得獎勵。你可以從這些中選擇一樣："

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_160:0
msgid "Gold and jewels"
msgstr "黃金與珠寶"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_160:1
msgid "A vial of healing water from the garden"
msgstr "一瓶來自花園的療癒之水"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_160:2
msgid "Everlasting thankfulness"
msgstr "永恆的感激"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_170
msgid "Here take this stuff. And now go and finally leave me alone."
msgstr "拿去這些東西。現在走吧，別再煩我了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_180
msgid "Well, choose what you want. Of course you'll have to pay for it."
msgstr "那就選你想要的吧。當然，你得付錢。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_190
msgid "You have it. And now go and finally leave me alone. Otherwise I'll turn you into a frog. [Muttering] Here, take this bottle."
msgstr "你拿著吧。現在快走，別再煩我。否則我會把你變成青蛙。[喃喃自語] 來，拿這瓶子。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_192
msgid "Still here? Begone!"
msgstr "還在這裡？快走！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_200
msgid "[Grinning wickedly] I think it's time you learn a lesson, meddling child."
msgstr "[邪惡地咧嘴笑] 我想是時候讓你這個多管閒事的孩子好好上點課了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_210
msgid "The old witch raises her hands, chanting ominously."
msgstr "老巫婆舉起雙手，陰森地吟唱著。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_212
msgid "A curse upon you, little one! May darkness be your companion, and fear be your guide!"
msgstr "詛咒降臨於你，小傢伙！願黑暗伴你左右，恐懼引領你前行！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_212:0
msgid "I won't let you curse me! (Draws the weapon)"
msgstr "我不會讓你詛咒我！(拔出武器)"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_212:1
msgid "I'm sorry, ma'am. Please forgive me."
msgstr "抱歉，女士。請原諒我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_212:2
msgid "Wait! Spare me please. I'll give you ..."
msgstr "等等！請饒了我。我會給你..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_214
msgid "Hahaha! You? Defeat me? We shall see!"
msgstr "哈哈哈！你？打敗我？我們拭目以待！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_220
msgid "Oh, the heroic little braveheart, off to save their own skin."
msgstr "喔，這位英勇的小勇士，正要自保逃命呢。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_222
msgid "What do you offer me?"
msgstr "你能給我什麼？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_222:0
msgid "100 gold coins"
msgstr "100 金幣"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_222:1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_222:2
msgid "My Ring of the Lesser Shadow"
msgstr "我的次級暗影戒指"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_222:3
msgid "A quick death"
msgstr "迅速的死亡"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_226
msgid "Insolence! Just you wait ..."
msgstr "無禮！你等著瞧……"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_228
msgid "I have no need for that. But I will take it nevertheless."
msgstr "我不需要那個，但我還是會拿。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_228:0
msgid "NO! I changed my mind."
msgstr "不！我改主意了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_20_228b
msgid "You don't even have this ring. Don't show off like that!"
msgstr "你連這枚戒指都沒有，別這麼炫耀！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_80
msgid "You again! You promised me peace and solitude!"
msgstr "又是你！你答應過我和平與寧靜！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_90
msgid "Oh - how did you pass through my distraction fence?"
msgstr "喔——你怎麼穿過我的分心籬笆？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_90_10:0
msgid "OK, sorry for disturbing your peace."
msgstr "好的，抱歉打擾你的安寧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_90_10:1
msgid "Can I buy more of your medicinal water?"
msgstr "我可以再買一些你的藥水嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_90_20
msgid "Well, if you promise to finally leave me alone afterwards."
msgstr "好吧，只要你答應之後終於不再打擾我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_90_20:0
msgid "Sure"
msgstr "當然"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swampwitch_board_note_10
msgid "Oh what's this? How unusual!"
msgstr "喔，這是什麼？真奇怪！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_checkkill_10
msgid ""
"This area will never be bullied by the old witch again.\n"
"You take the witch's staff - maybe it will find a good use as a walking stick."
msgstr ""
"這片區域再也不會被那老巫婆欺負了。\n"
"你拿起巫婆的法杖——也許它能當作拐杖派上用場。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_checkkill_20
msgid "The life of this lonely swamp witch was somehow sad. Fortunately for her, it is now over."
msgstr "這位孤獨沼澤女巫的生命，總帶著些許哀傷。幸好，現在一切都結束了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_checkkill_22
msgid "You try not to think about it anymore."
msgstr "你試著不再去想它。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamp_witch_checkkill_24
msgid "But you can't stop your heart from feeling heavy."
msgstr "但你無法阻止心頭沉重。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamphut_oven
msgid "Certainly these two mighty ovens were responsible for the thick fog outside."
msgstr "這兩座強大的爐子無疑是外頭濃霧的元兇。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamphut_oven:0
msgid "I wonder what would happen if I light a fire?"
msgstr "我想知道如果我點火會發生什麼事？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:swamphut_oven_10
msgid "Ah - nice and cozy."
msgstr "啊——真溫暖舒適。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_help_10
msgid "Wait! Hey kid, please help me!"
msgstr "等等！嘿，孩子，請幫幫我！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_1
msgid "Oh good, somebody comes to help me. Hey kid!"
msgstr "喔，好險，有人來幫我。嘿，小子！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_2
msgid "I am Tobby. Please, you must help me."
msgstr "我是托比。請你一定要幫幫我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_2:0
msgid "I am $playername. What can I do for you?"
msgstr "我是 $playername。請問有什麼需要幫忙的？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_3
msgid "I can't seem to find my brother, Sobby. He hasn't been back since he left last year."
msgstr "我似乎找不到我弟弟索比。他自從去年離開後就沒回來過。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_3:0
msgid "Never mind, he will probably not be back too soon."
msgstr "算了，他大概不會那麼快回來。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_10
msgid "My father had sent me to look for him. But I dare not pass the kobolds in the ravine."
msgstr "我父親派我去找他，但我不敢穿過峽谷裡的穴居魔。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_10:0
msgid "You are sure your brother went that way?"
msgstr "你確定你兄弟是往那邊走的？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_12
msgid "Absolutely. Once he was told of a lovely village hidden in the forest to the southeast."
msgstr "當然。他曾聽說東南方森林中藏著一個美麗的村莊。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_14
msgid "Since then not a single day passed when he didn't talk about it."
msgstr "從那時起，他每天都在談論這件事。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_16
msgid "And now he is gone."
msgstr "而他如今已離去。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_16:0
msgid "And you neither dare pass the kobolds, nor tell your father that you give up."
msgstr "你既不敢越過哥布林，也不敢告訴你父親你放棄了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_18
msgid "Well, yes."
msgstr "嗯，是的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_19
msgid "You have come from the south, so you know how to pass these nasty kobolds, right?"
msgstr "你是從南方來的，應該知道怎麼通過這些討厭的哥布林吧？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_19:0
msgid "Well, OK. I'll help you."
msgstr "好吧，我會幫你的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_20
msgid "I am glad you want to help me."
msgstr "我很高興你願意幫助我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_20:0
msgid "Sure thing. We brother-seekers must stand together."
msgstr "當然。我們尋兄者必須團結一致。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_22
msgid "I want to get some provisions from the house, just a second ..."
msgstr "我想從屋子裡拿些補給品，等一下..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_22:0
msgid "Go ahead, I'll wait and when you are ready, you can follow me. We will head south."
msgstr "請便，我會等你，準備好後再跟我走。我們將往南前進。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_22:1
msgid "OK. And tell your father that his rat problem is solved."
msgstr "好。告訴你父親，他的老鼠問題已經解決了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_22:2
msgid "OK. And bring your father this loaf of bread."
msgstr "好。還有，帶這條麵包給你父親。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_30
msgid "Oh, how did you know?"
msgstr "喔，你怎麼知道的？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_30:0
msgid "I just had an inspiration."
msgstr "我剛有個靈感。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_30:1
msgid "Also here, bring him a loaf of bread."
msgstr "這裡也帶他一條麵包來。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby_32
msgid "Now I'm speechless - thank you!"
msgstr "我現在無言以對——謝謝你！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby2
msgid "Ouch, my toes!"
msgstr "哎呀，我的腳趾！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby2:1
msgid "Booh!"
msgstr "嚇！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby2:2
msgid "Go away, or I have to kill you."
msgstr "走開，否則我只能殺了你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby2_1
msgid "No, I can't!"
msgstr "不，我不行！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby2_1:0
msgid "I'll show you - attack!"
msgstr "我來教你——攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby2_1:1
msgid "Then try harder."
msgstr "那就更努力點。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby2_2
msgid "Tobby cried out aloud and ran away like the wind. You monster!"
msgstr "托比大聲喊叫，像風一樣逃跑。你這怪物！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby5_1
msgid "Wow, that was an adventure!"
msgstr "哇，真是一場冒險！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby5_1:0
msgid "Was it? I have got used to such things by now."
msgstr "是嗎？我現在已經習慣這種事了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby5_10
msgid "I think that I'll find Sobby by myself now. Thank you - hope we'll meet again!"
msgstr "我想我現在自己去找索比了。謝謝你——希望我們能再見面！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby6
msgid "Hey $playername - great to see you again!"
msgstr "嘿 $playername，很高興再次見到你！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby6:0
msgid "Tobby? What are you doing here?"
msgstr "托比？你在這裡做什麼？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby6_10
msgid "Thanks to you I have found my brother Sobby."
msgstr "多虧了你，我找到了我的兄弟索比。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby6_10:0
msgid "Two-teeth ... is your brother?!"
msgstr "兩齒……是你的兄弟？！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby6_20
msgid "Well, due to his rat poison he has lost a few things in here ..."
msgstr "嗯，由於他的老鼠藥，他在這裡失去了一些東西..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby6_22
msgid "like his gold, his memory, most of his teeth ..."
msgstr "就像他的金子、他的記憶、大部分的牙齒一樣..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:tobby6_30
msgid "But yes - of course this is Sobby, my brother! Don't you see how we look alike?"
msgstr "但當然——這是索比，我的兄弟！你沒看到我們長得多像嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:fallhaven_coup_62
msgid "Hey, the window won't open. I hope Athamyr has a good excuse for that."
msgstr "嘿，窗戶打不開。希望亞薩米爾有個好理由。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:fallhaven_clothes_coup_20
msgid "Now look what we have found here! The famous Jewel of Fallhaven."
msgstr "看看我們在這裡發現了什麼！著名的墜港鎮寶石。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:fallhaven_clothes_coup_20:0
msgid "Take it."
msgstr "拿去。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:fallhaven_clothes_coup_20:1
msgid "Leave it."
msgstr "算了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:fallhaven_clothes_coup_30
msgid "Softly, softly now. We don't want to rush the tailor... Got it."
msgstr "輕手輕腳的。我們可不想催促裁縫……明白了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:fallhaven_clothes_coup_40
msgid "Great. Now let's leave quickly."
msgstr "太好了。現在快走吧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:boat0
msgid "Hi kid. You look curious. Want to try boating?"
msgstr "嗨，小朋友。你好奇嗎？想試試划船嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:boat0:1
msgid "No, I rather stay dry."
msgstr "不，我寧願保持乾燥。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:boat0_a
msgid "I would let you for 10 pieces of gold."
msgstr "我願意以10塊金幣放你走。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:boat0_a:1
msgid "Eh, I have changed my mind."
msgstr "嗯，我改主意了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:boat0_5a
msgid "The boat seems to have a leak!"
msgstr "船似乎漏水了！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:boat0_5a:0
msgid "Oh no. I can't swim."
msgstr "糟了，我不會游泳。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:boat0_5a:1
msgid "Why always me?!"
msgstr "為什麼總是我？！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:boat0_9a
msgid "Phew, I almost drowned in that puddle!"
msgstr "呼，差點就淹死在那個水坑裡！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_initial_phrase
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_start
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_odilia_start
msgid "Thank you for rescuing us earlier!"
msgstr "感謝你之前救了我們！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_initial_phrase:0
msgid "You're welcome, but I was hoping for more than gratitude."
msgstr "不客氣，但我希望得到的不只是感謝。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_initial_phrase:1
msgid "You're welcome, but I wanted to talk about the \"Feydelight\" again."
msgstr "不客氣，但我想再談談「妖精之光」。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_initial_phrase:2
msgid "I am wondering, is my Feydelight ready yet?"
msgstr "我在想，我的費伊之光準備好了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_1
msgid "If a reward is what your after, then a reward you shall have."
msgstr "如果你想要獎勵，那你就會得到獎勵。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_1:0
msgid "So exciting! I can't wait. Let me have it."
msgstr "真令人興奮！我等不及了。快給我吧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_1:1
msgid "Yes, ma'am. Please."
msgstr "是，女士。請。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_2_rude
msgid "Well, maybe with that attitude, you don't derserve one?"
msgstr "嗯，也許你這種態度，根本不配擁有一個？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_2_rude:0
msgid "I'm sorry. You see, I'm just in love with the new stuff."
msgstr "抱歉啦。我就是太愛那些新玩意兒了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_2_nice
msgid "Oh, how polite."
msgstr "哦，真有禮貌。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_3
msgid "Do you know what a \"Feydelight\" is?"
msgstr "你知道什麼是「妖精之光」嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_3:0
msgid "No. Should I?"
msgstr "不。我要嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_3:1
msgid "Whatever happened to my reward? Thanks for nothing."
msgstr "我的獎勵到底怎麼了？一點用都沒有。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_4
msgid "Well, you see? I make them. Not to brag, but I am in fact, the best baker in Feygard."
msgstr "你看到了吧？是我做的。不是自誇，我可是妖境最棒的烘焙師。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_4:0
msgid "But we aren't in Feygard."
msgstr "但我們不在妖境。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_feygard_1
msgid "[With a not so appreciative look on here face...] Oh, sometimes I miss that magnificent place so much. Though, I am happier here."
msgstr ""
"【臉上帶著不太感激的表情……】喔，有時我真的很想念那個壯麗的地方。不過，我在這"
"裡更快樂。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_feygard_1:0
msgid "I've never been there, so tell me, is it as great as I've been told?"
msgstr "我從未去過，那裡真的像我聽說的那麼棒嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_feygard_2
msgid "I've not the words to begin to describe its magnificence."
msgstr "我無法用言語形容它的壯麗。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_5
msgid "Let's get back to talking about those Feydelights."
msgstr "讓我們繼續談談那些妖精美味。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_5:0
msgid "You said that you bake them, but what is a \"feydelight\"?"
msgstr "你說你會烤它們，但「妖精點心」是什麼？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_6
msgid "Child, they are a delicious fig pie enjoyed by most Feygardians as an after dinner delicacy, often reserved for holidays and other celebrations."
msgstr ""
"孩子，它們是大多數妖境人喜愛的美味無花果派，作為餐後甜點，常在節日和其他慶典"
"時享用。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_6:0
msgid "Is that my reward? A fig pie?"
msgstr "那就是我的獎勵？無花果派？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_7
msgid "Well, of course. But there is a problem."
msgstr "當然沒錯。但有個問題。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_7:0
msgid "Oh, I wouldn't expect otherwise."
msgstr "喔，我本就不會期待別的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_7:1
msgid "Why is it?"
msgstr "為什麼會這樣？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_8
msgid "Well, as you are aware, we've been captive for so long. But what you are not aware of, is that while gone, all of my supplies have either gone rotten or been stolen."
msgstr ""
"嗯，如你所知，我們被囚禁已久。但你不知道的是，在我不在的這段時間裡，我所有的"
"物資不是腐壞了，就是被偷走了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_9
msgid "I need supplies. Ingredients to be more specific. I need eleven things, but six unique ingredients."
msgstr "我需要補給品。更確切地說，是材料。我需要十一樣東西，但只有六種獨特的材料。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_10
msgid "Yes. You need to get me some dough, two eggs, butter, honey and five Feygard fig fruits. I also need a bottle of wine. A splash for the pie and the rest of the bottle is for me. Oh don't forget, the figs cannot be found anywhere near those savages to the south."
msgstr ""
"是的。你需要幫我弄些麵團、兩顆蛋、奶油、蜂蜜和五顆妖境無花果。我還需要一瓶酒"
"。派裡用一點，剩下的給我喝。喔，別忘了，無花果可不能在南方那些野蠻人附近找到"
"。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_10:0
msgid "Dough! Where am I supposed to find dough?"
msgstr "錢！我該去哪裡找錢？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_10:1
msgid "I've been across a great amount of Dhayavar and I've not seen honey anywhere."
msgstr "我走遍了大部分的達亞瓦爾，卻沒見過蜂蜜。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_10:2
msgid "Where can I find butter?"
msgstr "我在哪裡可以找到奶油？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_11
msgid "Well, Brightport is known for its wondeful bakeries. I would start there. Of course, you could get some in Feygard too. But you need to seek out a baker."
msgstr ""
"嗯，光明港以其美味的麵包店聞名。我會從那裡開始。當然，你在妖境也能買到。但你"
"得找個麵包師傅。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_11:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_12_bee:0
msgid "OK, but what about..."
msgstr "好吧，但那..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_12
msgid "How about trying a beekeeper? Geez, you are not the smartest are you?"
msgstr "試試養蜂人怎麼樣？天啊，你真不聰明嘛？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_12:0
msgid "You know what? Now that you mention it, I have met a beekeeper before. But where? Anyway, what about..."
msgstr "你知道嗎？既然你提起，我確實見過一位養蜂人。但在哪裡呢？不管了，那..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_12:1
msgid "OK, but where do I find a beekeeper?"
msgstr "好，但我在哪裡可以找到養蜂人？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_13
msgid "Try a bakery. They always need butter."
msgstr "試試麵包店。他們總是需要奶油。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_start
msgid "Thank you for rescuing us earlier! I would have done it myself but..."
msgstr "謝謝你剛才救了我們！我本來想自己動手，但..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_start:0
msgid "You are pathetic?"
msgstr "你真可憐？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_start:1
msgid "You did not have The Shadow with you."
msgstr "你身邊沒有暗影。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_start:2
msgid "What about the state of your house? It's a mess now."
msgstr "你的房子狀況如何？現在一團糟。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_rude
msgid "Now watch it, kid!"
msgstr "小心點，孩子！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_shadow
msgid "The Shadow? You don't believe in that nonsense, do you?"
msgstr "暗影？你不會相信那種胡說八道吧？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_shadow:1
msgid "Me? No way! I was just kidding. Glory be to Feygard."
msgstr "我？才不呢！我只是開玩笑。榮耀歸於妖境。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:glory_be_to_feygard
msgid "Glory be to Feygard."
msgstr "榮耀歸於妖境。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_start:0
msgid "It was my pleasure!"
msgstr "不勝榮幸！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_start:1
msgid "Well, it was fun after all."
msgstr "嗯，畢竟還挺有趣的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_start:2
msgid "Right back to the garden I see?"
msgstr "看來你又回到花園了？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_fun
msgid "Is that what you do?"
msgstr "你就是這樣做的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_fun_2
msgid "You kill just for the thrill?"
msgstr "你殺人只是為了刺激？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_fun_2:0
msgid "Hah, that rhymes."
msgstr "哈，這押韻了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_fun_2:1
msgid "Maybe, but as an adventurer, I like to help where I can."
msgstr "也許吧，但作為冒險者，我喜歡盡我所能幫忙。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier
msgid "I see, but with those skills of yours, you should train to be a Feygard soldier."
msgstr "我明白，但以你的技能，應該訓練成為妖境士兵。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier:0
msgid "Train? I don't need Feygard soldier training. I am already stronger than them. "
msgstr "訓練？我不需要妖境士兵的訓練。我已經比他們強了。 "

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier:1
msgid "Oh, that would be my dream job. Protecting the citizens of Dhayavar!"
msgstr "喔，那會是我的夢想工作。保護達亞瓦爾的市民！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier_2
msgid "[While laughing uncontrollably] But you are just a kid?"
msgstr "[笑得停不下來] 可你不過是個孩子？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier_2:0
msgid "Um, did you already forget what I can do?"
msgstr "嗯，你已經忘了我能做什麼了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier_2a
msgid "Well, when you get a little bit older, you can move to Feygard and attend their soldier training school."
msgstr "嗯，等你長大一點，就可以搬到妖境，參加他們的士兵訓練學校。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier_2a:0
msgid "Wait. There's a school for learning to be a soldier?"
msgstr "等等。這裡有學習成為士兵的學校？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier_2a2
msgid "Of course there is."
msgstr "當然有。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_soldier_2a2:0
msgid "Wow! What an amazing place Feygard must be."
msgstr "哇！妖境一定是個令人驚嘆的地方。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_start
msgid "We are indebted to you now. Your heroism will never be forgotten by the members of this tiny village."
msgstr "我們現在欠你一份人情。這個小村莊的居民永遠不會忘記你的英勇事蹟。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_start:0
msgid "Why do you live in this \"tiny village\" anyway?"
msgstr "你為什麼要住在這個「小村莊」？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_1
msgid "That is indeed an excellent question."
msgstr "這確實是一個很好的問題。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_2
msgid "Let me explain."
msgstr "讓我解釋。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_2:0
msgid "Please, go ahead."
msgstr "請便。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_3
msgid "You see, all eight of us were born and raised in the glorious city of Feygard. In fact, we grew up together. Best friends too! But for various reasons, things started to change for us."
msgstr ""
"你看，我們八個人都是在光榮的費格爾出生長大的。事實上，我們是一起長大的。也是"
"最好的朋友！但因為各種原因，我們的關係開始改變。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_3:0
msgid "Really? I am intrigued to hear more."
msgstr "真的嗎？我很想聽更多。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_4
msgid "Well, I don't want to speak for everyone else, but for Theodora and I, we began to desire a quieter, more laid back lifestyle."
msgstr ""
"嗯，我不想替其他人說話，但對我和西奧多拉來說，我們開始渴望更安靜、悠閒的生活"
"方式。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_4:0
msgid "That makes sense. But what about the others?"
msgstr "這倒說得通。但其他人呢？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_4:1
msgid "But do you ever miss it? I mean, if Feygard is so glorious, then you must miss it?"
msgstr "但你會想念它嗎？我的意思是，如果妖境那麼美好，你一定會想念吧？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_5
msgid "Well, like I said before, I don't want to talk for them, but Osric is my best friend, so I know he longed for the days he could raise a garden and live off the land."
msgstr ""
"嗯，就像我之前說的，我不想替他們說話，但奧斯里克是我最好的朋友，所以我知道他"
"渴望能有一天種植花園，靠土地生活。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_miss_feygard
msgid "Oh, I do miss it a lot. Well, I miss most of it a lot. I miss my family. I miss my old customers coming into my market."
msgstr ""
"喔，我真的很想念。嗯，大部分我都很想念。我想念我的家人。我想念老顧客來我的市"
"場。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_miss_feygard:0
msgid "\"Most of it\"?"
msgstr "「大部分嗎？」"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_miss_feygard_2
msgid "Yeah. I don't miss the noise and the hustle and bustle of the city at all hours of the day. It gets tiresome."
msgstr "是啊。我一點也不懷念城市裡全天候的喧囂與忙碌，真讓人疲憊。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theobald_miss_feygard_2:0
msgid "Thank you for that. It really helped to hear about Feygard from one of its citizens."
msgstr "謝謝你。能聽一位妖境居民談論妖境，真的很有幫助。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine
msgid "Would you like to take a look around the well?"
msgstr "你想要看看這口井嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine:0
msgid "No. I don't have time for kid's games. I am not a kid anymore, afterall."
msgstr "不，我沒時間玩小孩子的遊戲。我已經不是小孩了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine:1
msgid "Yes. What would it hurt if I did?"
msgstr "是啊。我這麼做會有什麼壞處嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine_1
msgid "As you look around, you say to yourself..."
msgstr "當你環顧四周時，你心想..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine_1:0
msgid "There's nothing here. I should go."
msgstr "這裡什麼都沒有。我該走了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine_1:1
msgid "This well seems oddly intact compared to the rest of the village. I wonder what's at the bottom of it?"
msgstr "這口井看起來比村子其他地方還完整。我想知道井底有什麼？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine_2
msgid "You notice some scattered items around the well, as if someone has been throwing things down. Do you want to throw something into the well?"
msgstr "你注意到井周圍散落著一些物品，彷彿有人丟東西下去。你想丟些什麼進井裡嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine_2:0
msgid "No. Why would I want to play a kids game?"
msgstr "不會吧，我為什麼要玩小朋友的遊戲？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_examine_2:1
msgid "I hope this doesn't come back to hurt me somehow..."
msgstr "我希望這不會以某種方式反過來害我..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something
msgid "You are thinking to yourself now. Trying to decide what you want to throw down into the well..."
msgstr "你現在正在思考。試著決定想丟進井裡的是什麼..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something:0
msgid "[Throw a rock into the well]"
msgstr "[丟石頭進井裡]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something:1
msgid "[Throw an Oegyth Crystal]"
msgstr "[投擲一顆奧伊斯水晶]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something:2
msgid "[Throw Glass gem]"
msgstr "[丟擲玻璃寶石]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something:3
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_2:3
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_3:3
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_4:1
msgid "[Throw gold coin]"
msgstr "[丟擲金幣]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something:4
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_2:4
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_3:4
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_4:2
msgid "I have nothing else that I am willing to throw down there."
msgstr "我沒有其他願意丟下去的東西了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_rock
msgid "Bah! Rock no good! Why throw rock at Gamjee?"
msgstr "哼！石頭沒用！為什麼要丟石頭打甘吉？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_oegyth
#: _crystal
msgid "Glowing thing... pretty, but useless! Gamjee no care for it!"
msgstr "發光的東西……漂亮，但沒用！甘吉不在乎它！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_glass_gem
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_psg
msgid "Very shiny! Sparkly! But still not make Gamjee happy!"
msgstr "非常閃亮！閃閃發光！但仍然無法讓甘吉開心！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_coin
msgid "Shiny coin? Gamjee not need your shiny! Keep your gold!"
msgstr "閃亮的硬幣？甘吉不需要你的閃亮！留著你的金幣吧！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_2
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_3
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_4
msgid "You are thinking to yourself now. Trying to decide what else you want to throw down into the well..."
msgstr "你現在正在自言自語，試圖決定還想往井裡丟些什麼……"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_2:0
msgid "[Throw a leather boot into the well]"
msgstr "[把一隻皮靴丟進井裡]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_2:1
msgid "[Throw an Ruby gem]"
msgstr "[丟擲紅寶石]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_2:2
msgid "[Throw Polished gem]"
msgstr "[投擲拋光寶石]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_leather_boot
msgid "A foot thing? What Gamjee do with this? You silly!"
msgstr "腳的東西？甘吉拿這個做什麼？你真傻！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_ruby_gem
msgid "Red glass thingy? Hmmm... pretty, but not impress Gamjee!"
msgstr "紅色玻璃東西？嗯……漂亮，但不讓甘吉印象深刻！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_polished_gem
msgid "Shiny gem! Nice, but not enough for Gamjee!"
msgstr "閃亮的寶石！不錯，但對甘吉來說還不夠！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_coin_2
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_coin_3
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_coin_4
msgid "Again, shiny coin? Gamjee not need your shiny trash! Keep your gold!"
msgstr "又是閃亮的硬幣？甘吉不需要你的閃亮垃圾！留著你的金幣吧！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_3:0
msgid "[Throw a piece of rotten meat into the well]"
msgstr "[丟一塊腐爛的肉進井裡]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_3:1
msgid "[Throw an Sharpened gem]"
msgstr "[投擲一顆銳利的寶石]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_3:2
msgid "[Throw Polished sparkling gem]"
msgstr "[投擲拋光閃亮寶石]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_rotten_meat
msgid "Ugh! Stinky meat! Gamjee do want! But you rude!"
msgstr "噁！臭肉！甘吉想要！但你很沒禮貌！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_something_4:0
msgid "[Throw a bone into the well]"
msgstr "[丟骨頭進井裡]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_sharpened_gem
msgid "Sharp gem? What Gamjee do with this? You no make sense!"
msgstr "尖銳的寶石？甘吉拿這個做什麼？你講不通！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_throw_bone
msgid "Bone?! You mock Gamjee?! Me had enough! Die you will."
msgstr "骨頭？！你在嘲笑甘吉？！我受夠了！你必死無疑。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_map_change
msgid "Suddenly, a powerful force grabs you and drags you down into the darkness of the well. You find yourself dazed, confused in a dank, underground cavern while bleeding from what feels like every part of your body."
msgstr ""
"突然，一股強大的力量抓住你，將你拖入井底的黑暗中。你感到眩暈，在一個陰暗的地"
"下洞穴中迷惑不解，身體各處似乎都在流血。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_odilia_start:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_start:0
msgid "How did the troll manage to capture all of you without anyone noticing?"
msgstr "那個巨魔怎麼能在沒人發現的情況下抓到你們所有人？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_odilia_start:1
msgid "What about you? How are you doing?"
msgstr "你呢？你過得如何？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_odilia_explain_capture
msgid "The well was enchanted. We felt a strange compulsion to visit it, especially when alone."
msgstr "那口井被施了魔法。我們感到一種奇異的衝動，尤其是獨自一人時，更想去拜訪它。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_odilia_explain_capture:0
msgid "Enchanted, how?"
msgstr "被施了魔法，怎麼回事？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_odilia_explain_capture_1
msgid "The well has been enchanted by the troll. Anyone who draws water from it feels an inexplicable compulsion to keep returning."
msgstr "這口井被巨魔施了魔法。任何從中取水的人都會感到一種莫名的衝動，想要不斷回來。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_odilia_explain_capture_1:0
msgid "And you were one to draw water from the well?"
msgstr "你竟然還會從井裡汲水？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_odilia_explain_capture_2
msgid "Yes and every night, I would awake to find myself at the well with no memory of how I got there."
msgstr "是的，每晚我都會醒來，發現自己在井邊，卻完全不記得怎麼到那裡的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_odilia_explain_capture_3
msgid "Yes. This happened many times before that thing finally got me."
msgstr "是的。在那東西終於抓到我之前，這種事發生過很多次。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_odilia_explain_capture_3:0
msgid "Well, you are safe now."
msgstr "嗯，你現在安全了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_start
msgid "Thank you! Thank you! We men tried to rescue our wives, but you succeeded. Thank you!"
msgstr "謝謝你！謝謝你！我們男人試圖救出妻子，但你成功了。謝謝！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_start:1
msgid "What about the state of your village? How will you repair it?"
msgstr "你的村莊狀況如何？你打算怎麼修復？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_1
msgid "Once the women were taken, the troll mimicked their voices, calling out to us men. We thought our wives needed help, but it was a trap."
msgstr ""
"當婦女被帶走後，巨魔模仿她們的聲音，呼喚我們男人。我們以為妻子需要幫助，卻中"
"了圈套。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_1:0
msgid "Scary."
msgstr "可怕。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_2
msgid "Each of us was lured by what we thought were our loved ones. By the time we realized the truth, it was too late."
msgstr "我們每個人都被以為是摯愛之人所引誘。當我們察覺真相時，已經太遲了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_2:0
msgid "But after one of you men was grabbed, how did the last two of you stll fall for this trap?"
msgstr "但你們其中一人被抓後，剩下兩人怎麼還會落入這陷阱？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_3
msgid "Each of us was taken silently and swiftly. By the time we realized something was wrong, it was too late."
msgstr "我們每個人都被悄無聲息且迅速地帶走。當我們意識到有異狀時，已經太遲了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_3:0
msgid "I guess that makes some sense."
msgstr "我想這也說得通。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_1_1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_1_2
msgid "As you begin to traverse the tunnels, the dim light and damp air create an eerie atmosphere. Suddenly, you stop in your tracks."
msgstr ""
"當你開始穿越隧道時，昏暗的光線和潮濕的空氣營造出詭異的氛圍。突然，你停下了腳"
"步。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_1_1:0
msgid "[Thinking] Did I just hear... voices? No, it must be the concussion... or just the echoes playing tricks on me."
msgstr "[思考中] 我剛剛聽到……聲音了嗎？不，肯定是腦震盪……或者只是回聲在作祟。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_1_2:0
msgid "[Thinking] Did I just hear... voices? No, it's just the echoes playing tricks on me."
msgstr "[思考中] 我剛剛聽到...聲音了嗎？不，只是回聲在捉弄我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_2_1
msgid "You press on, the voices you thought you heard earlier seem to be growing louder now. It's hard to tell if they're real or just a figment of your imagination."
msgstr ""
"你繼續前進，先前以為聽到的聲音似乎越來越大聲。很難分辨它們是真實的還是你想像"
"出來的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_2_1:0
msgid "There it is again... I can't be imagining this, can I? I need to focus."
msgstr "又出現了……我不可能是在幻想吧？我得集中精神。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_2_2
msgid "We have to find a way out... this can't be the end for us."
msgstr "我們必須找到出路……這不可能是我們的終點。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_2_3
msgid "Stay calm, someone will come for us. We must have hope."
msgstr "保持冷靜，總有人會來救我們。我們必須抱有希望。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_2_4
msgid "Do you hear that? I think someone's coming..."
msgstr "你聽到了嗎？我覺得有人來了..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_hear_voices_2_4:0
msgid "[Thinking] They're real! I must be getting closer to whoever these people are. I need to hurry."
msgstr "[思考] 他們是真的！我一定快接近這些人了。我得快點。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_discover_villagers_1
msgid "You enter a larger cavern, the air thick with moisture and the scent of earth. The tunnel opens up to reveal a vast room, dimly lit by glowing fungi on the walls."
msgstr ""
"你進入一個更大的洞穴，空氣中充滿濕氣和泥土的氣味。隧道開闊，露出一個廣闊的房"
"間，牆上發光的真菌微微照亮。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_discover_villagers_1:0
msgid "This must be it... the source of those voices."
msgstr "這一定是……那些聲音的來源。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_discover_villagers_2
msgid "As you step further into the room, you notice a large pit in the center, deep below the surface. The voices are clearer now, unmistakably human and filled with fear and hope."
msgstr ""
"當你走進房間更深處時，注意到中央有一個深不見底的大坑。聲音變得更清晰，無疑是"
"人聲，充滿恐懼與希望。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_discover_villagers_2:0
msgid "What's this? There are people down there!"
msgstr "這是什麼？那裡有人！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_discover_villagers_3
msgid "Look! Someone's here! Help us!"
msgstr "看！有人來了！救救我們！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_discover_villagers_4
msgid "We're down here! Please, you have to get us out!"
msgstr "我們在這裡！拜託，請你一定要救我們出去！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_discover_villagers_5
msgid "Thank you Feygard, they have found us!"
msgstr "謝謝妖境，他們找到我們了！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_discover_villagers_5:0
msgid "[Thinking] I really need to talk to these people."
msgstr "[思考] 我真的需要和這些人談談。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_1
msgid "Please! We need your help."
msgstr "拜託！我們需要你的幫助。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_1:0
msgid "I can see that."
msgstr "我看得出來。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_2
msgid "Wait, you are not a Feygard soldier!"
msgstr "等等，你不是妖境士兵！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_2:1
msgid "No, I am better."
msgstr "不，我比較強。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_3
msgid "No matter! We need you to find a way to free us."
msgstr "沒關係！我們需要你想辦法救我們出來。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_3:0
msgid "How?"
msgstr "怎麼做？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_3:1
msgid "Who are you people?"
msgstr "你們是誰？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_3:2
msgid "How did you guys get down here?"
msgstr "你們怎麼下來這裡的？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_3:3
msgid "How long have you people been down here?"
msgstr "你們在這裡待了多久？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_4
msgid "Go kill the giant troll that is holding us here. Then come back here to free us."
msgstr "去殺掉那個困住我們的巨魔。然後回來解救我們。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:troll_hollow_godelieve_no
msgid "What?! No, no, no. I will not talk details right now."
msgstr "什麼？！不，不，不。我現在不會談細節。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_post_troll_1
msgid "Did you find something to free us from this pit?"
msgstr "你找到什麼能讓我們脫離這個坑嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_post_troll_1:0
msgid "Matter of fact, I have. But what I have will require a lot of effort on you guys' end."
msgstr "事實上，我有。但我所擁有的需要你們付出很多努力。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_post_troll_1:1
msgid "Not yet, but I'm working on it."
msgstr "還沒，但我正在努力。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_post_troll_rescue_1:0
msgid "It's a rope. I will tie one end to this rock here and throw down the other end to you. I hope you guys have the strength to do it."
msgstr ""
"這是一條繩子。我會把一端綁在這塊石頭上，另一端丟給你們。希望你們有力氣拉上來"
"。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_post_troll_rescue_2
msgid "We'll do anything. Please go ahead and drop the rope."
msgstr "我們願意付出一切。請放下繩索吧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_post_troll_rescue_2:0
msgid "[Tie the rope to the rock]"
msgstr "[將繩子綁在岩石上]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_post_troll_rescue_3
msgid "We are finally free!"
msgstr "我們終於自由了！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_1
msgid "Human, why you come here? Gamjee no hurt you if you leave now."
msgstr "人類，你為何來此？甘吉若你現在離開，絕不傷你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_1:0
msgid "I'm just exploring. Who are you, and why are you here?"
msgstr "我只是來探險的。你是誰？為什麼會在這裡？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_1:0
msgid "I've found the people you captured. You need to let them go."
msgstr "我找到了你抓的人。你得放他們走。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_1:1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_player_left_after_agreeing_to_help:0
msgid "I want to help you and the villagers."
msgstr "我想幫助你和村民們。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_2
msgid "Gamjee guard well. Humans come, take Gamjee's well, build village. They no ask. They just take. Gamjee scared. Need protect well. You help Gamjee?"
msgstr ""
"甘吉守護水井。人類來，搶走甘吉的水井，建村莊。他們不問，直接搶走。甘吉害怕。"
"需要保護水井。你願意幫助甘吉嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_2:0
msgid "You're afraid they'll come back and take more?"
msgstr "你怕他們會回來搶更多？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_2:1
msgid "I thought I heard somes voices earlier. Have you hurt anybody recently? "
msgstr "我剛才好像聽到有人聲。你最近有傷害過誰嗎？ "

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_peace
msgid "Yes! Humans take all if no stop. Gamjee alone. If you help, tell humans Gamjee no bad. Maybe they listen. Maybe they share well, no fight. You help, no need for hurt."
msgstr ""
"是的！人類如果不阻止會全拿走。只有甘吉一個人。如果你幫忙，告訴人類甘吉沒壞心"
"。也許他們會聽，也許會公平分享，不會打架。你幫忙，就不用受傷。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_peace:0
msgid "I understand. I'll help you find a peaceful solution."
msgstr "我明白。我會幫你尋找和平的解決方法。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_attack
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_fight
msgid "No! Gamjee protect! If humans come back, they take all. Gamjee alone, scared."
msgstr "不！甘吉保護！如果人類回來，他們會拿走一切。甘吉一個人，好害怕。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_attack:0
msgid "I don't believe you! I can't take that risk. This ends now"
msgstr "我不相信你！我不能冒那個險。現在就結束。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_killed_wo_villagers_known
msgid "Gamjee has grasped his last breath when you realize that you really need to follow those voices."
msgstr "當你意識到你真的需要跟隨那些聲音時，甘吉已經斷了最後一口氣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_killed_villagers_known
msgid "Gamjee has grasped his last breath and now it's time to rescue those people."
msgstr "甘吉已斷氣，現在是時候拯救那些人了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_2
msgid "Captured? No, no! Gamjee protect them! Humans take Gamjee's well, build village. They no ask. They just take. Gamjee keep them safe here. You see, they not hurt."
msgstr ""
"被抓了？不，不！甘吉保護他們！人類奪走甘吉的水井，建村莊。他們不問，直接拿走"
"。甘吉在這裡保護他們安全。你看，他們沒受傷。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_2:0
msgid "Keeping them in a pit isn't protecting them. It's imprisoning them."
msgstr "把他們關在坑裡不是保護，而是囚禁。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_3
msgid "No! Listen! Humans come, take Gamjee's well, leave Gamjee with nothing. Gamjee scared. If Gamjee let them go, they come back, take well again. They no understand, well is life for Gamjee. Please, you help. Tell humans Gamjee no bad. Maybe they listen. Maybe they share well, no fight. You help, no need for hurt."
msgstr ""
"不！聽我說！人類來了，搶走甘吉的水井，留甘吉一無所有。甘吉害怕。如果甘吉放他"
"們走，他們還會回來，再搶水井。他們不懂，水井是甘吉的命。請你幫忙。告訴人類甘"
"吉沒惡意。也許他們會聽，也許會共享水井，不再爭鬥。你幫忙，就不用受傷了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_3:0
msgid "I see. You acted out of fear and desperation. I'll help you find a peaceful solution."
msgstr "我明白了。你是出於恐懼和絕望行事。我會幫你尋找和平的解決方法。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_3:1
msgid "It's time to make me righteous!"
msgstr "是時候讓我變得正義了！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_1
msgid "You help Gamjee? Humans no hurt?"
msgstr "你幫助甘吉？人類沒受傷？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_1:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_1:1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_1:2
msgid "I'll do what I can. Let's talk to the villagers."
msgstr "我會盡力而為。讓我們去和村民談談。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_2
msgid "Let Gamjee call human with magic water."
msgstr "讓甘吉用魔法水召喚人類。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_2:0
msgid "OK. Now that I have you two together, let's talk about how you guys can reach a compromise and share the well water."
msgstr "好。既然你們兩個都在這裡，讓我們來談談如何達成妥協，共享井水。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_4
msgid "Why should we trust him? He's been keeping us captive!"
msgstr "我們為何要信任他？他一直囚禁著我們！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_4:0
msgid "Gamjee is afraid you'll take the well. He wants to protect it."
msgstr "甘吉擔心你會帶走水井，他想保護它。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_5
msgid "And what about us? We need water too."
msgstr "那我們呢？我們也需要水。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_6
msgid "Gamjee not want hurt. Humans need water. Gamjee need too."
msgstr "甘吉不想傷害。人類需要水。甘吉也需要。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_6:0
msgid "Is there a way you can share the well? Maybe take turns using it?"
msgstr "有辦法共享這口井嗎？或許輪流使用？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_7
msgid "We can agree to that. As long as Gamjee doesn't threaten us anymore."
msgstr "我們可以同意。只要甘吉不再威脅我們。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_8
msgid "Gamjee promise. No hurt. Protect well. Humans share. No fight."
msgstr "甘吉保證。不傷害。好好保護。人類共享。不打架。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_8:0
msgid "Alright. Let's make this work."
msgstr "好吧。讓我們來解決這件事。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_8:1
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_9:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_9:1
msgid "So our business here is done?"
msgstr "那我們的事就這樣結束了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_9
msgid "You human, go back village now."
msgstr "你這人類，現在回村子去。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_10_no_ac
msgid "Not same. Take rope, use to free others from pit."
msgstr "不一樣。拿繩子，用來救其他人出坑。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_2a:0
msgid "Let's talk about how you guys can reach a compromise and share the well water."
msgstr "讓我們談談你們如何達成妥協，共享井水。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_no_business
msgid "Why you still here? Leave now."
msgstr "你怎麼還在這？快走。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_compromise_10_oc
msgid "take shiny thing back."
msgstr "把閃亮的東西帶回來。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_osric_1
msgid "Please meet us back to Wexlow Village."
msgstr "請回到威克斯洛村與我們會合。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_osric_1:1
msgid "Wexlow Village? Where's that?"
msgstr "威克斯洛村？那是哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_osric_3
msgid "Didn't you find us after visiting our village and our well?"
msgstr "你不是在拜訪我們的村莊和水井後找到我們的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_well_osric_4
msgid "Yes, that place. I am leaving now. I will see you there."
msgstr "是的，就是那個地方。我現在就出發。到時見。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_cave_key
msgid "Too bad this tree is in the way."
msgstr "可惜這棵樹擋住了路。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godelieve_1
msgid "Oh, our hero returns to us."
msgstr "喔，我們的英雄回來了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godelieve_1:0
msgid "I'm just happy to see you guys safe."
msgstr "我只是很高興看到你們平安無事。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godelieve_2
msgid "I'm just happy to curl up with Godwin in our own bed tonight."
msgstr "我只要今晚能和高德溫一起窩在我們自己的床上就很開心了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godelieve_generic
msgid "It's very nice to see you again."
msgstr "很高興再次見到你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godelieve_generic:0
msgid "Would it be OK with you if I slept here? I'm pretty tired."
msgstr "你介意我在這裡睡一晚嗎？我真的很累。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_1
msgid "Have you by any chance seen my wedding ring? Oh my, Godelieve is going to kill me when she sees it's missing."
msgstr "你有沒有看到我的結婚戒指？天啊，戈德莉芙看到戒指不見了肯定會殺了我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_1:0
msgid "What does it look like?"
msgstr "它長什麼樣？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_2
msgid "Um, let me think. Oh, yeah, I remember. It's black, gold and covered in emeralds."
msgstr "嗯，讓我想想。喔，對了，我記得了。它是黑色的，鑲著金邊，還覆蓋著翡翠。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_2:0
msgid "\"Oh, yeah, I remember\"? What? Don't you know what it looks like?"
msgstr "「喔，對，我記得」？什麼？你不知道它長什麼樣嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_2:1
msgid "Actually, this is your lucky day. I have it here."
msgstr "其實，今天是你的幸運日。我這裡正好有。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_3
msgid "Leave me alone. I don't need you questioning me under this stressful situation."
msgstr "別煩我。我在這種壓力下不需要你質疑我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_4
msgid "Your messing with me, right? Give it to me, please."
msgstr "你在跟我開玩笑吧？拜託，把它給我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_4:0
msgid "Sure. Here, it's yours."
msgstr "當然。給你，這是你的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_4:1
msgid "What do you want to give me in exchange for your wife not \"killing you\"?"
msgstr "你想用什麼交換我不「殺了你」？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_take_ring
msgid "Thank you so much! Here take these coins."
msgstr "非常感謝！這些錢幣給你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_5
msgid "Give you? How about 2000 gold coins?"
msgstr "給你？2000金幣如何？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_5:1
msgid "Hey Godelieve, did you hear what happened to Godwin?"
msgstr "嘿，戈德莉芙，你聽說戈德溫發生了什麼事嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_godelieve
msgid "No. What happened?"
msgstr "不。發生了什麼事？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_godelieve:0
msgid "Well, he los..."
msgstr "嗯，他丟了..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_godelieve_2
msgid "NEVER MIND! Godelieve, this kid is being silly. You can go back to whatever it is that you were doing."
msgstr "沒關係！Godelieve，這孩子只是開玩笑。你可以回去繼續做你剛才的事。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_godelieve_2:0
msgid "3000 gold or no ring."
msgstr "3000 金幣，否則不給戒指。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_3k
msgid "Fine! Take the coins you thief."
msgstr "好吧！拿去吧，你這小偷。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_3k:0
msgid "I will put them to good use."
msgstr "我會好好利用它們。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:prevent_walk_into_pit
msgid "What good are you to these people if you're down there with them?"
msgstr "如果你和他們一起掉下去，對這些人有什麼幫助？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:coin_collector_troll_coins
msgid "Ah, these are Enchanted Coins, crafted by ancient wizards who once drew magic from the well's waters. The runes on these coins change patterns, a sign of their magical origin. Such artifacts are rare indeed."
msgstr ""
"啊，這些是附魔硬幣，由古代巫師鑄造，他們曾從井水中汲取魔力。硬幣上的符文會變"
"換圖案，顯示其魔法起源。這類神器確實罕見。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:coin_collector_troll_coins:0
msgid "What can you tell me about their enchantment?"
msgstr "你能告訴我關於他們的附魔嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:coin_collector_troll_coins:1
msgid "Boring."
msgstr "無聊。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:coin_collector_troll_coins_2
msgid "The coins hold a faint echo of the well's enchantment. Though their magic is subtle, they carry the essence of the well's power. As a token of my gratitude for bringing these to me, I offer you this rare artifact in exchange for three of these coins. It is imbued with protective magic, much like these coins."
msgstr ""
"這些硬幣隱約帶有井水的魔力。雖然魔法微弱，卻蘊含著井水的精髓。作為感謝你帶來"
"這些硬幣的回禮，我願以這件稀有神器交換三枚硬幣。它同樣附有保護魔法。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:coin_collector_troll_coins_2:0
msgid "Without knowing more about this \"rare artifact\", I'm afraid that I will have to pass on your offer."
msgstr "在不了解這個「稀有神器」的更多資訊前，恐怕我只能婉拒你的提議。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:coin_collector_troll_coins_2:1
msgid "Umm, I guess I can trust you now."
msgstr "嗯，我想我現在可以信任你了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:coin_collector_troll_coins_3a
msgid "Well, if you change your mind, I will be here."
msgstr "如果你改變主意，我會在這裡。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:coin_collector_troll_coins_3b
msgid "For your effort in retrieving these valuable coins, take this rare artifact. It is a relic from the same era as the coins, crafted with similar enchantments. It will serve you well in your journeys, offering protection and a touch of ancient abilities."
msgstr ""
"感謝你取回這些珍貴的硬幣，請收下這件稀有的神器。它與硬幣同時代，鑲嵌著相似的"
"魔法。旅途中它將保護你，並賦予你古老的力量。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:mean_cat
msgid "Hsss!"
msgstr "嘶！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_initial_phrase
msgid "How can I help you today?"
msgstr "今天有什麼我可以幫忙的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_initial_phrase:0
msgid "What is going on with that cat?"
msgstr "那隻貓到底怎麼了？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_initial_phrase:2
msgid "Do you know why the village of Wexlow is void of people?"
msgstr "你知道為什麼威克斯洛村裡沒有人嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_initial_phrase:3
msgid "I would like to make a purchase, please."
msgstr "我想要購買一些東西。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_1
msgid "Well, you see, he's my guard cat."
msgstr "嗯，你看，他是我的守護貓。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_1:0
msgid "Your guard cat?"
msgstr "你的守護貓？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_2
msgid "Yes. If you attempt to rob me, he'll attack you. Hence he is my guard cat."
msgstr "是的。如果你試圖搶劫我，他會攻擊你。所以他是我的守護貓。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_2:1
msgid "Seriously?"
msgstr "認真的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_3
msgid "No, not seroiusly. He guards my fruits and vegetables."
msgstr "不，真的不是。他是在守護我的水果和蔬菜。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_3:0
msgid "Guards them from what?"
msgstr "保護他們免受什麼？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_4
msgid "I have a business agreement with him. He guards my food from the rats in exchange for a place to sleep."
msgstr "我和他有生意協議。他守護我的食物免受老鼠侵害，換取一個睡覺的地方。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_4:0
msgid "Oh, why didn't you just say so?"
msgstr "喔，為什麼你不早說呢？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_4:1
msgid "Well, he's not holding up his end of the deal, because there's a rat behind your tent right now."
msgstr "嗯，他沒有履行他的承諾，因為你的帳篷後面現在有隻老鼠。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_5
msgid "I wanted to waste your time just as you are doing to my time. Walking up to my business counter asking about my cat! Get lost, kid."
msgstr ""
"我只是想浪費你的時間，就像你浪費我的時間一樣。走到我的櫃檯問我的貓！滾開，小"
"子。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain
msgid "This is my place of business. Right here on the side of Duleian Road."
msgstr "這是我的營業地點。就在杜雷安路旁邊。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain:0
msgid "Why here? There's nothing else here besides you."
msgstr "為什麼在這裡？這裡除了你什麼都沒有。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_2
msgid "Oh, you silly child. This is a very well traveled road. All the people coming and going from and to Feygard. It's a long road and they get hungry."
msgstr ""
"哦，你這個傻孩子。這是一條非常繁忙的道路。所有來往妖境的人都走這條路。路途遙"
"遠，他們會餓的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_2:0
msgid "I am not a child!"
msgstr "我不是小孩！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_2:1
msgid "OK, you sell food. What kind of food?"
msgstr "好，你賣食物。賣什麼種類的食物？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_2:2
msgid "And the fog? No one could take the path anymore."
msgstr "那霧呢？沒有人能再走那條路了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_3
msgid "I sell things that a child such as yourself is most likely not interested in."
msgstr "我賣的東西，小孩像你大概不會感興趣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_3:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_11:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_11a:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_road_closed:0
msgid "I am not a child anymore!!"
msgstr "我已經不是小孩子了！！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_4
msgid "I sell fruits and vegetables."
msgstr "我賣水果和蔬菜。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_4:0
msgid "As an adult, I am interested in seeing what you have."
msgstr "作為成年人，我想看看你有什麼。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_4:1
msgid "Where do you get these fruits and vegetables?"
msgstr "你從哪裡取得這些水果和蔬菜？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_5
msgid "From all over Dhayavar, but mostly from the great farmers in Loneford."
msgstr "來自整個達亞瓦爾，但大多數是來自孤河鎮的偉大農夫。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_5:0
msgid "Oh, yeah. I've seen all of their great farms."
msgstr "喔，對，我看過他們所有優秀的農場。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_5:1
msgid "Loneford, where's that?"
msgstr "隆福德，那是哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_10
msgid "What kind of fog are you talking about?"
msgstr "你說的是什麼樣的霧？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_10:0
msgid "The fog that the witch had created in the swamp, of course."
msgstr "當然是女巫在沼澤中製造的霧氣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_10:1
msgid "The fog further down the road behind the kobolds, of course."
msgstr "當然，是在眼前那些哥布林後方的霧氣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_11
msgid "Are you still afraid of witches or fog, child?"
msgstr "你還害怕女巫或迷霧嗎，孩子？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_11:1
msgid "I was with the witch! Without me the fog would still be there!"
msgstr "我和女巫在一起！沒有我，迷霧還會存在！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_11a
msgid "Are you still afraid of kobolds or fog, child?"
msgstr "你還害怕哥布林或迷霧嗎，孩子？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_11a:1
msgid "I have mastered the fog and survived the kobolds!!"
msgstr "我已掌握迷霧，並在哥布林中倖存！！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_explain_12
msgid "Yes, of course. Calm down, child."
msgstr "是的，當然。冷靜點，孩子。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_road_closed
msgid "Hey, child! You can't go there. You're not ready for the big city of Feygard. Or is Feygard not ready for you?"
msgstr ""
"嘿，孩子！你不能去那裡。你還沒準備好進入妖境大城。還是說，妖境還沒準備好迎接"
"你？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_road_closed_1
msgid "Either way, the road is closed to you."
msgstr "無論如何，這條路對你封閉。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_all_items_1
msgid "Great. I will take them now. But I want to warn you, making this pie will take me a while. Come back later and it will be ready."
msgstr ""
"太好了。我現在就拿。不過我要提醒你，做這個派需要一點時間。晚點再來，它就做好"
"了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_all_items_1:0
msgid "Here, take them all."
msgstr "拿去吧，全都給你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_all_items_2
msgid "Come back later and it will be ready."
msgstr "稍後再來，物品就準備好了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_complete_no
msgid "Sorry, no it is not. Please come back later."
msgstr "抱歉，現在還不行。請稍後再來。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:perciva_int_phrasel
msgid "What are you doing? Help us!"
msgstr "你在做什麼？快幫幫我們！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godelieve_bed
msgid "Of course. Just use the mat over there in the corner."
msgstr "當然。就在角落那邊的墊子上睡吧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_key_bed_not_allowed
msgid "Oh, these sleeping quarters stink so terribly that you don't want to get any closer."
msgstr "這些寢室臭氣熏天，讓人不想靠近。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_welcome
msgid "Ah, greetings, traveler! What brings you to my humble apiary?"
msgstr "啊，旅人，歡迎光臨！是什麼風把你帶到我這小小的蜂場？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_welcome:0
msgid "Hello. Who might you be?"
msgstr "你好。請問你是？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_intro
msgid "I be Leofric, master of bees and their keeper. I tend the hives and harvest their golden treasures"
msgstr "我是利奧弗里克，蜜蜂大師與守護者。我照料蜂巢，採集牠們的金色寶藏。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_intro:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_explain:0
msgid "What exactly do you do here, Leofric?"
msgstr "你到底在這裡做什麼，雷奧弗里克？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_intro:1
msgid "If you're a master of bees, why do you wear a helmet and mask?"
msgstr "既然你是蜜蜂大師，為何還戴著頭盔和面罩？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_job
msgid "I care for the bees, gather their honey and wax, and craft fine goods from their toil. Bees be wondrous creatures, providing both sweet sustenance and warm light."
msgstr ""
"我照料蜜蜂，採集牠們的蜂蜜與蜂蠟，並以牠們的辛勞製作精美物品。蜜蜂是奇妙的生"
"物，既提供甜美的食糧，也帶來溫暖的光芒。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_sell
msgid "Aye, I have many wares to offer. Jars of honey, beeswax and some fine mead. But that's it for now as my supply is lower than normal. Take a look, and see what catches your fancy."
msgstr ""
"是的，我有許多貨品可供選擇。蜂蜜罐、蜂蠟和一些上等蜂蜜酒。但目前庫存較少，就"
"先這些了。看看有什麼合你心意的吧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_sell:0
msgid "Sounds great."
msgstr "聽起來不錯。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:leofric_explain
msgid "Ah, a keen eye you have! The helmet and mask protect me from more than just bee stings. The forest holds dangers aplenty, and it's wise to be prepared. You never know what you might encounter when tending to the hives deep in the woods."
msgstr ""
"啊，你真是眼光敏銳！這頭盔和面罩不僅能防蜂螫。森林中危險重重，做好準備是明智"
"的。當你在深林中照料蜂巢時，永遠不知道會遭遇什麼。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_has_ring
msgid "A crisis has been averted thanks to you."
msgstr "多虧了你，危機已被化解。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_has_ring:0
msgid "You should do a better job protecting that ring."
msgstr "你應該更好地保護那枚戒指。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_12_bee
msgid "I don't know, kid. Somewhere along the Duleian Road? Towards those savages, maybe?"
msgstr "我不知道，孩子。大概是在杜雷安之路的某處？也許是朝那些野蠻人那邊？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:thief_seraphina_helmet_1
msgid "What, do I look like a merchant?"
msgstr "什麼，我看起來像商人嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:thief_seraphina_helmet_2
msgid "Well, I am not. But today is your lucky day."
msgstr "嗯，我可不是。但今天是你的幸運日。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:thief_seraphina_helmet_2:0
msgid "It is?"
msgstr "是嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:thief_seraphina_helmet_3
msgid "Yes. You see, I recently \"acquired\" this \"beauty\" from a dumb guy trying to cross the bridge before you fixed it. Do you want to take a look"
msgstr ""
"是的。你看，我最近「取得」了這個「寶物」，是從一個笨蛋那裡搶來的，他想在你修"
"好橋之前過去。要不要看看？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:thief_seraphina_helmet_3:1
msgid "No, thanks. I'm leaving."
msgstr "不，謝謝。我走了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_1
msgid "Take a peak down the well?"
msgstr "要往井裡瞧一瞧嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_1:0
msgid "Sure. Why not?"
msgstr "當然，為什麼不呢？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_1:1
msgid "That's boring. I need to go now."
msgstr "太無聊了。我現在得走了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_peak
msgid "While staring down into the dark nothingness, you think to yourself..."
msgstr "凝視著黑暗的虛無，你心中暗想..."

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_peak:0
msgid "What is Andor doing right now? I need to find him."
msgstr "安多爾現在在做什麼？我得找到他。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_peak:1
msgid "How deep does this thing go? Let's throw something down there and see if I can hear it hit the bottom."
msgstr "這東西有多深？我們丟點東西下去，看看能不能聽到碰到底部的聲音。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_selector
msgid "What item can you live without?"
msgstr "你能沒有什麼物品活下去？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_selector:0
msgid "[Throw a small rock.]"
msgstr "[丟一顆小石頭。]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_selector:1
msgid "[Throw a piece of animal hair?]"
msgstr "[丟一根動物毛髮？]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_selector:2
msgid "[Toss in a piece of that gross rotten meat.]"
msgstr "[丟進一塊那腐爛噁心的肉。]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_selector:3
msgid "[Lob down an insect shell.]"
msgstr "[丟下昆蟲殼。]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_selector:4
msgid "[Whip an empty flask down there.]"
msgstr "[把空瓶子甩下去。]"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_selector:5
msgid "I have nothing that I want to waste by throwing down there."
msgstr "我沒有什麼想丟下去浪費的東西。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_object
msgid "You are not sure if the faint sound that you think you heard can really tell you anything about determining the depth of the well."
msgstr "你不確定那微弱的聲音是否真的能幫助你判斷井的深度。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_object:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_hair:0
msgid "Let's try and throw something else down there."
msgstr "我們試著丟點別的東西下去吧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_object:1
msgid "This is stupid. I'm leaving now."
msgstr "這真蠢。我現在走。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_hair
msgid "The hair fails to even come close to going down the well as it simply floats in the air and lands on your shoulder."
msgstr "頭髮根本沒能接近井口，只是在空中飄浮，最後落在你的肩膀上。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_hair:1
msgid "That's enough of the kid's games, I'm leaving."
msgstr "小孩子的遊戲夠了，我要走了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_flask
msgid "You hear the flask shattering into a million pieces against what you can only presume are rocks."
msgstr "你聽見藥瓶摔成千百碎片，砸在你只能猜是岩石的東西上。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_flask:0
msgid "Now, that was fun! Let's try something else."
msgstr "真有趣！我們試試別的吧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:loneford_well_script_throw_flask:1
msgid "That's enough of that."
msgstr "夠了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_ip
msgid "Halt!"
msgstr "停下！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_ip:0
msgid "Wait a minute. Don't I know you from somewhere?"
msgstr "等一下。我不是在哪裡見過你嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_halt
msgid "I said \"halt\"!"
msgstr "我說「停下」！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_halt:0
msgid "Yes! I know you. But I am pretty damn sure that I killed you back there [pointing southeast] on the bridge."
msgstr "是的！我認識你。但我很確定我剛剛在那邊[指向東南方]的橋上殺了你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_brother_1
msgid "You killed my brother?!"
msgstr "你殺了我兄弟？！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_brother_1:0
msgid "Yes, it appears so, but I had no choice. You see, he wouldn't get out of my way. Kind of like you."
msgstr "是的，看起來是這樣，但我別無選擇。你知道的，他不肯讓開。就像你一樣。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_brother_2
msgid "I am disheartened and full of rage hearing of this."
msgstr "聽聞此事，我既心灰意冷又怒火中燒。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_brother_2:0
msgid "Well, if it's any consolation, you are about to join him."
msgstr "嗯，如果這能讓你稍感安慰，你也即將與他同行。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_blocker_brother_2:1
msgid "Step aside before I am forced to reunite you two."
msgstr "讓開，否則我將被迫讓你們兩人重聚。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_ip
msgid "I'm so saddened by the loss of my brother, all I can do is stand here starring at these flowers."
msgstr "我為失去兄弟感到無比悲痛，唯有站在這裡凝視這些花朵。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_ip:0
msgid "Why'd you move so quickly?"
msgstr "你為什麼動得這麼快？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_mother_letter_prompt
msgid "On the table, you notice a series of papers. Some appear to be letters. Do you want to be nosy and read them?"
msgstr "桌上有一疊文件，其中一些看起來像是信件。你想偷看一下嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_mother_letter_prompt:0
msgid "I sure do."
msgstr "我當然願意。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_mother_letter_prompt:1
msgid "I better not. It's none of my business."
msgstr "我最好別管。這不關我的事。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_mother_letter
msgid ""
"Dear Theodora,\n"
"\n"
"I've come to visit you again today, but once more, I find your home empty. It's been nearly a month since I last saw you, and my heart grows heavier with each passing day.\n"
"\n"
"Where have you gone, my dear? The village seems so quiet, as if all life has been drawn away. I've knocked on your door, looked through the windows, and even asked the few people I saw on the Duleian Road (do you know Rosmara, the \"fruit lady\"), but no one has seen you or heard a word.\n"
"\n"
"Please, if you find this letter, send word to me at once. I cannot bear the thought of something having happened to you. If you've simply gone away for a time, I understand, but let me know that you are safe. I will return again in a week's time, praying that I find you here.\n"
"\n"
"With all my love,\n"
"Mother"
msgstr ""
"親愛的西奧多拉，\n"
"\n"
"我今天又來看你，但你的家依舊空無一人。自從上次見面已近一個月，我的心隨著日子"
"一天天沉重。\n"
"\n"
"親愛的，你去了哪裡？村莊顯得如此寂靜，彷彿所有生命都被抽走了。我敲過你的門，"
"透過窗戶張望，甚至問過在杜雷安路上遇見的幾個人（你認識「水果女士」羅絲瑪拉嗎"
"？），但沒有人見過你或聽到任何消息。\n"
"\n"
"請你若看到這封信，立刻回信告訴我。我無法承受你出了什麼事的念頭。如果你只是暫"
"時離開，我能理解，但請讓我知道你平安無事。我會在一週後再來，祈禱能在這裡找到"
"你。\n"
"\n"
"滿懷愛意，\n"
"母親"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_godwin_journal_prompt
msgid "As you walk by the table, in the corner of your eye, you catch a glimpse of someone's journal. Maybe you should read the current page?"
msgstr "當你走過桌邊，眼角瞥見某人的日記。或許你該讀讀當前頁面？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_godwin_journal_prompt:0
msgid "And violate someone's privacy? No way!"
msgstr "侵犯別人隱私？絕不可能！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_godwin_journal_prompt:1
msgid "I think I should."
msgstr "我想我應該這麼做。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_godwin_journal
msgid ""
"It's been days since anyone has seen Odilia. At first, we thought she might have gone to visit her sister in Feygard, but she never mentioned leaving. The same happened with Philippa, and now Godelieve too. It's as if they vanished without a trace, all in their sleep. I remember Godelieve looked troubled the night before she disappeared, as though she was fighting some invisible force, but I dismissed it. I should have known something was wrong.\n"
"\n"
"The village feels different now, quieter, emptier. The men are on edge, but we can't make sense of what's happening. The nights are the worst, filled with a heavy silence that chills the bone. I fear for Leofwyn and Theobald, and I can't help but wonder if something in the night is calling to them.\n"
"\n"
"We're losing hope, and I'm terrified of what might happen next.\n"
"\n"
"End Entry"
msgstr ""
"已經好幾天沒有人見過奧迪莉亞了。起初，我們以為她可能去妖境探望她的姊姊，但她"
"從未提過要離開。菲莉帕也是如此，現在連戈德莉芙也消失了。彷彿她們在睡夢中無聲"
"無息地消失了。我記得戈德莉芙消失前一晚看起來很不安，像是在與某種看不見的力量"
"抗爭，但我當時沒放在心上。我早該察覺有異狀。\n"
"\n"
"村子現在感覺不同了，更安靜，也更空蕩。男人們神經緊繃，但我們無法理解發生了什"
"麼。夜晚最糟，充滿令人寒心的沉寂。我擔心利奧芬和西奧巴德，忍不住想知道是否有"
"什麼東西在夜裡召喚他們。\n"
"\n"
"我們正在失去希望，我害怕接下來會發生什麼。\n"
"\n"
"日誌結束"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_godwin_journal:0
msgid "I wonder who these people are?"
msgstr "我想知道這些人是誰？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_cat_rat
msgid "Oh, my!"
msgstr "哎呀！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_cleanup
msgid "Can you believe it? It'll take weeks to clear out all the cobwebs. It's like the spiders moved in the moment we disappeared. And the food... oh, the smell of it all rotting away. It's a mess."
msgstr ""
"你能相信嗎？清理這些蜘蛛網得花上好幾週。彷彿我們一消失，蜘蛛就立刻搬進來了。"
"還有食物……啊，那腐爛的味道。真是一團糟。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_percival_cleanup:0
msgid "Good luck with all that."
msgstr "祝你一切順利。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_garden
msgid "Our poor garden! It's been choked by weeds, and what few crops are left are withered. It'll be a full season's work just to get it back to where it was. I've never seen it this bad before."
msgstr ""
"我們可憐的花園！全被雜草纏繞，剩下的作物也枯萎了。要花整整一季的時間才能恢復"
"原狀。我從未見過這麼糟糕的情況。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_garden:0
msgid "Farming is in my blood, so I could help you, but I won't. It's time to find my brother, Andor. Have you seen him?"
msgstr ""
"務農是我的天性，我本可以幫你，但我不會。現在是時候去找我的兄弟，安多爾。你有"
"見過他嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_theodora_garden_2
msgid "I think we both know the answer to that. Now, leave me to tend to this mess."
msgstr "我想我們都知道答案。現在，讓我來處理這場混亂。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_cleanup
msgid "It's like the village itself fell into a deep sleep, just like us. Now, we have to wake it up again, clean out the overgrowth, and hope the roots haven't gone too deep. This'll take every bit of strength we've got."
msgstr ""
"就像整個村莊也陷入了沉睡，和我們一樣。現在，我們得喚醒它，清理雜草，希望根部"
"還沒長得太深。這將耗盡我們所有的力量。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_osric_cleanup:0
msgid "Oh, it most certainly will."
msgstr "哦，絕對會的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_odilia_cleanup
msgid "Everything's out of place, left exactly as it was when we... when we vanished. It's eerie, really. We'll need everyone's help to tidy up and get the village back to how it was. But first, we need to clear away the webs and rot."
msgstr ""
"一切都亂了套，完全保持著我們……消失時的樣子。真是詭異。我們需要大家的幫助來整"
"理，讓村莊恢復原貌。但首先，我們得清除蜘蛛網和腐朽。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:road_rondel_move_hint
msgid "[While scanning you up and down with his eyes...] There's something... about you... something warm. Ain't my place to stand in the way of that."
msgstr "[他用眼睛上下打量著你...] 你身上有種...溫暖的感覺。這不是我該阻擋的。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_village_hole
msgid "There's a disgusting smell emanting from that hole in the wall. You think there must be a dead animal inside it."
msgstr "牆上的洞散發出一股惡臭。你猜裡面一定有隻死掉的動物。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_village_welcome
msgid ""
"Welcome to Wexlow Village.\n"
"\n"
"~Glory be to Feygard"
msgstr ""
"歡迎來到威克斯洛村。\n"
"\n"
"~榮耀歸於妖境"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_ip
msgid "Hey there. I am \"Wulfric the Wonderful\"."
msgstr "你好。我是「奇妙的沃爾弗里克」。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_ip:0
#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_andor:0
msgid "I am wondering..."
msgstr "我在想…"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_wonder
msgid "Why I'm so wonderful?"
msgstr "我為何如此出色？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_wonder:0
msgid "Well, yeah, but no, not really."
msgstr "嗯，是這樣，但又不是完全如此。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_wonder:1
msgid "Do you know where the residents of Wexlow Village are?"
msgstr "你知道威克斯洛村的居民在哪裡嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_wonder:2
msgid "Yes, why are you so wonderful?"
msgstr "是啊，你怎麼這麼棒？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_ask_about_andor:0
msgid "Whether you've seen my brother, Andor or not. You see, he looks like me, but not as good looking."
msgstr "不管你有沒有見過我兄弟安多爾。他長得像我，但沒我帥。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_andor
msgid "Nope. Sorry. Is there anything else?"
msgstr "不行，抱歉。還有其他事嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_andor:1
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_default_10:1
msgid "Nope."
msgstr "不。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_wexlow
msgid "Wexlow Village? Where is that?"
msgstr "威克斯洛村？那是哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_wexlow:0
msgid "Oh, nevermind."
msgstr "哦，算了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wulfric_wonder_answer
msgid "Because all the ladies say that I am."
msgstr "因為所有女士都這麼說我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_wexlow
msgid "What?! There's nobody in the village?"
msgstr "什麼？！村子裡沒有人？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_wexlow:0
msgid "Nope. Not a single person, and it looks like there hasn't been for a while."
msgstr "沒有。連一個人都沒有，看起來已經很久沒有人了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:rosmara_wexlow2
msgid "Hmm, I hope they are all right."
msgstr "嗯，希望他們沒事。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_known_fight:0
msgid "This ends now for you!"
msgstr "這一切現在就結束了！"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_player_left_after_agreeing_to_help
msgid "Human, why you leave? Rude."
msgstr "人類，你為何離開？真沒禮貌。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd
msgid "Would you like to try a piece before you dig into yours?"
msgstr "你想先嘗一口再開始吃你的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd:0
msgid "Nah, thanks anyway."
msgstr "不，還是謝謝你。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd:1
msgid "Yes, please. That would be great."
msgstr "是的，請。那太好了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd_1
msgid "Here you go. Eat it up while it's hot."
msgstr "給你。趁熱吃吧。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd_1:0
msgid "Oh, man, that was nasty."
msgstr "哇，真噁心。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd_1:1
msgid "That was delicious! But what...is it...doing to me? I feel so funny."
msgstr "真好吃！但這……對我做了什麼？我感覺好奇怪。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd_nasty
msgid "What?! You ungrateful little brat."
msgstr "什麼？！你這忘恩負義的小鬼。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd_good
msgid "Oh, that? That's nothing. Just some side effects of great cooking."
msgstr "喔，那個？沒什麼啦。只是美味料理的小副作用。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_try_fd_good:0
msgid "Umm...OK."
msgstr "嗯……好。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_fd_complete_no_impatient
msgid "You know, my Feygard customers never pester me like this. They know to be patient and wait for this great delicacy."
msgstr "你知道嗎，我的妖境顧客從不會這樣煩我。他們都知道要耐心等待這道美味佳餚。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_3
msgid "Me alone."
msgstr "只有我。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_3:0
msgid "Really? I'm not so sure about that, but I'll see about that."
msgstr "真的嗎？我不太確定，但我會去看看。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:gamjee_villagers_unknown_3:1
msgid "I don't believe you! Prove it."
msgstr "我不相信你！證明給我看。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_selector_has_ingredients
msgid "Were you successful in finding all of the items that I've requested of you?"
msgstr "你是否成功找齊我所要求的所有物品？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_selector_has_ingredients:0
msgid "Yes, I have everything that you asked for in order to bake the Feydelight."
msgstr "是的，我擁有你所需的所有材料來烘焙費伊之光。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_selector_not_all_ingredients
msgid "Did you find all the ingredients?"
msgstr "你找到所有材料了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_philippa_selector_not_all_ingredients:0
msgid "What do I need to do again to get my \"Feydelight\"?"
msgstr "我還需要做什麼才能獲得「妖精之光」？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:village_godwin_lost_ring_give_ring_free
msgid "Thank you so much! I really appreciate you just giving it to me. Here are a few coins for your trouble."
msgstr "非常感謝！真的很感激你直接送給我。這是幾枚銅幣，辛苦你了。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_jump_10
msgid "Do you want to jump inside?"
msgstr "你想跳進去嗎？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_jump_10:0
msgid "No way! I remember How badly I was hurt the last time."
msgstr "不可能！我還記得上次我受傷有多嚴重。"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_jump_10:1
msgid "Yes. What choice do I have?"
msgstr "是啊。我還能有什麼選擇？"

#: conversationlist_feygard_1.json:wexlow_well_ask_to_jump_20
msgid "You jumped down into the darkness of the well. At the bottom of the well, you find yourself dazed and bleeding from what feels like every part of your body."
msgstr "你跳入了井底的黑暗中。井底，你發現自己眩暈且全身流血。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_1
msgid "My sleep has been very restless lately."
msgstr "我最近睡得很不安穩。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_1:0
msgid "Oh no, why are you not sleeping well?"
msgstr "糟了，為什麼你睡不好？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_2
msgid "I am being taunted by naughty lytwings at night. At least that is what Rigmor tells me. They play with my hair while I sleep, and tangle it into fairy-lock knots. Every morning I wake up tired, and I spend an hour brushing out the knots. I don't know what to do!"
msgstr ""
"夜晚有頑皮的萊特翼在嘲弄我。至少這是瑞格莫告訴我的。牠們在我睡覺時玩弄我的頭"
"髮，還把它打成妖精結。每天早上我醒來都很疲憊，還得花一小時梳理這些結。我真不"
"知道該怎麼辦！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_2:0
msgid "I am sorry to hear that, but I cannot help you right now."
msgstr "很遺憾聽到這個消息，但我現在無法幫助你。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_2:1
msgid "That sounds awful, can I help in any way?"
msgstr "聽起來很糟，我能幫上什麼忙嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_3
msgid "I understand. I guess I will just have to live with their mischief, and hope that I don't lose my hair, or my sanity!"
msgstr "我明白了。看來我只能忍受他們的惡作劇，希望別因此掉髮或失去理智！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_4
msgid "You would be willing to help me? I would be so grateful if you could make them leave me alone."
msgstr "你願意幫助我嗎？如果你能讓他們別再煩我，我將非常感激。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_5
msgid "Have you found them yet?"
msgstr "你找到他們了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_5:0
msgid "Not yet. I still need to go talk with Rigmor to find out more."
msgstr "還沒。我還需要去找瑞格摩談談，了解更多。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_5:1
msgid "Not yet. I am still looking for their mushroom patch. You wouldn't know where it is, perhaps?"
msgstr "還沒有。我還在找他們的蘑菇地。你或許知道在哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_5:2
msgid "I did, they asked that I bring them a gift of apples and strawberries."
msgstr "我有，他們要我帶蘋果和草莓作為禮物。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6
msgid "Please tell me you have good news?"
msgstr "請告訴我你有好消息？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:0
msgid "They accepted the gift and will allow me to talk to them."
msgstr "他們接受了禮物，願意讓我與他們交談。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:1
msgid "The lytwings are upset that you took their mushrooms. I pleaded with them, and am now waiting on their decision."
msgstr "萊特翼族因你拿走了他們的蘑菇而不悅。我已向他們懇求，現在正等待他們的決定。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:2
msgid "I have, and they agreed to stop pestering you if I help cut down a tree for them."
msgstr "我有，他們同意如果我幫忙砍樹，就不再煩你。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:3
msgid "The lytwings changed their minds, and are now thinking of something else they want instead."
msgstr "萊特翼改變了主意，現在想要別的東西。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:4
msgid "They now want four bottles of mead. They sure are giving me the run around today!"
msgstr "他們現在要四瓶蜂蜜酒。今天真是讓我繞來繞去！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:5
msgid "They took the mead, but said they need something else."
msgstr "他們拿了蜂蜜酒，但說還需要別的東西。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:6
msgid "They want a dozen wild flowers."
msgstr "他們想要一打野花。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:7
msgid "They took the wild flowers ..."
msgstr "他們採了野花..."

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:8
msgid "The lytwings ask that you make a promise to never pick mushrooms from their fairy ring again."
msgstr "萊特翼族請你答應，永遠不要再從他們的妖精圈中採摘蘑菇。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:9
msgid "I will take your ring to them at once!"
msgstr "我會立刻把你的戒指帶給他們！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_6:10
msgid "I gave them your ring, they are busy discussing it now."
msgstr "我把你的戒指給他們了，他們現在正忙著討論。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_7
msgid "Oh that is great news! If you need an axe, check with Jakrar, my father, over there."
msgstr "喔，那真是好消息！如果你需要斧頭，可以去找那邊的賈克拉爾，我父親。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_8
msgid "Please keep me updated."
msgstr "請隨時告知我最新情況。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_9
msgid "Thank you so much for helping me with the lytwings!"
msgstr "非常感謝你幫我照顧小翼！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_9:0
msgid "You are welcome!"
msgstr "不客氣！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_10
msgid "Okay thanks for letting me know. Don't let them wait too long."
msgstr "好的，謝謝告訴我。別讓他們等太久。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_11
msgid "Oh wonderful! An odd request nonetheless."
msgstr "喔，真是太好了！不過這請求有點奇怪。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_11:0
msgid "I better go and find those fruit."
msgstr "我最好去找那些水果。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_11:1
msgid "Where can I find apples and strawberries?"
msgstr "我在哪裡可以找到蘋果和草莓？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_12
msgid "You can buy apples at the Fallhaven tavern. Not sure about strawberries though."
msgstr "你可以在墜港鎮酒館買蘋果。不過草莓就不確定了。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_13
msgid "Oh no, they sound very difficult to deal with. I hope it gets better."
msgstr "糟了，他們聽起來很難對付。希望情況會好轉。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_14
msgid "I am so sorry."
msgstr "非常抱歉。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_15
msgid "You have done so much for me already. I will understand if you want to quit, I won't blame you."
msgstr "你已經為我做了這麼多。如果你想放棄，我會理解，不會怪你。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_15:0
msgid "I want to see this through."
msgstr "我想堅持到底。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_15:1
msgid "The lytwings are driving me insane. I thought about this, and I can't help you any more. I am sorry."
msgstr "那些光翼鳥快把我逼瘋了。我想過了，我無法再幫你了。抱歉。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_16
msgid "You are too kind!"
msgstr "你太客氣了！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_17
msgid "I appreciate your help either way."
msgstr "無論如何，我都感謝你的幫助。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_18
msgid "Oh please tell me that is the end of it?"
msgstr "拜託告訴我這就是結局吧？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_18:0
msgid "I'm afraid not, they still want more."
msgstr "恐怕不行，他們還想要更多。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_19
msgid "Of course! anything!"
msgstr "當然！任何事！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_19:0
msgid "You have to make this promise to a piece of jewellery, which I will take back to them."
msgstr "你必須向這件飾品許下承諾，我會將它帶回給他們。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_20
msgid "I know, I will promise on this ring I'm wearing. It belonged to my mother, and it's dear to me, but I will do anything to stop the lytwings!"
msgstr ""
"我知道，我會以我戴著的這枚戒指發誓。它是我母親的遺物，對我很重要，但我會不惜"
"一切阻止光翼族！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_20:0
msgid "I hope this works."
msgstr "希望這有效。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_21
msgid "I made a promise to the ring, here take it to the lytwings!"
msgstr "我向戒指許下了承諾，這個交給光翼族吧！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_21:0
msgid "I will, right away!"
msgstr "我馬上去！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_22
msgid "There is nothing else to be done, and I will have to live with the lytwings tormenting me until my last day."
msgstr "別無他法，我只能忍受這些萊特翼族折磨我直到生命的最後一刻。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_23
msgid "So ... what did they say?"
msgstr "那麼……他們怎麼說？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_23:0
msgid "The lytwings finally agreed to leave you in peace."
msgstr "萊特翼族終於同意放你一馬。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_24
msgid "I cannot thank you enough, $playername. You have saved my sanity!"
msgstr "我無法用言語表達我的感激，$playername。你拯救了我的理智！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_24:0
msgid "Unfortunately they kept your mother's ring (Lie)."
msgstr "很不幸，他們留下了你母親的戒指（謊言）。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_24:1
msgid "They used their magic on your ring, and asked that I give it back to you."
msgstr "他們用魔法作用在你的戒指上，並請我把它還給你。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_25
msgid "That is okay. I did not expect to get it back."
msgstr "沒關係。我本來就沒指望能拿回來。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_26
msgid "After everything you have done for me ... I want you to keep it. Please, I insist!"
msgstr "在你為我做了這麼多之後……我希望你能留下它。拜託，我堅持！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_26:0
msgid "That is very generous, I won't forget it."
msgstr "真是太慷慨了，我不會忘記的。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_27
msgid "I can't say that I have noticed it. A few days ago I was picking mushrooms to the west of here."
msgstr "我倒沒注意到。幾天前我還在這裡西邊採蘑菇呢。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_28
msgid "They sure are a greedy bunch!"
msgstr "他們真是一群貪婪的傢伙！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_29
msgid "Are you sure that you want to quit?"
msgstr "你確定要退出嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_29:0
msgid "Yes, I want to quit."
msgstr "是的，我想退出。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_29:1
msgid "On second thought, I want to see this through."
msgstr "再想想，我想堅持到底。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_30
msgid "How can I help?"
msgstr "我能幫什麼忙？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_30:0
msgid "Where can I find wild flowers?"
msgstr "我在哪裡可以找到野花？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_30:1
msgid "I found some wild flowers, I just need a few more."
msgstr "我找到了一些野花，還需要幾朵。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_30:2
msgid "I have found a dozen wild flowers. I will take them to the lytwings."
msgstr "我找到了一打野花。我要帶給萊特翼族。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_30:3
msgid "Will this ever end?"
msgstr "這會結束嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_31
msgid "Look to the south, and southeast from here. You will see the wild flowers growing next to the trees. "
msgstr "從這裡向南和東南望去，你會看到樹旁盛開的野花。 "

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_32
msgid "Oh I hope they accept it, and I hope they are done with their silly errands."
msgstr "哦，我希望他們會接受，也希望他們已經完成那些愚蠢的差事。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_33
msgid "You should talk to Rigmor, as she knows more about the lytwings than I do. She lives here in Fallhaven, just go north past the tavern."
msgstr "你應該去找瑞格摩，她比我更了解光翼族。她住在墜港鎮，就在酒館北邊。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_33:0
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "好的。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_34
msgid "They have, I no longer wake up with fairy-locks."
msgstr "他們有，我不再醒來時頭髮糾結成結。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_34:0
#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_34:1
msgid "I am happy to hear that."
msgstr "很高興聽到這個消息。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_35
msgid "But I see you have the ring I gave them. You told me they kept it, which can only mean that you lied to me. You are just a common thief. Shame on you."
msgstr ""
"但我看到你有我給他們的戒指。你告訴我他們保留了它，這只能意味著你對我說謊。你"
"不過是個普通的小偷。真丟臉。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_35:0
msgid "But, I ... um ...."
msgstr "但是，我……嗯……"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_36
msgid "I see you have my magical ring. I hope it serves you well, you deserve it."
msgstr "我看到你帶著我的魔法戒指。希望它能助你一臂之力，你值得擁有它。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_36:0
msgid "I keep it safe, and it keeps me safe in return."
msgstr "我守護它，它也守護我。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:arensia_lytwing_37
msgid "Those flowers look perfect."
msgstr "那些花看起來完美無瑕。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:bela_lytwing_strawberries
msgid "I don't, but I believe the potion merchant here in Fallhaven has some."
msgstr "我沒有，但我相信墜港鎮這裡的藥水商人有一些。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_1
msgid "I take it you spoke to Arensia?"
msgstr "我猜你已經和艾倫西亞談過了？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_2
msgid "What do you want to know?"
msgstr "你想知道什麼？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_2:0
msgid "What do you know about lytwings?"
msgstr "你對萊特翼族了解多少？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_2:1
msgid "Where can I find lytwings?"
msgstr "我在哪裡可以找到萊特翼？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_2:2
msgid "Thank you. I really need to go now."
msgstr "謝謝你。我現在真的得走了。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_3
msgid "Lytwings are small magical beings that are also known as the guardians of the forest, and they are known to take revenge on us when we intrude on them, or on nature."
msgstr ""
"萊特翼是小型魔法生物，被稱為森林守護者，當我們侵擾他們或自然時，他們會報復我"
"們。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_4
msgid "They are also very mischievous, and love causing trouble. They probably eat too many fermented berries, if you ask me."
msgstr "他們也非常調皮，喜歡惹麻煩。如果你問我，他們大概吃了太多發酵漿果。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_5
msgid "Lytwings gather near fairy rings. I suggest that you look for large mushroom patches in the woodland surrounding Fallhaven."
msgstr "萊特翼會聚集在妖精圈附近。我建議你在墜港鎮周圍的森林中尋找大型蘑菇群。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:rigmor_lytwing_6
msgid "The poor girl. She looks exhausted, and her hair is absolutely tousled. Will those lytwings never leave her alone?"
msgstr ""
"可憐的女孩。她看起來筋疲力盡，頭髮完全亂糟糟的。那些萊特翼族難道永遠不會放過"
"她嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_1
msgid "Hello there, stranger!"
msgstr "你好，陌生人！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_1:0
msgid "Oh, hi. My name is $playername. Who are you?"
msgstr "哦，你好。我叫 $playername。你是誰？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_2
msgid "Well met, $playername. I won't tell you my name, it is forbidden for otherkinds to know our names."
msgstr "久違了，$playername。我不會告訴你我的名字，其他種族知道我們的名字是被禁止的。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_3
msgid "Did you bring us a gift?"
msgstr "你帶禮物來了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_3:0
msgid "Yes, here are two red apples and two strawberries."
msgstr "是的，這裡有兩顆紅蘋果和兩顆草莓。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_3:1
msgid "I did not, sorry."
msgstr "我沒有，抱歉。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_4
msgid "Bring us two red apples and two strawberries. Since you came without a gift, we cast on you a mystical Lytwing spell!"
msgstr "帶來兩顆紅蘋果和兩顆草莓。既然你空手而來，我們便對你施放神秘的萊特翼咒語！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_4:0
msgid "I feel so ... tired."
msgstr "我感覺好...累。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_5
msgid "Wonderful! These strawberries are so sweet. You may stay!"
msgstr "太棒了！這些草莓真甜。你可以留下來！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_6
msgid "Hi $playername! Want to play with us?"
msgstr "嗨 $playername！想和我們一起玩嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_6:0
msgid "I'm here on behalf of Arensia. She is very upset."
msgstr "我是代表艾倫西亞來的。她非常難過。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_7
msgid "She should be sorry! She stole our mushrooms."
msgstr "她應該感到抱歉！她偷了我們的蘑菇。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_7:0
msgid "I'm sure she did not mean to steal them. She was probably just gathering mushrooms for a stew."
msgstr "我相信她並非有意偷竊。她大概只是為了燉湯採集蘑菇。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_8
msgid "A STEW? That is unacceptable. She must be punished."
msgstr "燉菜？這無法接受。她必須受到懲罰。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_8:0
msgid "Don't be mad, I am just trying to help. Is there anything I can do to make this right?"
msgstr "別生氣，我只是想幫忙。有什麼我能做的讓事情變好嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_9
msgid "Hmmm, let us discuss this amongst ourselves. Can you give us a minute alone?"
msgstr "嗯，讓我們私下討論一下。你能給我們一點時間嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_9:0
msgid "OK, I will wait nearby."
msgstr "好的，我會在附近等。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_10
msgid "We are busy discussing the matter. Please wait a little bit longer."
msgstr "我們正在忙著討論此事，請稍候片刻。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_11
msgid "We have decided to entertain your request."
msgstr "我們已決定接受您的請求。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_11:0
msgid "Thank you, Arensia will be happy to hear that!"
msgstr "謝謝你，艾倫西亞聽到這個消息一定會很高興！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_12
msgid "But you have to do something for us first [giggle]."
msgstr "但你得先幫我們做件事 [giggle]。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_12:0
msgid "Oh please just let Arensia be, she meant no ill will."
msgstr "拜託別管艾倫西亞，她並無惡意。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_12:1
msgid "Please just forgive her mistake. There is no need to prolong her suffering."
msgstr "請原諒她的錯誤，無需讓她繼續受苦。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_12:2
msgid "Yes of course. What do you need?"
msgstr "當然可以。你需要什麼？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_13
msgid "Suit yourself. If you won't help us, we won't help Arensia. Goodbye!"
msgstr "隨你便。如果你不幫我們，我們也不會幫艾倫西亞。再見！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_14
msgid "Please chop down this gnarly old tree inside our fairy circle. Can you do that for us?"
msgstr "請砍倒我們精靈圈內這棵扭曲的老樹。你能幫我們做嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_14:0
msgid "No, I am not willing to do that."
msgstr "不，我不願意那麼做。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_14:1
msgid "OK, I will chop it down."
msgstr "好的，我會砍倒它。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_15
msgid "Hmm, this must be the tree the lytwings want chopped down. I need to get an iron axe."
msgstr "嗯，這一定是萊特翼族想砍倒的樹。我得先弄把鐵斧頭。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_16
msgid "Hey wait! We changed our minds. We like that tree and want to keep it."
msgstr "等等！我們改主意了。我們喜歡那棵樹，想留下它。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_17
msgid "We are having a celebration, please get us four bottles of mead. [giggle]"
msgstr "我們正在慶祝，請幫我們拿四瓶蜂蜜酒。[咯咯笑]"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_17:0
msgid "I don't think so. Your demands are getting ridiculous."
msgstr "我不這麼認為。你的要求越來越離譜了。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_17:1
msgid "Okay, fine. I will get you the mead. But you better not change your mind again."
msgstr "好吧，我會給你蜂蜜酒。但你最好別再改主意。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_18
msgid "Do you have our mead?"
msgstr "你有我們的蜂蜜酒嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_18:1
msgid "Yes, here is your mead."
msgstr "是的，這是你的蜂蜜酒。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_19
msgid "Wonderful!"
msgstr "太棒了！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_19:0
msgid "Will you leave Arensia alone now?"
msgstr "你現在會放過艾倫西亞嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_20
msgid "Yes, of course we will."
msgstr "是的，當然會的。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_20:0
msgid "Arensia wil be very happy to hear this."
msgstr "艾倫西亞聽到這消息一定會非常高興。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_21
msgid "We just need you to do one more thing for us ..."
msgstr "我們只需要你再幫我們做一件事..."

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_21:0
msgid "More? No I don't think so. This is absurd."
msgstr "還要更多？不，我不這麼認為。這太荒謬了。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_21:1
msgid "What do you want now?"
msgstr "你現在想要什麼？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_22
msgid "For our celebrations, we would like a dozen wild flowers."
msgstr "為了慶祝，我們需要一打野花。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_22:0
msgid "This is getting silly. I don't want to collect flowers for you."
msgstr "這太荒謬了。我才不想幫你採花。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_22:1
msgid "Okay fine. But this better be the last thing."
msgstr "好吧。但這最好是最後一件事。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_23
msgid "Do you have our wild flowers?"
msgstr "你有我們的野花嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_23:0
msgid "No I don't."
msgstr "不，我沒有。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_23:1
#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_23:2
msgid "Yes, here are your flowers."
msgstr "是的，這是你的花。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_23a
msgid "No, you don't have enough flowers. A dozen means 12, not one less. Do you think lytwings can't count?"
msgstr "不，你的花不夠。一打是12朵，不是少一朵。你以為萊特翼不會數數嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_23a:0
msgid "I have collected enough for you. Take it or leave it."
msgstr "我已為你收集足夠。要就拿，不要就算。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_23a:1
msgid "Sorry, I'm going to look for the missing wild flowers now."
msgstr "抱歉，我現在要去找失蹤的野花。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_24
msgid "These are perfect. Thank you!"
msgstr "這些很完美，謝謝！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_24:0
msgid "Is that everything? Will you leave Arensia be?"
msgstr "就這些嗎？你會放過艾倫西亞嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_25
msgid "Give us a minute to think about it."
msgstr "給我們一點時間考慮。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_26
msgid "Okay so after carefully considering your request ..."
msgstr "好的，經過仔細考慮你的請求..."

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_27
msgid "We have decided what would make this right ..."
msgstr "我們已決定如何彌補這一切..."

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_27:0
msgid "OK?"
msgstr "好嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_28
msgid "We want Arensia to promise not to pick our mushrooms again. And we want proof!"
msgstr "我們希望艾倫西亞答應不再摘我們的蘑菇。還要有證據！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_28:0
msgid "I can ask her, but how can I provide proof?"
msgstr "我可以問她，但我該如何提供證據？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_29
msgid "She must give a piece of jewelry as proof of her promise. Her word would be bound to it."
msgstr "她必須交出一件珠寶作為承諾的證明。她的話語將與之綁定。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_29:0
msgid "This sounds very silly."
msgstr "這聽起來很傻。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_29:1
msgid "Very well. I will go talk to Arensia."
msgstr "很好。我會去找艾倫西亞談談。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_30
msgid "Good. And remember, she has to make her promise to the jewelry."
msgstr "很好。記得，她必須向珠寶許下承諾。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_31
msgid "Did you bring us Arensia's promise?"
msgstr "你帶來了艾倫西亞的承諾嗎？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_31:0
msgid "No, I have not."
msgstr "沒有，我沒有。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_31:1
msgid "Yes, here is her promise ring."
msgstr "是的，這是她的承諾戒指。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_32
msgid "This will do just fine, thank you $playername."
msgstr "這樣就很好了，謝謝你 $playername。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_32:0
msgid "I hope this settles the matter?"
msgstr "我希望這能解決問題？"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_33
msgid "Well, I think you know what I will say next ..."
msgstr "嗯，我想你知道我接下來會說什麼..."

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_33:0
msgid "Oh no, not again!"
msgstr "糟了，又來了！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_35
msgid "We have discussed this matter and made a final decision ..."
msgstr "我們已討論此事並做出最終決定..."

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_35:0
msgid "OK, I hope this turns out well."
msgstr "好的，希望結果順利。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_36
msgid "Please tell Arensia that we have accepted her promise. We will no longer taunt her at night."
msgstr "請告訴艾倫西亞，我們已接受她的承諾。我們不會再在夜晚嘲弄她。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_36:0
msgid "Oh how wonderful. Thank you forest lytwings!"
msgstr "喔，真是太棒了。謝謝你們，森林光翼！"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_37
msgid "However, we have no need for a human ring. We embued it with our magical powers. Please take this ring back to Arensia."
msgstr "不過，我們不需要人類的戒指。我們已將魔力注入其中。請將這枚戒指帶回艾倫西亞。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_37:0
msgid "I will give Arensia her ring back. She will appreciate this gesture very much."
msgstr "我會把戒指還給艾倫西亞。她會非常感激這個舉動。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_38
msgid "Hello $playername. We hope you are staying out of trouble."
msgstr "你好 $playername。希望你遠離麻煩。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_39
msgid "It is important that you use an iron axe. That tree is cursed, and only an iron axe will work."
msgstr "重要的是你必須使用鐵斧。那棵樹被詛咒了，只有鐵斧才能砍倒。"

#: conversationlist_lytwings.json:lytwing_fallhaven_39:0
msgid "OK, I understand."
msgstr "好的，我明白了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt
msgid "Sure. I heard you're looking for Sly Seraphina."
msgstr "當然。我聽說你在找狡猾的塞拉菲娜。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt:0
msgid "Eavesdropping is not nice."
msgstr "偷聽是不好的。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt:1
msgid "Yes. Do you have any idea where she might be hiding?"
msgstr "是的。你知道她可能藏在哪裡嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_10
msgid "We are thieves - already forgotten?"
msgstr "我們是盜賊——已被遺忘了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_10:0
msgid "So can you help me?"
msgstr "那你能幫我嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_10:1
msgid "Nevertheless, one can still maintain one's good manners."
msgstr "儘管如此，仍可保持禮貌。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_12
msgid "Phh."
msgstr "哼。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_20
msgid "Of course. In fact, I know exactly where she's hiding right now."
msgstr "當然。我甚至知道她現在正藏在哪裡。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_20:0
msgid "Great. That will save me a lot of running around."
msgstr "太好了。這樣我就不用跑來跑去了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_22
msgid "Here's how we do it: You can guess, and I'll tell you whether it's true or not."
msgstr "我們這樣玩：你猜，我會告訴你對不對。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_24
msgid "And each tip only costs you 100 gold pieces."
msgstr "而且每個提示只需花費你100金幣。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_24:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_204:0
msgid "I should have known."
msgstr "我早該知道。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_26
msgid "You already know that she is near a town."
msgstr "你已經知道她就在鎮附近。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_26:0
msgid "But which one?"
msgstr "但是哪一個？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30
msgid "Guess!"
msgstr "猜猜看！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:2
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:3
msgid "Brimhaven?"
msgstr "布林哈文？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:4
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:5
msgid "Prim?"
msgstr "普莉姆？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:6
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:7
msgid "Loneford?"
msgstr "隆福？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:8
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:9
msgid "Stoutford?"
msgstr "斯托福德？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:10
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:11
msgid "Sullengard?"
msgstr "蘇倫加德？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:12
msgid "Oh, I'm running out of gold."
msgstr "喔，我的金幣快用完了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_30:13
msgid "Enough. I think you don't know yourself."
msgstr "夠了。我看你根本不了解自己。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_32
msgid "You are so smart. I'm sorry I tried."
msgstr "你真聰明。抱歉我曾嘗試過。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_34
msgid "No problem. I can wait."
msgstr "沒問題。我可以等。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_40
msgid "Hey, that's right!"
msgstr "嘿，沒錯！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_50
msgid "Nope - 100 gold. Try again ..."
msgstr "不行 - 100 金幣。再試一次 ..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:fanamor_tt_60
msgid "Thanks for the gold. But don't tell her that I betrayed her."
msgstr "謝謝你的金幣。但別告訴她我背叛了她。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_10
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_12
msgid "You? How dare you show your face?"
msgstr "你？竟敢現身？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_18
msgid "You betrayed the Guild over the task with Defy. Get out!"
msgstr "你因違抗任務而背叛了公會，滾出去！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_20
msgid "Hi there. I am Nanath, the oldest and most experienced man in the guild. No need to introduce yourself, I know who you are, $playername."
msgstr ""
"你好。我是納納斯，公會中最年長且經驗最豐富的人。不用自我介紹，我知道你是誰"
"，$playername。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_20:0
msgid "Oh. Hi Nanath. You look scared."
msgstr "喔。嗨，Nanath。你看起來很害怕。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_22
msgid "Well, one of our ex-clients, Lady Dameni, has put an adverse Shadow spell on us."
msgstr "嗯，我們的一位前客戶，達梅妮夫人，對我們施加了不利的暗影魔法。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_24
msgid "It makes us noticeable, and thus vulnerable to being caught - paralyzing our honest bread and butter work."
msgstr "這會讓我們顯眼，因此容易被抓住——癱瘓我們誠實謀生的工作。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_24:0
msgid "Oh. Sounds awful."
msgstr "喔。聽起來很糟。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_26
msgid "Umar wants me to handle it. He wants me to get it dispelled, so that the Thieves' Guild can work again."
msgstr "烏瑪爾想讓我處理這件事。他希望我解除詛咒，讓盜賊公會能重新運作。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_26:0
msgid "Ah, OK then."
msgstr "啊，那好吧。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_28
msgid "The thing is I don't know much about the Shadow or any other so-called powers. My life has been being an honest thief, a score here, a score there - I don't tangle with the supernatural stuff."
msgstr ""
"問題是我對暗影或其他所謂的力量所知不多。我的生活就是當個誠實的小偷，這裡偷一"
"點，那裡偷一點——我不沾惹那些超自然的東西。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_30
msgid "Can't anyone help?"
msgstr "沒有人能幫忙嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_30:0
msgid "I can help. I've had some dealings with the Shadow."
msgstr "我可以幫忙。我曾與暗影有所接觸。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_32
msgid "Really? Like what?"
msgstr "真的嗎？像什麼？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_32:0
msgid "Sorry, hush-hush stuff around Loneford and Vilegard."
msgstr "抱歉，這是關於隆福德和維雷加德的機密消息。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_34:0
msgid "You want my help?"
msgstr "你需要我的幫助？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_40
msgid "First things first, how can we know the nature of the spell?"
msgstr "首先，我們如何得知這個法術的本質？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_42
msgid "Or its name?"
msgstr "還是它的名字？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_44
msgid "Maybe talking to a Shadow priest may help?"
msgstr "也許跟暗影牧師談談會有幫助？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_70
msgid "Oh, back again? I hope you bring good news."
msgstr "喔，又回來了？希望你帶來好消息。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_70:0
msgid "Maybe. Talion, a Shadow priest, has put the Striking Spectacle Shadow spell on us."
msgstr "也許吧。塔利昂，一位暗影牧師，對我們施放了震擊奇觀暗影法術。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_70:1
msgid "I have been looking for the things for Talion."
msgstr "我一直在為塔利昂尋找那些東西。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_70:2
msgid "About Luthor's ring ..."
msgstr "關於路索爾的戒指..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_70:3
msgid "I am still looking for Seraphina."
msgstr "我仍在尋找賽拉菲娜。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_72:0
msgid "And ... I think I have to talk to Talion again."
msgstr "而且……我想我得再跟塔利昂談談。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_72:1
msgid "Talion said he can help dispel it."
msgstr "塔利昂說他能幫忙驅散它。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_80
msgid "What a relief."
msgstr "真是鬆了一口氣。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_82
msgid "What does he want in return?"
msgstr "他想要什麼回報？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_82:0
msgid "Lady Dameni paid him. Talion wants 50000 gold to dispel us."
msgstr "達梅妮夫人付了他錢。塔利昂想要五萬金幣來驅散我們。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_84
msgid "That's a lot, but it was to be expected. It's good that he doesn't want more."
msgstr "那很多，但也在預料之中。他不想要更多，倒是件好事。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_84:0
msgid "Well ... he also wants the following items: The Villain's ring, Troublemaker's ring, the Ring of backstabbing and the Tears of the Shadow potion."
msgstr "嗯……他還想要以下物品：惡棍之戒、麻煩製造者之戒、背刺之戒和暗影之淚藥水。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_86
msgid "That's fine with me."
msgstr "我沒意見。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_86:0
msgid "And - most important - Luthor's ring."
msgstr "還有——最重要的——路索爾的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_90
msgid "What?! He must be crazy!"
msgstr "什麼？！他一定瘋了！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_92
msgid "Do you already have all of the items?"
msgstr "你已經擁有所有物品了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_92:0
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:1
msgid "I don't have Troublemaker's ring yet."
msgstr "我還沒有麻煩製造者的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_92:1
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:2
msgid "I don't have the Ring of backstabbing yet."
msgstr "我還沒有背刺之戒。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_92:2
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:3
msgid "I don't have the Villain's ring yet."
msgstr "我還沒有得到反派的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_92:3
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:4
msgid "I don't have the Tears of the Shadow yet."
msgstr "我還沒有暗影之淚。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_92:4
msgid "I have already brought the 4 easier things."
msgstr "我已經帶來了4樣較簡單的東西。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_94
msgid "Well, then go and find it. Hurry now!"
msgstr "那就去找吧。快點！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_100
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_76
msgid "Good, that's a start."
msgstr "很好，這是個開始。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_100:0
msgid "I expect to be reimbursed of course."
msgstr "我當然期望獲得賠償。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_100:1
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_76:1
msgid "I am glad you approve."
msgstr "很高興你認同。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_102
msgid "Umar will refund you, but only if you succeed."
msgstr "烏瑪爾會退還給你，但只有成功時才會。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_110
msgid "Have you found Luthor's ring yet?"
msgstr "你找到路索爾的戒指了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_110:0
msgid "I am looking for it now."
msgstr "我現在正在找。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_110:1
msgid "I have no idea where to look any more."
msgstr "我已經不知道該往哪裡找了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_120
msgid "Looks like it ended up being kept somewhere dangerous."
msgstr "看起來最後被藏在了危險的地方。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_122
msgid "Then ... only one person may know: Fanamor's friend Sly Seraphina."
msgstr "那麼...只有一個人可能知道：法納摩的朋友狡猾的賽拉菲娜。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_122:0
msgid "Sly Seraphina? Where can she be found?"
msgstr "狡猾的賽拉菲娜？她在哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_122:1
msgid "On no! Not Seraphina! I refuse to talk to her."
msgstr "糟了！不是賽拉菲娜！我拒絕跟她說話。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_130
msgid "She's the thief near the Sutdover bridge."
msgstr "她是蘇特多橋附近的盜賊。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_130:0
msgid "Sutdover bridge? So I'll look for her to the south."
msgstr "薩特多弗橋？那我就往南邊找她。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_132
msgid "You must. For the Guild!"
msgstr "你必須這麼做。為了公會！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_132:0
msgid "All right, I hate to, but for the greater good I'll go."
msgstr "好吧，我不情願，但為了大局我會去。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_136
msgid "Then it's all settled. Go and find her, now."
msgstr "那就這麼定了。現在就去找她。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_140
msgid "Then go and find her, now."
msgstr "那就現在去找她。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_150
msgid "How progresses the task? I hope you've done it? We're in a pickle here, kid. No time to dawdle."
msgstr "任務進展如何？希望你已完成？我們現在陷入困境，孩子。別再拖延了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_150:0
msgid "Dawdle! Do it yourself if you know everything better!"
msgstr "磨蹭！既然你什麼都知道，那就自己做吧！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_152
msgid "Calm down. I'm just nervous. Did you make any progress?"
msgstr "冷靜點。我只是緊張而已。你有什麼進展嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_160
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_410:0
msgid "Tell me."
msgstr "告訴我。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_160:0
msgid "Seraphina doesn't trust me."
msgstr "賽拉菲娜不信任我。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_160:1
msgid "Seraphina has disappeared. She's scared to unleash some monsters which she says Umar and her sealed up."
msgstr "烏瑪爾和她封印的怪物，賽拉菲娜害怕釋放，已經消失了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_160:2
msgid "About Seraphina ..."
msgstr "關於賽拉菲娜 ..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_170
msgid "She must. Go to Umar. He's the only one she'll listen to."
msgstr "她必須去找烏瑪爾。只有他她才會聽。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_180
msgid "So, that's what Umar is hush-hush about."
msgstr "所以，這就是烏瑪爾一直守口如瓶的原因。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_180:0
msgid "He could really be more talkative sometimes."
msgstr "他有時候真的可以多說點話。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_181
msgid "Anyway, we must find her. I know some of her usual hidings."
msgstr "無論如何，我們必須找到她。我知道她常藏身的幾個地方。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_181a
msgid "She prefers to be close to a town so she can easily stock up."
msgstr "她喜歡靠近城鎮，方便補給。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_181a:0
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_183:0
msgid "Makes sense."
msgstr "說得通。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_182
msgid "Let me think: Fallhaven would be too near. Sullengard, Stoutford, Vilegard and Prim come to my mind. And Loneford or Brimhaven, of course."
msgstr ""
"讓我想想：墜港鎮太近了。蘇倫加德、斯托福德、維雷加德和普林都在我腦海中。當然"
"還有隆福德或布瑞姆港。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_183
msgid "So look for her near one of these towns."
msgstr "所以就在這些城鎮附近找她。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_183:1
msgid "Which towns did you say again?"
msgstr "你剛剛說的是哪些城鎮？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_183a
msgid "Sometimes I could despair. It's so hard to find good workers these days."
msgstr "有時我會感到絕望。如今要找到好工人真難。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_184
msgid "She must be found. By any means."
msgstr "她必須被找到。不擇手段。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_184:0
msgid "Yes, sir"
msgstr "是，長官"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_190
msgid "Have you found Seraphina yet?"
msgstr "你找到賽拉菲娜了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_190:1
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_190:2
msgid "Yes. She told me I would need Luthor's key."
msgstr "是的。她告訴我我需要路索爾的鑰匙。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_192
msgid "I spoke to Umar. He already suspected that you would need this key."
msgstr "我和烏瑪爾談過了。他早就懷疑你會需要這把鑰匙。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_192a
msgid "Here you have it, handle it carefully."
msgstr "給你了，小心處理。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_193
msgid "I have given it to you already, forgotten?"
msgstr "我已經給過你了，忘了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_193:0
msgid "Oh, right. I'm ashamed of myself for trying to trick you."
msgstr "喔，對了。我真該為試圖欺騙你而感到羞愧。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_194
msgid "I truly hope you are."
msgstr "我真心希望你是。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_200
msgid "Hi kid."
msgstr "嗨，小子。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_200:0
msgid "I have got Luthor's ring."
msgstr "我拿到了路索爾的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_272
msgid "Then take it to Talion. Quickly."
msgstr "那就快點帶去給塔利昂。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_290
msgid "You were obviously successful. We seem to be inconspicuous again."
msgstr "你顯然很成功。我們似乎又恢復了低調。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_300
msgid "Good job! I didn't think you could do it. But you did."
msgstr "幹得好！我還以為你做不到呢。但你做到了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_300:0
msgid "Yes. The search was a nice change."
msgstr "是的。這次搜尋是個不錯的轉變。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_302
msgid "Sly Seraphina has already been here and returned Luthor's key to Umar. So the room with those dangerous creatures is sealed again."
msgstr ""
"狡猾的賽拉菲娜已經來過這裡，並將路索爾的鑰匙交還給烏瑪爾。因此，那間有危險生"
"物的房間再次被封鎖。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_302:0
msgid "So quick?"
msgstr "這麼快？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_304
msgid "Sure. You should know her by now."
msgstr "當然。你現在應該認識她了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_308
msgid "Umar asked me to reimburse you for your expenses. And something as a thank you. So here are 75000 shining pieces of gold."
msgstr "烏瑪爾請我補償你的花費，並表示感謝。這裡有75000枚閃亮的金幣。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:nanath_310
msgid "Stay safe, kid."
msgstr "保重，孩子。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt
msgid "Hello $playername, good that you are here. Please talk to Nanath, I am really busy right now."
msgstr "你好 $playername，很高興你來了。請去找納納斯，我現在真的很忙。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt:1
msgid "OK, I'll go find Nanath."
msgstr "好，我去找納納斯。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_100
msgid "$playername, didn't I make it clear that I didn't want to be disturbed?"
msgstr "$playername，我不是已經說過不想被打擾了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_100:0
msgid "Yes, I'm sorry too. But we need your help."
msgstr "是的，我也很抱歉。但我們需要你的幫助。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_102
msgid "[Muttering to himself] Tu quoque, mi fili? Sigh."
msgstr "[自言自語] 你也背叛我，我的孩子？唉。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_102:0
msgid "To break the spell, we need King Luthor's ring. Sly is the only one who knows where it is. But she refuses to cooperate."
msgstr "要破解魔咒，我們需要路索爾王的戒指。只有斯萊知道它在哪裡，但她拒絕合作。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_110
msgid "She must. Tell her this password [whispering something]. It means you have direct order from me, Umar. Let no one else hear it."
msgstr ""
"她必須知道。告訴她這個密碼 [低聲說著什麼]。這表示你有烏瑪爾我的直接命令。別讓"
"其他人聽見。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_110:0
msgid "OK. She will listen to you."
msgstr "好的。她會聽你的。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_120
msgid "My head is so full. I can hardly concentrate on the important things."
msgstr "我的腦袋好亂，幾乎無法專注於重要的事。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_120:0
msgid "I won't bother you any further."
msgstr "我不會再打擾你了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_120:1
msgid "The spell will be broken."
msgstr "魔法將被解除。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_120:2
msgid "Thoroughness is the key to success."
msgstr "徹底是成功的關鍵。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_130
msgid "Key? To success? Don't talk nonsense."
msgstr "成功的關鍵？別胡說。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_132
msgid "There's something else I should think about. But it just doesn't occur to me right now."
msgstr "還有其他事情我該考慮，但現在就是想不起來。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_132:0
msgid "I better leave you alone now."
msgstr "我還是先不打擾你了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:umar_tt_132:1
msgid "I'm sure you'll remember it again."
msgstr "我相信你會再想起來的。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:t_guild03_hideout3_lock_10
msgid "The lock is sealed again."
msgstr "鎖又被封印了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_jolnor_10
msgid "Excuse me? I don't know what you want from me."
msgstr "請問？我不知道你想從我這裡得到什麼。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_10
msgid "Umar? Who's that?"
msgstr "烏瑪爾？那是誰？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_10:0
msgid "Oh well: I am nothing. You don't see me."
msgstr "唉，我什麼都不是。你看不見我。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_12
msgid "That's better, little child. Get used to it."
msgstr "好多了，小孩。習慣點吧。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_12:1
msgid "I'm not a little child anymore!"
msgstr "我已經不是小孩子了！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_14
msgid "Then stop stomping on the ground."
msgstr "那就別再跺腳了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_30
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_40
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_50
msgid "Now what does Umar want?"
msgstr "烏瑪爾現在想要什麼？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_30:0
msgid "We have to remove the Striking Spectacle Shadow spell from members of the Thieves' Guild. Or the Guild may as well cease to exist."
msgstr "我們必須從盜賊公會成員身上移除「震撼暗影幻象」法術。否則公會恐怕將不復存在。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_32
msgid "And what do I have to do with it?"
msgstr "那跟我有什麼關係？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_32:0
msgid "We need Luthor's ring, and you know ..."
msgstr "我們需要路索爾的戒指，你也知道的..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_34
msgid "Likely story, kid. Buzz off!"
msgstr "真會編故事，小子。滾開！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_40:0
msgid "We have to remove the Striking Spectacle Shadow spell from ..."
msgstr "我們必須從...中移除震撼暗影魔法"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_42
msgid "Yes, you've said already. Stop repeating yourself."
msgstr "是的，你已經說過了。別再重複了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_42:0
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_44:0
msgid "Sure. We need Luthor's ring, and ..."
msgstr "當然。我們需要路索爾的戒指，還有..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_44
msgid "Forget it, kid. Buzz off!"
msgstr "算了，孩子。滾開！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_46
msgid "And please, stop repeating yourself."
msgstr "拜託，別再重複了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_50:0
msgid "Listen ... [whispering the password] Now you believe me? We have to remove the Striking Spectacle ..."
msgstr "聽著……[低聲說出密碼] 現在你相信我了嗎？我們必須移除驚人奇觀……"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_52
msgid "You are still repeating yourself."
msgstr "你還在重複同樣的話。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_52:0
msgid "Stop that game now and answer me!"
msgstr "現在立刻停止那個遊戲，回答我！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_54
msgid "All right. Umar wants me to give you Luthor's ring? And unleash evil on all of Dhayavar?"
msgstr "好吧。烏瑪爾要我把路索爾的戒指交給你？然後釋放邪惡於整個達亞瓦爾？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_54:0
msgid "Why would that ring unleash evil?"
msgstr "那枚戒指為何會釋放邪惡？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_56
msgid "Not the ring itself. But the cave does, if the door is opened."
msgstr "不是戒指本身。但如果門被打開，洞穴會有反應。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_56:0
msgid "That makes even less sense. Explain."
msgstr "這更說不通了。解釋一下。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_58
msgid "Say 'please'."
msgstr "請說「請」。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_58:1
msgid "Never."
msgstr "絕不。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_58:3
msgid "[With rolling eyes] OK - please."
msgstr "【翻白眼】好啦，拜託。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_60
msgid "You might remember Crackshot's hideout, do you?"
msgstr "你應該還記得神射手的藏身處，對吧？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_60:0
msgid "Of course. Behind the many ugly larvals."
msgstr "當然。在那些醜陋幼蟲的背後。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_62
msgid "Good. Do you know why that cave in the back was sealed?"
msgstr "很好。你知道後面那個洞穴為什麼被封住了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_62:0
msgid "No, tell me."
msgstr "不，告訴我。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_70
msgid "A while back, when the Thieves' Guild got successful, we managed to acquire many items of value, including magical items."
msgstr "前陣子，當盜賊公會成功時，我們獲得了許多有價值的物品，包括魔法物品。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_72
msgid "A place was needed to keep them safely. We heard of this deep cave where you met and bested Crackshot."
msgstr ""
"需要一個地方安全地保存它們。我們聽說過這個深洞，你曾在那裡遇見並擊敗了神射手"
"。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_72:0
msgid "That was no easy fight."
msgstr "那可不是場輕鬆的戰鬥。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_72:1
msgid "Phh, child's stuff."
msgstr "哼，小兒科。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_74
msgid "So, when we created that deep cave hideout for our most precious items, we never imagined that the cave held such terrible monsters. While we were exploring, they came and attacked us!"
msgstr ""
"所以，當我們為最珍貴的物品打造那個深邃的洞穴藏身處時，從未想過洞穴裡藏著如此"
"可怕的怪物。當我們在探索時，它們突然襲擊了我們！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_76
msgid "Seraphina suddenly shivers."
msgstr "賽拉菲娜突然顫抖起來。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_80
msgid "We're thieves, not warriors. We tried to escape from there. Lost a few members ..."
msgstr "我們是盜賊，不是戰士。我們試圖從那裡逃脫，失去了幾名成員……"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_82
msgid "Lost Luthor's ring in the cave in the scramble to get out."
msgstr "在逃出洞穴的混亂中遺失了路索爾的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_84
msgid "Still, we managed to hold off the cave monsters, and we managed to seal it."
msgstr "儘管如此，我們還是成功抵擋住洞穴怪物，並封印了它。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_84:0
msgid "Using Luthor's items?"
msgstr "使用路索爾的物品？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_90
msgid "That's right!"
msgstr "沒錯！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_92
msgid "We used Luthor's Key and his gloves to seal it, by creating a magical, impermeable door."
msgstr "我們用路索爾的鑰匙和他的手套封印了它，創造了一扇魔法的、不透水的門。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_94
msgid "Umar and I decided to separate the key and the gloves. And the two of us never meet, to keep that door permanently sealed."
msgstr "烏瑪爾和我決定將鑰匙與手套分開保管。我們兩人永不相見，以確保那扇門永遠封閉。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_94:0
msgid "So that the door may never be opened."
msgstr "以確保此門永不開啟。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_96
msgid "Exactly."
msgstr "沒錯。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_96:0
msgid "But we need to retrieve Luthor's ring now."
msgstr "但我們現在必須取回路索爾的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_100
msgid "Even Umar's current plea will not change my mind. Whatever ails the Guild - find another solution."
msgstr "即使是烏瑪爾現在的懇求也無法改變我的決心。公會出了問題——找其他解決方法。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_120
msgid "Even us thieves are not so callous as to put Dhayavar in danger. You'll never find me."
msgstr "就連我們這些盜賊也不會冷酷到置達亞瓦於險境。你永遠找不到我。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_120:0
msgid "Hey, don't run away!!"
msgstr "嘿，別跑！！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_202
msgid "Watch out, kid. Behind you!"
msgstr "小心，孩子。你身後！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_210
msgid "OK, you're tough, even if not smart, kid."
msgstr "好吧，你很硬朗，雖然不太聰明，孩子。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_210:0
msgid "Thank you?"
msgstr "謝謝你？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_211
msgid "Smart enough to find me, and tough enough to beat my friends. You convinced me that we can do it."
msgstr "夠聰明找到我，也夠強悍打敗我的朋友。你讓我相信我們能做到。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_212
msgid "As we discussed, Luthor's Ring can be found in the secret room which Crackshot tried to open with Luthor's key from Umar."
msgstr ""
"如我們所討論，路索爾的戒指可在神射手試圖用烏瑪爾給的路索爾鑰匙開啟的密室中找"
"到。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_213
msgid "So you have to go and ask Umar for Luthor's key."
msgstr "所以你得去找烏瑪爾要路索爾的鑰匙。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_214
msgid "However, that door can only be opened if you also wear Luthor's gloves, which breaks the spell on it."
msgstr "然而，只有戴上路索爾的手套，才能打開那扇門，解除其上的魔咒。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_214:0
msgid "And the evil you mentioned are monsters, nothing more?"
msgstr "你說的邪惡只是怪物，僅此而已？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_216
msgid "In fact, I didn't take the time to look at them more closely. But they seemed terrible and deadly to me."
msgstr "事實上，我沒仔細看過它們。但它們看起來對我來說既可怕又致命。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_220
msgid "When the door opens, and these strong monsters escape into the open, they will attack Dhayavar, which we must avoid at all costs."
msgstr "當門打開，這些強大的怪物逃出來時，它們會攻擊達亞瓦，我們必須全力避免。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_222
msgid "Which reminds me: Another kid was looking for information to open it."
msgstr "說到這個：另一個孩子正在尋找開啟它的資訊。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_222:0
msgid "That kid, did he look just like me, but older?"
msgstr "那孩子，他看起來是不是跟我一模一樣，只是年紀比較大？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_240
msgid "Come to think of it, he did."
msgstr "仔細想想，他確實有。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_240:0
msgid "[to self] What was Andor trying to do now?"
msgstr "[自言自語] 安多爾現在到底想做什麼？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_250
msgid "Looking at your strength, kid, you may just be able to beat those monsters. We might give it a try."
msgstr "看你這實力，小子，或許真能打敗那些怪物。我們可以試試看。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_250:0
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_250:1
msgid "Thanks again."
msgstr "再次感謝。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_252
msgid "By the way, here's your money back. 1000 gold."
msgstr "順便給你還錢。1000 金幣。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_252:0
msgid "Hmm, OK."
msgstr "嗯，好。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_254
msgid "Meet me at the door to the secret room, and bring Luthor's key. Together with Luthor's gloves the door will open."
msgstr "在秘密房間的門口見我，並帶上路索爾的鑰匙。配合路索爾的手套，門就會打開。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_300
msgid "What did you expect?"
msgstr "你以為會怎樣？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_310
msgid "OK, I admit that you are quite good."
msgstr "好吧，我承認你相當厲害。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_320
msgid "I would actually do a job with you again if the opportunity came up."
msgstr "如果有機會，我真的願意再和你一起工作。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_320:0
msgid "Yes, that would be nice."
msgstr "是的，那會很好。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_330
msgid "And now buzz off, kid. ... $playername."
msgstr "現在滾開，小子。... $playername。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_330:0
msgid "[Grinning] See you."
msgstr "[咧嘴笑] 再見。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_350
msgid "See you."
msgstr "回頭見。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2
msgid "At last! Did you sleep all the way here?"
msgstr "終於到了！你一路上都在睡嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2:0
msgid "Polite as ever."
msgstr "一如既往的有禮。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2_10
msgid "Give me Luthor's key now."
msgstr "現在把路索爾的鑰匙給我。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2_10:0
msgid "Haha, funny. I forgot to bring it."
msgstr "哈哈，好笑。我忘了帶了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2_10:1
msgid "Here it is. Let's do it."
msgstr "給你。開始吧。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2_12
msgid "Seraphina stares at you in disbelief."
msgstr "賽拉菲娜難以置信地盯著你。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2_12:0
msgid "Eh, I'm getting it, I'm running. Just a minute ..."
msgstr "嗯，我明白了，我正在趕來。請稍等一下..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2_14
msgid "Don't you dare to come back without it!"
msgstr "別敢沒帶回來就回來！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2_20
msgid "Seraphina takes the key and easily unlocks the door. As quick as a weasel, she slips into the dark corridor."
msgstr "賽拉菲娜拿起鑰匙，輕鬆打開門。她如黃鼠狼般迅速，滑入黑暗走廊。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly2_20:0
msgid "I had better follow immediately."
msgstr "我最好立刻跟上。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack0b
msgid "Hey kid, stay close behind me! It's going to be dangerous."
msgstr "小子，緊跟著我！前面很危險。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack1_10
msgid "Ha! Take that, skeleton!"
msgstr "哈！給你看看，骷髏！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack1_20
msgid "Just one more hit ..."
msgstr "再多打一下就好..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack1_90
msgid "Finished. Take a quick breather and then move on to the next one ..."
msgstr "完成。稍作休息，然後繼續下一個任務 ..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack1_92
msgid "And keep staying close behind me!"
msgstr "緊跟在我身後！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack2_10
msgid "Bang!!"
msgstr "砰！！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack2_20
msgid "Bang again!!"
msgstr "再來一擊!!"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack2_90
msgid "Pew, it's getting warm. Oh, now there are three of them ..."
msgstr "噗，越來越熱了。喔，現在有三個了……"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack2_92
msgid "Stay close to me!"
msgstr "待在我身邊！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack3_10
msgid "Ha! Move, you lazy bones!"
msgstr "哈！動起來，懶骨頭！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack3_20
msgid "Ouch! That has hurt."
msgstr "哎呦！好痛。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack3_30
msgid "Aaargh!!"
msgstr "啊啊！！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack3_80
msgid "Noo! I can't ... Help! I'm wounded ... Run!"
msgstr "不！我不行了……救命！我受傷了……快跑！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack3_90
msgid "With her last bit of strength, Seraphina leapt past you and fell to the ground."
msgstr "塞拉菲娜用盡最後一絲力氣，跳過你倒在地上。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly_attack4_10
msgid "I'm OK again! I'll help in the search."
msgstr "我又沒事了！我會幫忙搜尋。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly3
msgid "Don't push me. I need to concentrate."
msgstr "別逼我，我需要專心。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_key
msgid "Help ... don't let me die here ..."
msgstr "救命...別讓我死在這裡..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4
msgid "It's good to ... see you are alive, kid."
msgstr "很高興……看到你還活著，孩子。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4:0
msgid "You look terrible."
msgstr "你看起來很糟糕。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4:1
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_2:0
msgid "You are severely wounded."
msgstr "你受了重傷。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4:2
msgid "You look better now."
msgstr "你現在看起來好多了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4:3
msgid "Hey, I'm back. Don't be alarmed, I'll squeeze past you."
msgstr "嘿，我回來了。別緊張，我會從你身邊擠過去。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_2
msgid "Nice compliment, kid. Ooouw ..."
msgstr "不錯的讚美，小子。喔喔喔..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_4
msgid "Yes, thanks to you. Just give me a few seconds ..."
msgstr "是的，多虧了你。給我幾秒鐘……"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10
msgid "Give me some healing potion ... please ..."
msgstr "請給我一些治療藥水……拜託……"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10:0
#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10:1
msgid "Here, have a minor vial of health."
msgstr "給你一小瓶治療藥水。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10:2
msgid "Here, have a potion of health."
msgstr "給你一瓶治療藥水。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10:3
msgid "Here, have a major potion of health."
msgstr "給你一瓶強效治療藥水。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10:4
msgid "Here, have a major flask of health."
msgstr "給你一大瓶強效治療藥水。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10:5
msgid "Here, have a bonemeal potion."
msgstr "給你一瓶骨粉藥水。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10:6
msgid "Here, have a bonemeal potion from Lodar."
msgstr "給你一瓶來自洛達的骨粉藥水。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_10:7
msgid "Here, have this nice potion. [give her a poison potion]"
msgstr "給你這瓶好藥水。[給她一瓶毒藥]"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_12
msgid "That didn't work. My wounds are too deep."
msgstr "那沒用。我的傷太重了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_12:0
msgid "Oh dear, wait, I'll get something different."
msgstr "哎呀，等等，我去拿別的。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_20
msgid "Ahh, that's good. Thank you, kid ... $playername."
msgstr "啊，真好。謝謝你，孩子……$playername。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_20:0
msgid "[Embarrassed] Sure thing."
msgstr "[尷尬] 當然。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_22
msgid "[Spits] What is this stuff?! Throw it away before you drink it yourself. It's rotten."
msgstr "[吐口水] 這是什麼東西？！趕快丟掉，別自己喝了。它壞掉了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_22:0
msgid "So - sorry."
msgstr "真—抱歉。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_24
msgid "You hope that she doesn't notice your guilty conscience."
msgstr "你希望她不會察覺你的愧疚心情。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_24:0
msgid "You are tough."
msgstr "你很堅強。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_30
msgid "Now don't just stand around here. Look lively and find Luthor's ring."
msgstr "別只是站在這裡。快點去找路索爾的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly4_30:0
msgid "Ah, you're back to your old self already."
msgstr "啊，你已經恢復原來的樣子了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5
msgid "Suits me, this place. Don't you think?"
msgstr "我很喜歡這地方，你不覺得嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5:0
msgid "Better help me search."
msgstr "最好幫我找找。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5:1
msgid "[Sarcastic] Truly royal."
msgstr "【諷刺】真是皇室風範。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5:2
msgid "This throne looks familiar to me."
msgstr "這張王座看起來很眼熟。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_2
msgid "Royal, yes."
msgstr "皇室，沒錯。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_3
msgid "In fact, I am King Luthor's heir. He's my ancestor."
msgstr "事實上，我是路索爾王的繼承人。他是我的祖先。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_4
msgid "How else would I be able to wear his gloves without getting hurt?"
msgstr "不然我怎麼戴他的手套而不受傷？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_4:0
msgid "True."
msgstr "沒錯。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_6
msgid "Nothing to be proud of though. Forget it, child. I should have kept quiet about it."
msgstr "不值得驕傲。算了，孩子。我本該閉嘴不提。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_8
msgid "So you've been to King Luthor's tomb. Yes, we have ... borrowed ... his throne."
msgstr "所以你去過路索爾王的陵墓。是的，我們……借用了……他的王座。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_10
msgid "Of course I'll help you. What are you looking for?"
msgstr "當然我會幫你。你在找什麼？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_10:0
msgid "Luthor's ring, of course. I just can't find it."
msgstr "當然是路索爾的戒指。我就是找不到。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_12
msgid "Ah - you are looking for this ring here, am I right?"
msgstr "啊——你是在找這枚戒指，對吧？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_12:0
msgid "What? And I've been searching here for hours!"
msgstr "什麼？我已經在這裡找了好幾個小時了！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_20
msgid "Well, you were so engrossed in the matter that I didn't want to disturb you."
msgstr "嗯，你當時太專注於那件事，我不想打擾你。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_20:0
msgid "[Grumble]"
msgstr "[咕噥]"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_22
msgid "Okay, we're done here. We should get out of here now."
msgstr "好了，我們這裡完成了。現在該離開了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_24
msgid "The monsters will come back. Then the door should be closed and sealed. From the outside."
msgstr "怪物會回來的。那時門應該從外面關閉並封印。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_24:0
msgid "And all the riches?"
msgstr "那所有的財寶呢？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_26
msgid "Don't leave anything here you want to keep. We'll never go back in here."
msgstr "不要留下任何你想保留的東西。我們絕不會再回來這裡。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_30
msgid "Here, catch the ring! Keep it safe and take it to Talion. I'm off."
msgstr "接住這枚戒指！保管好，帶給塔利昂。我先走了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_sly5_32
msgid "A light breeze remains where Seraphina had just been sitting."
msgstr "微風仍在賽拉菲娜剛坐過的地方輕拂。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_start_10
msgid "You enter the Thieves' Guild looking for things to do."
msgstr "你進入盜賊公會尋找可做的事。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_start_10:0
msgid "I am sure that there is another job for me today."
msgstr "我確信今天還有另一份工作等著我。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_start_20
msgid "Happy and expectant, you move on."
msgstr "滿懷喜悅與期待，你繼續前行。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_10
msgid "Oh, that lovely spell! The Striking Spectacle Shadow spell!"
msgstr "喔，那美妙的魔法！震撼的暗影奇觀魔法！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_12
msgid "One of my specials! I just had an opportunity to use it again recently. It went great!"
msgstr "我的必殺技之一！我最近剛有機會再用一次，效果超棒！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_12:0
msgid "Why did you do that? People can get hurt!"
msgstr "你為什麼要那樣做？人會受傷的！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_20
msgid "Nonsense! How can it hurt to be more noticeable? It makes one stand out more, makes one more popular."
msgstr "胡說！變得更顯眼怎麼會有害？這會讓人更突出，更受歡迎。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_20:0
msgid "Not if you want to be a thief or similar."
msgstr "如果你想當盜賊或類似職業，那可不行。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_30
msgid "Why would these so-called thieves approach you?"
msgstr "這些所謂的盜賊為何會接近你？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_30:0
msgid "I'm a kid. No one notices me ..."
msgstr "我只是個孩子。沒有人注意到我..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_40
msgid "That's debatable in your case, but I see the point."
msgstr "這點你未必同意，但我明白你的意思。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_40:0
msgid "Thanks! So, why did you do it?"
msgstr "謝謝！那你為什麼要這麼做？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_50
msgid "Because of the gold! Why else?"
msgstr "因為是為了黃金！還能為了什麼？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_52
msgid "Of course I use it for the church ..."
msgstr "當然我用它來供教會……"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_52:0
msgid "Well, what will it take to remove the spell?"
msgstr "那麼，要怎麼解除這個魔咒？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_60
msgid "Around 50000 gold, of which a large portion will go back to the mysterious Lady Dameni, who had me do the spell. I would need to pacify her, otherwise her toughs will kill me."
msgstr ""
"大約五萬金幣，其中大部分要交給讓我施法的神秘達梅妮女士。我得安撫她，否則她的"
"手下會殺了我。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_60:0
msgid "50000 gold! I hope the guild can reimburse me!"
msgstr "五萬金幣！希望公會能報銷！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_62
msgid "I also need a few more items ..."
msgstr "我還需要幾樣物品..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_62:0
msgid "Which items?"
msgstr "哪些物品？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_64
msgid "Indeed? We'll see. I need the following things:"
msgstr "真的嗎？我們拭目以待。我需要以下物品："

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_70
msgid "Oh, just a few little things, easy to get."
msgstr "喔，只是幾件小事，輕鬆取得。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72
msgid "Villain's ring, Troublemaker's ring, Ring of backstabbing, Tears of the Shadow potion. And most important, Luthor's ring. Together with 50000 gold."
msgstr ""
"反派戒指、麻煩製造者戒指、背刺戒指、暗影之淚藥水。最重要的是，路索爾的戒指。"
"還有五萬金幣。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:0
msgid "You don't ask for much! Where do I find all that?"
msgstr "你要求不多！那我要去哪裡找這些？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:5
msgid "I don't have Luthor's ring yet."
msgstr "我還沒有路索爾的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:6
msgid "I don't have the 50000 gold yet."
msgstr "我還沒有五萬金幣。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:7
msgid "I have everthing other than Luthor's ring"
msgstr "我擁有除了路索爾的戒指以外的一切。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_72:8
msgid "Here's all you have asked for."
msgstr "這就是你所要求的一切。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_74
msgid "Well, then go and find it."
msgstr "那就去找吧。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_75
msgid "By the way, don't come to me with polished rings. The counterspell works with the unmeddled ones only. Hurry now!"
msgstr "順帶一提，別拿拋光過的戒指來找我。反咒只能對未經干預的戒指生效。快點！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_76:0
msgid "Now I am going to find Luthor's ring."
msgstr "現在我要去找路索爾的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_80
msgid "Check with your thief friends, they should know. All these rings form part of your thievery business."
msgstr "問問你的盜賊朋友，他們應該知道。這些戒指都是你盜竊生意的一部分。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_80:0
msgid "Luthor's ring ..."
msgstr "路索爾的戒指 ..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_82
msgid "Yes, this ring might be a little harder to find. I trust in you."
msgstr "是的，這枚戒指可能比較難找。我相信你。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_82:0
msgid "Don't you have any idea where it could be?"
msgstr "你一點頭緒都沒有嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_84
msgid "No. Ask your thief friends."
msgstr "不。問問你的盜賊朋友。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_86
msgid "I said no. Go now, child."
msgstr "我說過不行。現在走，孩子。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_90
msgid "I don't know anybody with that name. Sorry."
msgstr "我不認識那個名字的人，抱歉。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_92
msgid "Did you find the things I asked? Especially Luthor's Ring?"
msgstr "你找到我拜託的東西了嗎？尤其是路索爾的戒指？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_92:0
msgid "That is hard to get. No one knows where it is."
msgstr "那很難取得。沒有人知道它在哪裡。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_94
msgid "Good thieves don't have to search for the things they want. They know where they are."
msgstr "優秀的盜賊不必四處尋找目標，他們知道目標在哪裡。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_94:0
msgid "Can't you cast the counterspell without the ring?"
msgstr "你不能不用戒指施放反咒嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_96
msgid "No ring - no help, sorry."
msgstr "沒戒指，無法幫忙，抱歉。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_98
msgid "Find it or your friends may have to retire or go into another honest business. He he!"
msgstr "找到它，否則你的朋友們可能得退休或轉行做別的正經生意。呵呵！"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_98:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:sullengard_citizen_celdar:0
msgid "Very funny."
msgstr "真有趣。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_100
msgid "Behold - Luthor's ring! And this much gold! I didn't expect that you would manage this so soon."
msgstr "看哪——路索爾的戒指！還有這麼多金幣！我沒想到你這麼快就辦到了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_100:0
msgid "An easy thing for me."
msgstr "對我來說很簡單。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_110
msgid "[muttering] With all that gold and rings I could start a new and wealthy life in Nor City. Hmm ..."
msgstr "[喃喃自語] 有了這些金幣和戒指，我可以在諾爾城開始新的富裕生活。嗯..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_110:0
msgid "You know that I can hear you?"
msgstr "你知道我能聽見你嗎？"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_112
msgid "Eh, well. Now it's time to keep my promise and dispell your friends."
msgstr "嗯，好吧。現在是時候履行我的承諾，驅散你的朋友們了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_112:0
msgid "That sounds better."
msgstr "聽起來好多了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_120
msgid "[muttering strange words]"
msgstr "[喃喃自語奇怪的話]"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_122
msgid "[muttering more strange words]"
msgstr "[喃喃自語更多奇怪的話]"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_124
msgid "[muttering even more strange words]"
msgstr "[喃喃自語更多奇怪的話]"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_130
msgid "Done. Go back to your friends, everything is as it was before."
msgstr "完成。回去找你的朋友，一切如昔。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_130:0
msgid "Great! Thank you."
msgstr "太好了！謝謝你。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_300:0
msgid "The rings. I need them back of course."
msgstr "戒指。我當然需要把它們拿回來。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_310
msgid "Oh no, you don't. And it's not possible."
msgstr "哼，不行的。這不可能。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_320
msgid "I said you don't need the rings. Also it's not possible ..."
msgstr "我說過你不需要那些戒指。而且那也不可能..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_320:0
msgid "OK, it was just a question. Bye."
msgstr "好啦，只是問個問題而已。掰掰。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_320:1
msgid "I'll show you what's possible ..."
msgstr "我會讓你見識可能性..."

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_330
msgid "[Hasty] Now here is Luthor's ring. It is the only one that was powerfull enough to survive the spell. The others are broken."
msgstr ""
"[匆忙] 這就是路索爾的戒指。它是唯一足夠強大能夠承受魔咒的戒指。其他的都已破碎"
"。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_330:0
msgid "Hmm, thanks."
msgstr "嗯，謝謝。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_talion_132
msgid "[to himself] I hope."
msgstr "[自言自語] 我希望如此。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_tahalendor_10
msgid "Eh, what? Better ask Yolgen."
msgstr "欸，什麼？還是問問約爾根吧。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_thoronir_10
msgid "You must be confusing me with someone else."
msgstr "你一定是認錯人了。"

#: conversationlist_troubling_times.json:tt_yolgen_10
msgid "I don't understand ... What are you talking about?"
msgstr "我不明白……你在說什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis
msgid "Hello, $playername"
msgstr "你好，$playername"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_5
msgid "Begone, you Feygard lackey! I refuse to talk to you! You reek of Feygard!"
msgstr "滾開，你這妖境走狗！我拒絕跟你說話！你身上散發著妖境的氣息！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_5:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_7:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_8:0
msgid "I ... eh ... what?"
msgstr "我……呃……什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_6
msgid "Begone!"
msgstr "滾開！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_7
msgid "You have betrayed our work by telling the truth about Beer Bootlegging from Sullengard. At least you did the right thing when you provided the Feygardians with bad weapons. So I'll let it go this time."
msgstr ""
"你背叛了我們的計劃，洩露了蘇倫加德的啤酒走私真相。至少你在提供妖境人劣質武器"
"時做了正確的事。這次我就放你一馬。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_8
msgid "You have betrayed our work by providing the Feygardians with weapons. At least you did the right thing when you didn't tell the truth about the Beer Bootlegging from Sullengard. So I'll let it go this time."
msgstr ""
"你背叛了我們的工作，向妖境人提供了武器。至少你在沒有透露蘇倫加德的啤酒走私真"
"相時做了正確的事。所以這次我就放你一馬。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_10
msgid "Shadow bless you, child!"
msgstr "暗影祝福你，孩子！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_10:0
msgid "And you, sir!"
msgstr "你也是，先生！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_20
msgid "A very polite kid! Plus, as the Shadow has been whispering to me, a helpful one."
msgstr "一個非常有禮貌的孩子！而且，正如暗影一直在對我耳語的那樣，他還很有幫助。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_22
msgid "Listen, do you want help the Shadow?"
msgstr "聽著，你想幫助暗影嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_22:0
msgid "That depends on what you want me to do."
msgstr "那要看你想讓我做什麼。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_30
msgid "A cautious one! Capital!"
msgstr "小心謹慎的！資本家！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_40
msgid "Listen carefully - you have met many of us Shadow priests across Dhayavar. But, not all of us are equal."
msgstr "仔細聽——你在達亞瓦爾遇過許多暗影祭司，但我們並非全然相同。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_40:0
msgid "You mean, there are priests more powerful than you?"
msgstr "你的意思是，有比你更強大的牧師？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_50
msgid "Er ... well ... not exactly what I mean."
msgstr "嗯……嗯……不完全是我的意思。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_52
msgid "What I mean is this: there seems to be a priest who thinks the Shadow calls for the conquest of Dhayavar!"
msgstr "我的意思是：似乎有位牧師認為暗影召喚征服達亞瓦爾！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_52:0
msgid "That's terrible!"
msgstr "太糟了！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_60
msgid "And I need your help to stop him!"
msgstr "我需要你的幫助阻止他！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_60:0
msgid "Why? You can't take him on? Not powerful enough?"
msgstr "為什麼？你無法對付他？實力不夠？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_70
msgid "No! Not that! To stop him, one needs a Shadow warrior, like you!"
msgstr "不！不是那個！要阻止他，需要像你這樣的暗影戰士！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_70:0
msgid "Me a Shadow warrior! OK, what do I need to do?"
msgstr "我是暗影戰士！好，我需要做什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_80
msgid "That's the spirit!"
msgstr "就是這股氣勢！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_82
msgid "Now, in the wasteland south of Stoutford, there have been reports of some suspicious activities."
msgstr "現在，在斯托福德南方的荒原上，有一些可疑活動的報告。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_84
msgid "I fear it is my fellow priest summoning monsters to conquer all of Dhayavar. If it is not stopped, we might see lots of really unstoppable monsters popping up all over Dhayavar."
msgstr ""
"我擔心是我的同袍祭司召喚怪物，意圖征服整個達亞瓦爾。如果不阻止，整個達亞瓦爾"
"可能會出現大量無法阻擋的怪物。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_84:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_92:0
msgid "I'll kill them all!"
msgstr "我會殺光他們！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_90
msgid "Brave - but only few in Dhayavar have the skills to go toe-to-toe against these monsters."
msgstr "勇敢——但在達亞瓦爾，只有少數人有能力與這些怪物正面交鋒。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_92
msgid "We must stop them at the source."
msgstr "我們必須從源頭阻止他們。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_92:0
msgid "Yes, but what can we do?"
msgstr "是的，但我們能做什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_100
msgid "Journey to the south of Stoutford, into the forests there. See what that Shadow priest is doing there, and stop him from doing it."
msgstr "前往斯托福德南部的森林，看看那個暗影祭司在做什麼，阻止他。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_150
msgid "Ah, you're back!  Don't tell me you have defeated the renegade priest already? Not that I detected any change in the Shadow energies, which are in turmoil."
msgstr ""
"啊，你回來了！別告訴我你已經擊敗了叛教的牧師？不過我並未察覺暗影能量有任何變"
"化，它們正處於動盪中。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_150:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_200:0
msgid "There's some sort of force shield blocking the path."
msgstr "有某種力場擋住了道路。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_152:0
msgid "I found some stones with strange markings on them."
msgstr "我發現了一些刻有奇異符號的石頭。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_154
msgid "With strange markings? Hmm. Show me."
msgstr "有奇怪的符號？嗯，給我看看。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_154:0
msgid "I don't have any of these stones."
msgstr "我沒有這些石頭。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_156
msgid "No? You didn't think of the obvious idea that I should see them?"
msgstr "沒有？你沒想到我應該去見他們這個明顯的主意嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_156:0
msgid "Unfortunately the stones could not be picked up or moved - as if they had some kind of energy in them."
msgstr "可惜這些石頭無法被撿起或移動——彷彿蘊含某種能量。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_160
msgid "That sounds like a Shadow shield! Used to protect our incantations from outside interference, like those Feygard interferers."
msgstr "那聽起來像是暗影護盾！用來保護我們的咒語不受外界干擾，就像那些妖境的干擾者。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_160:0
msgid "But can't it recognize I am Shadow warrior, as you say, and let me pass?"
msgstr "但它不能識別我如你所說是暗影戰士，讓我通過嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_162:0
msgid "But of course it would let you pass, wouldn't it?"
msgstr "但當然它會讓你通過，不是嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_170
msgid "Kid, the world is more complex than you might think with that small brain of yours."
msgstr "小子，這世界比你那小腦袋想的還複雜。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_172
msgid "A Shadow shield is a very basic shield, even if strong. It keeps everyone out after it is cast."
msgstr "暗影盾是一種非常基本的盾牌，即使堅固。施放後能阻擋所有人。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_174
msgid "Those small stones are shadow wards. They need to be neutralized"
msgstr "那些小石頭是暗影護符。需要將它們中和。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_174:0
msgid "But how?"
msgstr "但是怎麼做？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_180
msgid "Let me conjure a chant. I'll need some Shadow energies for that."
msgstr "讓我念一段咒語。為此我需要一些暗影能量。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_180:0
msgid "Shadow what?"
msgstr "暗影什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_181
msgid "Sorry. Of course you can't have knowledge of such things."
msgstr "抱歉，你當然不可能知道這種事。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_182
msgid "Shadow priests can create and give energies in form of blessings to one."
msgstr "暗影牧師能以祝福的形式賜予能量給他人。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_184
msgid "You need get and carry those energies to me. I'll use them to create a chant to take down the Shadow shield."
msgstr "你需要取得並帶來那些能量給我。我會用它們創造一個咒語來擊破暗影護盾。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_184:0
msgid "OK. Now what exactly do I ask for? And from whom?"
msgstr "好。那我到底該問什麼？又該問誰？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_190
msgid "You'll need to get me the blessings of Shadow's Strength, Shadow Sleepiness, Fatigue and Life Drain. Through yourself."
msgstr "你需要為我帶來暗影之力、暗影昏睡、疲勞與生命吸取的祝福。親自來。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_190:0
msgid "Through myself?"
msgstr "透過我自己？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_192:0
msgid "That'll make things harder."
msgstr "那會讓事情更難。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_200
msgid "This is the only way! Now, be a Shadow warrior! Go fetch them."
msgstr "這是唯一的道路！現在，成為暗影戰士！去把他們帶回來。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_200:0
msgid "Sigh. From where?"
msgstr "嘆。從哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_210
msgid "Go to my friend Talion in Loneford. He'll give you the blessing of Shadow's Strength."
msgstr "前往孤城的好友塔利昂，他會賜予你暗影之力的祝福。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_212
msgid "Also he can tell you where to find the others."
msgstr "他也能告訴你其他人的下落。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_250
msgid "It took you a while. I thought you had given up."
msgstr "你花了不少時間。我還以為你放棄了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_250:0
msgid "[panting] Here are your energies, Borvis. I'm exhausted!"
msgstr "[喘息] 這是你的能量，博維斯。我累壞了！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_260
msgid "Great! Let me quickly extract them from you."
msgstr "太好了！讓我快速從你身上提取。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_260:0
msgid "[Weak voice] Please do."
msgstr "[虛弱的聲音] 請。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_264
msgid "Borvis examines you."
msgstr "博維斯審視著你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_266
msgid "Oh you useless kid!"
msgstr "哎，你這沒用的孩子！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_267
msgid "You didn't get them all! Go get the missing ones right now!"
msgstr "你還沒全拿到！快去把缺的都找回來！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_270
msgid "Borvis did many obscure things, chanting all the way. But you were too tired to follow and dozed."
msgstr "博維斯做了許多奇怪的事，一路上都在吟唱。但你太累了，跟不上，便打盹了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_272
msgid "Suddenly you wake up, completely refreshed."
msgstr "突然你醒來，神清氣爽。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_272:0
msgid "Ah! I feel like I could tear down trees!"
msgstr "啊！我感覺自己能連樹都拔起來！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_280
msgid "While you slept I've prepared a tiny chant that nevertheless will destroy the Shadow shield. Here, read it."
msgstr "當你沉睡時，我準備了一段微小的咒語，卻能摧毀暗影護盾。來，念給你聽。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_280:0
msgid "This little thing?"
msgstr "這小東西？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_290
msgid "Go now and destroy the shield, and then the renegade priest. Make haste!"
msgstr "現在前去摧毀護盾，然後消滅叛教神父。速速行動！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_500
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_500
msgid "It's not done yet. Can you talk to this priest? And tackle him as he deserves?"
msgstr "還沒完成。你能跟這位牧師談談嗎？還有好好教訓他一頓？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_500:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_502:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_500:0
msgid "Of course! On my way!"
msgstr "當然！馬上來！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_500:1
msgid "Why not you?"
msgstr "為什麼不是你？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_502
msgid "You'll be faster. Don't worry, I'll follow you."
msgstr "你會更快的。別擔心，我會跟著你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_540
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_540
msgid "The monster is not dead. Go and finish it!"
msgstr "怪物還沒死。快去收尾！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_550
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_550
msgid "Finally. Well done, kid."
msgstr "終於。幹得好，孩子。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_550:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_550:0
msgid "Is it over?"
msgstr "結束了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_560
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_560
msgid "This is over, yes."
msgstr "這結束了，是的。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_562
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_562
msgid "And now for your reward."
msgstr "現在是你的獎勵時間。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_562:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_562:0
msgid "Yes? Hope it is worth it."
msgstr "是嗎？希望值得。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_570
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_570
msgid "You are still looking for your brother?"
msgstr "你還在找你的兄弟嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_580
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_580
msgid "I know where he is. Or better, where he will be soon."
msgstr "我知道他在哪裡。或者更確切地說，他很快就會出現的地方。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_580:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_580:0
msgid "Really? Tell me!"
msgstr "真的嗎？告訴我！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_590
msgid "Andor is going to visit Alynndir to refill his travel supplies."
msgstr "安多爾將前往艾林迪爾補充他的旅行物資。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_590:1
msgid "Who is Alynndir?"
msgstr "阿林迪爾是誰？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_592
msgid "Alynndir lives in a lonely house down the road to Nor City. Don't you know?"
msgstr "艾林迪爾住在通往諾爾城路上的一間孤寂小屋。你不知道嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_borvis_600
msgid "Isn't it a lovely day?"
msgstr "今天天氣真好，不是嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_10
msgid "Oh, it's good that you said that."
msgstr "喔，幸好你這麼說。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_12
msgid "Then I have to slightly modify the chant so that it stays fresh and will still work after your long journey."
msgstr "那我得稍微修改咒語，讓它保持新鮮感，並在你長途跋涉後仍能奏效。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_20
msgid "Very well. [starts chanting]"
msgstr "很好。[開始吟唱]"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_30
msgid "There. I hope Borvis knows what he is doing."
msgstr "好了。希望博維斯知道自己在做什麼。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_30:0
msgid "Thank you. Bye"
msgstr "謝謝，再見"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_30:1
msgid "Thank you. And I need to ask you something."
msgstr "謝謝你。我有件事想問你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_30:2
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_50:0
msgid "Where can I receive blessings of Shadow Sleepiness, Fatigue and Life Drain?"
msgstr "我在哪裡可以獲得暗影睡意、疲勞和生命吸取的祝福？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_40
msgid "How about a word of thanks first?"
msgstr "先說聲謝謝如何？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_42
msgid "Oh times, oh customs. These ill-behaved children these days..."
msgstr "唉，時代變了，風俗也變了。如今這些不成器的孩子……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_44
msgid "Well, you see - was that really so difficult?"
msgstr "你看——真的有那麼難嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_50
msgid "Just tell me what you need to know."
msgstr "只要告訴我你想知道什麼。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_60
msgid "Why do you need all those? I hope you are not helping the Shadow's enemies get through a Shadow shield!"
msgstr "你為什麼需要這些？我希望你不是在幫助暗影的敵人突破暗影護盾！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_60:0
msgid "No, of course not!"
msgstr "不，當然不是！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_62
msgid "Then what for? Speak!"
msgstr "那是為了什麼？說！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_62:0
msgid "Borvis wants my help in breaking a Shadow shield in the south of Stoutford. He says someone is misusing Shadow powers behind the Shield."
msgstr "博維斯想讓我幫忙破解斯托福德南方的暗影護盾。他說有人在護盾背後濫用暗影力量。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_70
msgid "Sending a kid to do a priest's job! Isn't Borvis strong enough?"
msgstr "派小孩去做牧師的工作！博維斯不夠強嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_72
msgid "Very well. Go to my friend Jolnor for Shadow Sleepiness. Rest you get even in spite of bad dreams - but not permanently, and potion effects don't help."
msgstr ""
"很好。去找我的朋友喬爾諾爾，尋求暗影昏睡。即使有惡夢，你仍能休息——但不會是永"
"久的，藥水效果也無濟於事。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_72:0
msgid "Right. I got that ... I think."
msgstr "對。 我懂了……我想是這樣。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_74
msgid "Ask Jolnor of Vilegard."
msgstr "詢問維雷加德的喬爾諾爾。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_80
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_130
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_90
msgid "That's no problem at all."
msgstr "一點也不麻煩。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_80:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_130:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_90:0
msgid "I'm glad about that."
msgstr "我很高興。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_82
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_132
msgid "It'll just cost you another 300 gold pieces."
msgstr "這將花費你額外的300金幣。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_82:0
msgid "If that's all - here you go."
msgstr "如果沒其他事——給你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_82:1
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_132:1
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_92:1
msgid "I don't have that much with me. I'll be back."
msgstr "我身上沒帶那麼多。馬上回來。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_10
msgid "I don't provide any blessings."
msgstr "我不提供任何祝福。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_10:0
msgid "But Talion said that you could."
msgstr "但塔利昂說你可以。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_20
msgid "Oh, you mean Shadow Sleepiness?"
msgstr "哦，你是指暗影昏睡嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_22
msgid "So Talion still can't tell a blessing from a spell."
msgstr "所以塔利昂還分不清祝福和魔法。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_24
msgid "He never could."
msgstr "他從未能做到。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_24:0
msgid "Now what?"
msgstr "接下來呢？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_26
msgid "If Talion says - OK, it's yours for only 300 gold. Though it's not a blessing as such..."
msgstr "如果塔利昂說 - 好的，只要300金幣，這就是你的了。雖然這不算是祝福……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_26:1
msgid "That is too much. I'd offer you 50 gold at the most."
msgstr "那太多了。我最多出價50金幣。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_26:2
msgid "300? I have to get some gold first."
msgstr "300？我得先湊點金幣。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_28
msgid "Your choice. Come again, when you are wiser."
msgstr "隨你便。等你更有智慧時再來。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_50
msgid "What do you want it for?"
msgstr "你要它做什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_50:0
msgid "Well, Borvis wanted it to break through a Shadow shield, as someone is misusing Shadow powers to the south of Stoutford."
msgstr "嗯，博維斯想讓它突破暗影護盾，因為有人在斯托福德南方濫用暗影力量。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_60
msgid "Tsk! Tsk! Not strong enough, is he? Sending a kid to do a priest's duty?"
msgstr "啧啧！他不夠強嗎？派個小孩來做牧師的事？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_62
msgid "Well, give me the 300 gold."
msgstr "好，給我300金幣。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_62:0
msgid "Sure, here."
msgstr "當然，給你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_70
msgid "Jolnor is chanting, murmuring, gesticulating."
msgstr "喬爾諾爾正在吟唱、低語、比劃。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_70:0
msgid "[Thinking to himself] He's probably just doing this to distract me so I can't figure out how to do it."
msgstr "[心想] 他大概只是想分散我的注意力，讓我無法想出辦法。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_80
msgid "Here you go. Take it to Borvis with care."
msgstr "給你。小心帶給博維斯。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_80:1
msgid "Please, I still have a question."
msgstr "請問，我還有個問題。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_100
msgid "Well, ask away."
msgstr "那就問吧。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_100:0
msgid "Can you also give 'blessings' of Fatigue and Life Drain"
msgstr "你也能賜予「疲勞」和「生命吸取」的祝福嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_110
msgid "Borvis can't even manage those?! How unworthy!"
msgstr "博維斯連那些都搞不定？！真不堪！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_110:0
msgid "Well, could you?"
msgstr "那，你能嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_112
msgid "Of course I could, if I wanted to."
msgstr "當然可以，如果我願意的話。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_120
msgid "There's one priest, Favlon, who can give you both. However, he went researching in the area west of Sullengard and hasn't been seen since."
msgstr ""
"有一位牧師，法夫隆，可以同時給你兩者。不過，他前往蘇倫加德西方地區調查，從此"
"未曾現身。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_jolnor_120:0
msgid "West of Sullengard. Sigh."
msgstr "蘇倫加德以西。嘆。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_talion_132:0
msgid "Sure, I am wealthy enough."
msgstr "當然，我很富有。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_2
msgid "Ah, my brave Shadow warrior. I hope you could help Borvis."
msgstr "啊，我勇敢的暗影戰士。希望你能幫助博維斯。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_2:1
msgid "Yes, we have saved the world."
msgstr "是的，我們拯救了世界。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_2:2
msgid "Your 'blessings' has worn off too early. Could you give them again?"
msgstr "你的「祝福」效果太早消失了。可以再給一次嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_10
msgid "By the Shadow - a kid! Here? How? Why?"
msgstr "是暗影——一個孩子！在這裡？怎麼會？為什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_10:0
msgid "Jolnor sent me to find you here."
msgstr "喬爾諾爾派我來這裡找你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_12
msgid "He did?"
msgstr "他真的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_12:0
msgid "Borvis wants me to help him take care of a renegade Shadow priest. So, he asked me to get some 'blessings' - of which I need Fatigue and Life Drain."
msgstr ""
"博維斯想讓我幫他對付一名叛逃的暗影牧師。所以，他叫我去取得一些「祝福」——我需"
"要疲勞和生命吸取。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_14
msgid "And Jolnor says I can bestow them?"
msgstr "喬爾諾爾說我可以賜予他們？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_14:0
msgid "Exactly. I need Fatigue and Life Drain."
msgstr "沒錯。我需要疲勞和生命吸取。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_20
msgid "Is Borvis that weak that he can't get them himself?"
msgstr "博維斯真的那麼弱，連自己都抓不到他們嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_20:0
msgid "He said a Shadow warrior is needed, not a Shadow priest."
msgstr "他說需要的是暗影戰士，不是暗影牧師。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_30
msgid "A likely story!"
msgstr "真是個可信的故事！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_30:0
msgid "So you can't do it?"
msgstr "所以你做不到嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_40
msgid "No insults, please. Of course I can!"
msgstr "請勿侮辱。當然可以！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_42
msgid "Do you have any cooked meat? I've been living on berries for so long, some meat can give me strength."
msgstr "你有熟肉嗎？我已經靠漿果活了很久，吃點肉能讓我恢復力氣。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_42:0
msgid "How many do you need?"
msgstr "你需要多少？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_44
msgid "Ten should be enough."
msgstr "十個應該足夠了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_44:0
msgid "OK, I have it here."
msgstr "好的，我拿到了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_44:1
msgid "I have to fetch some."
msgstr "我得去取一些。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_50
msgid "I'll eat while I work the chants. You are sure that you still want them?"
msgstr "我邊吃邊念咒。你確定還要嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_50:0
msgid "Yes, I'm sure."
msgstr "是的，我確定。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_50:1
msgid "Maybe I'd better think about it again."
msgstr "也許我應該再好好想想。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_60
msgid "Here you go. Take them to Borvis with care."
msgstr "給你。小心帶他們去博維斯。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_60:1
msgid "Ugh! What a terrible feeling. Thanks nevertheless."
msgstr "唉！真是糟透的感覺。不過還是謝謝你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_70
msgid "Take care! The return journey will be dangerous"
msgstr "小心！回程將充滿危險"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_70:0
msgid "See you!"
msgstr "再見！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_80
msgid "[Muttering] Sending a kid to do a priest's job?! How lazy!"
msgstr "[喃喃] 派小孩去做牧師的事？！真懶！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_92
msgid "It'll just cost you another 10 cooked meat."
msgstr "你只需再付10塊熟肉。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_favlon_92:0
msgid "Sure. Here, enjoy."
msgstr "當然。給你，請享用。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor
msgid "Hey, who's that running over?"
msgstr "嘿，那個跑過來的是誰？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_10
msgid "Hello, $playername, is it really you? You have grown."
msgstr "你好，$playername，真的是你嗎？你長大了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_10:0
msgid "I've finally found you!"
msgstr "我終於找到你了！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_20
msgid "Why? Did you miss me so much? Or do you not want to have to do Mikhail's work all by yourself?"
msgstr "為什麼？你這麼想我嗎？還是你不想獨自承擔米哈伊爾的工作？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_20:0
msgid "Don't talk nonsense. I'm glad to see you. Come home with me."
msgstr "別胡說。我很高興見到你。跟我回家吧。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_30
msgid "I can't. At least not yet."
msgstr "我不能。至少現在還不行。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_30:0
msgid "But why? Does someone want to do something bad to you? I won't allow that."
msgstr "但為什麼？有人想對你不利嗎？我不會允許的。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_40
msgid "[Andor laughs dryly] Let it go, it's the big brother's job to keep an eye on things."
msgstr "[安多爾乾笑] 算了，這是大哥的責任，盯著點。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_50
msgid "No. It's not possible. You'll understand that one day."
msgstr "不，這不可能。你總有一天會明白的。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_50:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_50:1
msgid "Are you just going to disappear again? Please don't!"
msgstr "你又要消失了嗎？拜託不要！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_andor_62
msgid "Don't worry - we'll see each other again, in happier days."
msgstr "別擔心——我們會在更幸福的日子再相見。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_10
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_110
msgid "I have never seen such a barrier."
msgstr "我從未見過這樣的屏障。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_10:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_110:0
msgid "I should examine it further. Maybe I can find a way into it?"
msgstr "我應該進一步檢查。或許能找到進入的方法？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_10:1
msgid "I should tell Miri of all this."
msgstr "我應該把這一切告訴米莉。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_20
msgid "You stumble upon a piece of paper."
msgstr "你發現一張紙條。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_20:0
msgid "Oh, I have seen this paper before. It is a part of the Kazaul ritual! I should talk to Miri about all this."
msgstr "喔，我以前見過這張紙。這是卡札爾儀式的一部分！我應該跟米莉談談這些事。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_50
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_150
msgid "The barrier feels rather massive."
msgstr "這道屏障感覺相當巨大。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_50:0
msgid "I'm here. Miri isn't. Well, I can't wait. Let's chant."
msgstr "我在這裡。米莉不在。好吧，我等不及了。開始念咒吧。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_52
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_152
msgid "As soon as you have finished, the barrier fades away."
msgstr "一完成，結界便消失。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_110:1
msgid "I should tell Borvis of all this."
msgstr "我應該把這一切告訴博維斯。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_120
msgid "Near the shield you find some small black stones with strange markings. The stones seem to be fixed and can't be moved."
msgstr "在盾牌附近，你發現一些帶有奇異符號的小黑石。這些石頭似乎固定著，無法移動。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_120:0
msgid "Oh, these stones look weird. The markings even seem to glow a bit. Are they the cause of this barrier? I should talk to Borvis about all this."
msgstr ""
"喔，這些石頭看起來很奇怪。上面的符號還微微發光。難道它們是這道屏障的原因？我"
"應該跟博維斯談談這件事。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_shadow_150:0
msgid "I'm here. Borvis isn't. Well, I can't wait. Let's chant."
msgstr "我在這裡。博維斯不在。好吧，我等不及了。開始吟唱吧。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_spawn2_10
msgid "Oh, a new guest in this sad establishment."
msgstr "喔，這悲涼場所來了新客人。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_spawn2_20
msgid "Hey, Miri is back at last."
msgstr "嘿，米莉終於回來了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_5
msgid "Ah, one of the kids who've been causing trouble around Dhayavar."
msgstr "啊，是在達亞瓦爾惹麻煩的那些孩子之一。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_5:0
msgid "Oh, you know of me?"
msgstr "哦，你認識我？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_10
msgid "Yes, I know of you. And a little about what your brother has been up to."
msgstr "是的，我知道你，也稍微了解你兄弟最近的行蹤。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_10:0
msgid "Tell me please."
msgstr "請告訴我。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_20
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_30
msgid "Information is for the trustworthy."
msgstr "資訊只給值得信賴的人。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_22
msgid "By switching Gandoren's shipment with degraded ones, you have proved not to be. Suffice to say, when I was last there I heard your brother has been up to shenanigans in Feygard."
msgstr ""
"透過將甘多倫的貨物換成劣質品，你已證明並非如此。話說回來，上次我去那裡時，聽"
"說你兄弟在妖境惹了麻煩。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_22:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_32:0
msgid "How would you know that I did such things?"
msgstr "你怎麼會知道我做過那種事？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_25
msgid "As an investigator, it's my job to know. Now, buzz off, kid. Redeem yourself, if you can."
msgstr "作為調查員，我的工作就是知道真相。現在，滾開，小子。能的話，就證明你自己。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_32
msgid "By hiding the truth of the beer bootlegging from Sullengard, you have proved not to be. Suffice to say, when I was last there I heard your brother has been up to shenanigans in Feygard."
msgstr ""
"隱瞞蘇倫加德啤酒走私的真相，證明你並非如此。話說回來，我上次去那裡時聽說你兄"
"弟在妖境惹了麻煩。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_40
msgid "Information is for a price."
msgstr "資訊是有代價的。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_42
msgid "You've aided Feygard once before. Now, investigate something for me. If you succeed, I'll tell you what I know of Andor."
msgstr ""
"你曾經幫助過妖境一次。現在，幫我調查一件事。如果你成功，我會告訴你我所知道的"
"安多爾。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_42:0
msgid "So, what do you want from me?"
msgstr "那麼，你想從我這裡得到什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_50
msgid "While investigating the forests east of Sullengard, slitherers got to me. Nasty little slitherers. Damned beasts."
msgstr "在蘇倫加德東邊的森林調查時，被那些滑行者襲擊了。討厭的小滑行者。該死的野獸。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_52
msgid "I need to recover from the nausea and poison."
msgstr "我需要從噁心和中毒中恢復。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_52:0
msgid "Can I help you with some potions?"
msgstr "需要我幫你準備一些藥水嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_60
msgid "No, thanks. I've already taken some potions, and I'm waiting for them to take effect."
msgstr "不，謝謝。我已經喝了幾瓶藥水，正在等待生效。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_70
msgid "But there's something bad happening in the lands south of Stoutford, and if we don't stop it, not only Feygard, but the whole of Dhayavar will be in trouble."
msgstr ""
"但在斯托福德南方的土地上正發生著不祥之事，如果我們不阻止，不僅妖境，整個達亞"
"瓦爾都將陷入危機。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_70:0
msgid "So what's new?"
msgstr "有什麼新鮮事？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_80
msgid "Yeah - many weird things going on. But no time to waste."
msgstr "是啊——發生了很多奇怪的事。但沒時間浪費。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_90
msgid "In the lands south of Stoutford, there have been reports of some suspicious activities. It is said to happen in the Purple Hills there."
msgstr ""
"在斯托福德以南的土地上，有關於一些可疑活動的報告。據說這些事情發生在那裡的紫"
"色山丘。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_92
msgid "I fear if left unchecked, we might see lots of really unstoppable monsters popping up all over Dhayavar."
msgstr "我擔心若不加以控制，整個達亞瓦爾將會出現大量真正無法阻擋的怪物。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_100
msgid "Admirable - but only few in Dhayavar have the skills to go toe-to-toe against these monsters. No, we must stop them at the source."
msgstr ""
"令人欽佩——但在達亞瓦爾，只有少數人有能力與這些怪物正面交鋒。不，我們必須從源"
"頭阻止它們。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_100:0
msgid "So, what do we do?"
msgstr "那麼，我們該怎麼做？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_110
msgid "Journey to the south of Stoutford, into the weird lands there. Investigate what's going on in the Purple Hills."
msgstr "前往斯托福德南方，進入那片詭異之地。調查紫丘發生的異狀。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_110:0
msgid "OK, I'm off. Stoutford ... I haven't been there in a long time ..."
msgstr "好，我走了。斯托福德……我很久沒去了……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_110:1
msgid "The Purple Hills?"
msgstr "紫色山丘？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_112
msgid "Head south through Stoutford. The Purple Hills lie between the lake region and the mountains further south."
msgstr "向南穿過斯托福德。紫色山丘位於湖區與更南方的山脈之間。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_114
msgid "You could also go west from Sullengard, but the route is longer."
msgstr "你也可以從蘇倫加德向西走，但路程較長。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_114:0
msgid "And how do I know that I am there?"
msgstr "我怎麼知道我已經到了？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_116
msgid "That's easy. The Purple Hills aren't just called that; they really have that color."
msgstr "這很簡單。紫色山丘不只是名字，它們真的就是那個顏色。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_200
msgid "Ah, you're back. Too soon - did you run into any issue?"
msgstr "啊，你回來了。太快了——遇到什麼問題了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_202
msgid "And? There must be more to it."
msgstr "然後呢？一定還有更多。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_202:0
msgid "I haven't seen anything suspicious."
msgstr "我沒看到任何可疑的東西。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_202:1
msgid "And I found this piece of Kazaul ritual again."
msgstr "我又找到了這塊卡札爾儀式碎片。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_204
msgid "Search thoroughly around this force shield to find anything unusual."
msgstr "仔細搜尋這道力場周圍，找出任何異常。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_210
msgid "What do you mean - again?"
msgstr "你說什麼——又來一次？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_210:0
msgid "When I was at the Blackwater settlement, I had used this, on the guidance of Throdna, as part of purifying the Kazaul shrine."
msgstr "當我在黑水定居點時，曾依照索羅德納的指引，使用這個來淨化卡札爾神殿。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_220
msgid "That is bad news indeed. We must act."
msgstr "這確實是壞消息。我們必須採取行動。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_222
msgid "Go meet Throdna. Since he's known to ramble, just say 'Kazaul est' to focus him again."
msgstr "去見索羅德納。因為他愛絮叨，只要說「卡札爾在」就能讓他重新專注。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_222:0
msgid "'Kazaul est.'"
msgstr "「卡札爾已然降臨」"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_224
msgid "Exactly. Hurry now."
msgstr "沒錯。快點。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_300
msgid "What did you find out from Throdna?"
msgstr "你從索羅德納那裡得知了什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_300:0
msgid "We talked about the rest of the spell to break the barrier for Kazaul."
msgstr "我們討論了剩下的魔法來破除卡札爾的屏障。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_300:1
msgid "Apart from two parts of the spell which I know, the rest of the spell to break the barrier for Kazaul is in the book Calomyran Secrets."
msgstr ""
"除了我知道的咒語兩部分外，破解卡札爾屏障的其餘咒語都記載在《卡洛米蘭秘辛》一"
"書中。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_302
msgid "[Rolling eyes] That's not much. Go, talk to Throdna again."
msgstr "[翻白眼] 那不多。去，再跟索羅德納說說話。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_310
msgid "Where can this book be found?"
msgstr "這本書在哪裡可以找到？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_310:0
msgid "I know! I helped find this book for that old man in Fallhaven. He must still have it. Let me talk to him."
msgstr "我知道！我幫墜港鎮那個老頭找過這本書。他一定還有。讓我去跟他談談。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_310:1
msgid "I have already visited the owner in Fallhaven."
msgstr "我已經拜訪過墜港鎮的店主。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_320
msgid "Good thinking! Do that, seek the old man with the book."
msgstr "好主意！去找那位有書的老人。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_350
msgid "Any news about the Calomyran Secrets?"
msgstr "有關卡洛米蘭秘辛的消息嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_350:1
msgid "I got more of the chant but I need to find another book, Azimyran Secrets, for the rest of the chant."
msgstr ""
"我已經得到更多咒語，但我還需要找到另一本書《阿齊米蘭祕密》，才能完成剩下的咒"
"語。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_360
msgid "Where can that book be found?"
msgstr "那本書在哪裡可以找到？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_370
msgid "No worries. I'm healed enough now."
msgstr "別擔心，我現在已經恢復得差不多了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_372
msgid "You have run around enough. Let me ask around. Why don't you rest? Stroll around outside a bit to refresh!"
msgstr "你已經跑夠了。讓我問問看。你為什麼不休息一下？到外面走走，放鬆一下吧！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_400
msgid "Hi $playername, I'm back."
msgstr "嗨 $playername，我回來了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_400:0
msgid "Did you find anything?"
msgstr "有找到什麼嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_410
msgid "About the Azimyran Secrets? Yes, my sources were most informative"
msgstr "關於阿齊米蘭的秘密？是的，我的消息來源非常詳盡。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_420
msgid "There's an Old Hermit who lives in the mountains south of Remgard."
msgstr "雷姆加德南方山脈有位隱士。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_422
msgid "You know, at the old watch tower. The Hermit is said to have a copy of Azimyran Secrets. Go ..."
msgstr "你知道嗎，在舊瞭望塔。據說隱士擁有一份《阿茲米蘭秘典》的副本。去吧..."

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_422:0
msgid "Go and get it?"
msgstr "去拿吧？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_428
msgid "Yes! Go and get it."
msgstr "是的！去拿吧。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_450
msgid "Have you found the complete chant?"
msgstr "你找到完整的咒語了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_450:0
msgid "I haven't even found the old hermit yet."
msgstr "我還沒找到那位老隱士。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_450:1
msgid "I found the old hermit, but he hasn't given me his book."
msgstr "我找到那位隱士了，但他還沒把書給我。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_452
msgid "You'll have to put in a little more effort. All of Dhayavar trusts you."
msgstr "你得再多加把勁。整個達亞瓦都信任你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_454
msgid "He must. Go again."
msgstr "他必須。再去一次。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_460
msgid "Great. And now off to the barrier! Make haste - I'll join you as fast as my injuries allow."
msgstr "太好了。現在前往結界！快點——我會盡快趕上，視傷勢而定。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_462
msgid "[Smiling] What an eager kid."
msgstr "[微笑] 真是個熱情的孩子。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_590
msgid "Andor is going to visit Rosmara to refill his travel supplies."
msgstr "安多爾將前往羅斯瑪拉補充他的旅行物資。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_590:1
msgid "Who is Rosmara?"
msgstr "羅絲瑪是誰？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_592
msgid "She's the fruit lady on the road near Feygard."
msgstr "她是妖境附近路上的水果攤販。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_miri_600
msgid "Isn't it a lovely day? Even in here?"
msgstr "今天天氣真好，不是嗎？即使在這裡也是？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_2
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_4
msgid "Go away. I will never be happy in my life."
msgstr "走開。我這輩子永遠不會快樂。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_10
msgid "[mumbling chants]"
msgstr "[喃喃咒語]"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_22
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_222
msgid "Nooooo!"
msgstr "不～～～！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_24
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_224
msgid "Now the spell is broken. Everything is in vain!"
msgstr "現在魔咒已破。一切皆徒勞！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_30
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_230
msgid "Why did you do that? Who gave you the right?"
msgstr "你為什麼要那麼做？誰給你的權利？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_30:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_230:0
msgid "Do you know what you were doing?"
msgstr "你知道你在做什麼嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_40
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_240
msgid "I was getting my husband back from the afterlife!"
msgstr "我正在從冥界帶回我的丈夫！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_50
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_250
msgid "Is that what you think?"
msgstr "你是這麼想的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_50:0
msgid "Miri? When did you get here?"
msgstr "米莉？你什麼時候來的？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_60
msgid "I came with all haste. Too bad the poison is slowing me down."
msgstr "我火速趕來。可惜毒素讓我行動遲緩。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_62
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_262
msgid "[To the mourning woman] The ritual was not to bring back your husband - it is to bring Kazaul's powerful monsters into Dhayavar."
msgstr ""
"[對哀悼的女子] 這個儀式不是為了讓你丈夫復活，而是為了將卡札爾的強大怪物帶入達"
"亞瓦爾。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_70
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_270
msgid "You lie! You don't want my happiness."
msgstr "你說謊！你不想要我的幸福。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_72
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_272
msgid "Do you think monsters would have assisted you? And a barrier would have sprung up? Just for one person?"
msgstr "你覺得怪物會幫助你嗎？還會為了一個人出現結界？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_82
msgid "Then why did the ritual not include something that links to your husband? Something precious to him?"
msgstr "那為什麼儀式中沒有包含與你丈夫有關的東西？對他珍貴的東西？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_90
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_290
msgid "Oh no! What do I do now? He's gone."
msgstr "糟了！我現在該怎麼辦？他走了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_92
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_292
msgid "Pray where have you been praying. And tell me who put you up to this?"
msgstr "祈禱，你到底在哪裡祈禱？告訴我，是誰叫你這麼做的？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_92:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_292:0
msgid "Yes, who put you up to this?"
msgstr "是誰教你這麼做的？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_100
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_300
msgid "Why? That famous miracle priest who walks on lava, west of here. Do you need me anymore? Then I'm going home to mourn again."
msgstr ""
"為什麼？那位著名的奇蹟牧師，就在這裡西邊的熔岩上行走。你還需要我嗎？那我就回"
"家繼續哀悼。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_110
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_310
msgid "Yes, you go back to your village. And we will have a chat with this famous miracle priest."
msgstr "是的，你回你的村莊去。我們會和這位著名的奇蹟牧師聊聊。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_110:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_310:0
msgid "Nice job."
msgstr "幹得好。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_250:0
msgid "Borvis? I didn't expect you already."
msgstr "Borvis？我沒想到你已經來了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_260
msgid "I came with all haste. You were faster."
msgstr "我急忙趕來，你更快一步。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_mourning_woman_282
msgid "Then why did the ritual not include something that links to your husband?  Something precious to him?"
msgstr "那為何儀式中沒有包含與你丈夫相關的東西？對他珍貴的東西？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit
msgid "Go away. Leave me alone."
msgstr "走開。別打擾我。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_12
msgid "I thought hiding on this hill would ensure no riff-raff would find me."
msgstr "我以為躲在這座山丘上就不會被那些無賴找到。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_14
msgid "This tower has long been deserted after all."
msgstr "畢竟這座塔早已荒廢。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_14:0
msgid "I'm no riff-raff, and I'm not here to see the sights. I've come to meet you."
msgstr "我可不是無賴，也不是來觀光的。我是來見你的。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_20
msgid "Leave me alone. I am no one."
msgstr "別理我。我是無名之人。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_20:0
msgid "You are not no one. You have a copy of Azimyran Secrets."
msgstr "你不是無名之輩。你擁有《阿茲米蘭秘典》的副本。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_30
msgid "So? I'm not giving it to anyone. I'm too old to be threatened. And I want nothing."
msgstr "怎樣？我不會給任何人。我年紀太大，不會被威脅。我什麼都不要。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_30:0
msgid "Can I at least read it? I need to copy only one chant."
msgstr "我至少能讀一下嗎？我只需要抄一段咒語。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_40
msgid "Kazaul again, eh?"
msgstr "又是卡札爾，對吧？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_50
msgid "Hehe. I'm a hermit, but not senile. In fact, I moved here to stay away from all those holier-than-thou morons: Geomyr, Shadow, Elythom ..."
msgstr ""
"呵呵。我是隱士，但不糊塗。事實上，我搬到這裡是為了遠離那些自以為是的笨蛋："
"Geomyr、暗影、Elythom ..."

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_50:0
msgid "Sounds oddly appealing. Can I copy the rest of the chant?"
msgstr "聽起來怪怪的，但挺吸引人。我可以抄下剩下的咒語嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_60:0
msgid ""
"[Flipping through the pages] Ah, here's the rest of chant.\n"
"[Talking to the hermit]: Thanks! Here's the book back."
msgstr ""
"[翻閱頁面] 啊，這裡是剩下的咒語。\n"
"[對隱士說]：謝謝！書還給你了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_70
msgid "Welcome! Try and not disturb me again, if you can."
msgstr "歡迎！如果可以，別再打擾我了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldhermit_70:0
msgid "Unless my brother comes this way, we won't disturb you again."
msgstr "除非我兄弟來這邊，否則我們不會再打擾你。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_10
msgid "Who are you? Not here to steal my books, are you?"
msgstr "你是誰？不會是來偷我的書吧？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_10:0
msgid "I once helped to find your book. Don't be rude!"
msgstr "我曾幫你找過書，別無禮！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_20
msgid "Sorry, there seem to be folks who want to take my books and not return them."
msgstr "抱歉，似乎有人想拿走我的書卻不歸還。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_20:0
msgid "In fact, I'd like to borrow your copy of Calomyran Secrets."
msgstr "事實上，我想借用你那本《卡洛米蘭秘辛》。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_30
msgid "No can do. It's too rare and precious."
msgstr "不行。那太稀有珍貴了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_30:0
msgid "But Dhayavar is at stake!"
msgstr "但達亞瓦岌岌可危！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_40
msgid "Sounds serious. But, what's the book got to do with that?"
msgstr "聽起來很嚴重。但那本書跟這有什麼關係？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_40:0
msgid "I need a chant from it to break a Kazaul spell."
msgstr "我需要從中取得咒語來破解卡札爾的魔法。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_50
msgid "Copy it then."
msgstr "那就複製吧。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_50:0
msgid "OK ... just a second ..."
msgstr "好……請稍等……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_60
msgid "Have you finished yet?"
msgstr "你完成了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_60:0
msgid "[Talking to self, while reading] So, this is the chant. Wait, this is half a chant! The books says the rest of the chant is written in another book - Azimyran Secrets."
msgstr ""
"[自言自語，邊讀邊說] 這就是咒語。等等，這才是咒語的一半！書上說剩下的咒語寫在"
"另一本書裡——《阿茲米蘭祕密》。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_62
msgid "And stop babbling to yourself!"
msgstr "別再自言自語了！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_62:0
msgid "Done. Here's your book back, thank you."
msgstr "完成了。這是你的書，謝謝。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_64
msgid "Do I see greasy fingerprints there?"
msgstr "我看到那裡有油膩的指紋嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_64:0
msgid "However, it is not complete. Do you also have the book Azimyran Secrets?"
msgstr "不過，這還不完整。你也有《阿茲米蘭的秘密》這本書嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_oldman_70
msgid "No, sorry. Do let me know if you come across a copy."
msgstr "不，抱歉。如果你找到一份，請告訴我。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_10
msgid "You keep on disturbing us?"
msgstr "你還要繼續打擾我們嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_10:0
msgid "How did you manage to lose this? [Gives Throdna the second piece of the Kazaul ritual]"
msgstr "你怎麼會弄丟這個？【交給索羅德納第二塊卡札爾儀式碎片】"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_20
msgid "Why did you steal this? You must be part of that terrible cult of the Kazaul."
msgstr "你為什麼偷這個？你一定是那個可怕的卡札爾邪教的一員。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_22
msgid "Where was I? Ah, yes ..."
msgstr "我說到哪了？啊，對了……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_22a
msgid "O Kazaul, venerabilis deus, where art thou in the shadows of tempus ..."
msgstr "卡札爾，尊貴的神祇，你在時間的暗影中何處……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_22b
msgid "... Sacra ritus, anciente, must be reawakened, sed obscure ..."
msgstr "... Sacra ritus，anciente，必須重新喚醒，sed obscure ..."

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_22c
msgid "... Lumen in tenebris, the sigil of Kazaul, lost in the mists of memoria ..."
msgstr "… 黑暗中的光明，卡札爾的符印，遺失於記憶的迷霧中 …"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_24
msgid "... Perhaps the incantatio of the ancients holds the key, sed forgotten ..."
msgstr "……或許古人的咒語藏有關鍵，卻被遺忘了……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_24:0
msgid "What was the word again? Ah, I remember. [Loud voice] Kazaul Est!"
msgstr "那個詞是什麼來著？啊，我記起來了。[大聲]卡札爾·艾斯特！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_30
msgid "You are still here? Well ..."
msgstr "你還在這裡？那麼..."

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_32
msgid "So, you're not the one who stole my notes?"
msgstr "所以，不是你偷了我的筆記？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_32:0
msgid "No, in fact I helped purify the shrine."
msgstr "不，事實上是我幫忙淨化了神社。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_40
msgid "That is right. So, what do you want?"
msgstr "沒錯。那麼，你想要什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_40:0
msgid "I need to know what all this chant can do."
msgstr "我需要知道這咒語能做什麼。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_50
msgid "It's a powerful chant for many dangerous things. I'm not sure I should tell. Followers of Kazaul want to get a foothold in Dhayavar."
msgstr ""
"這是對許多危險事物的強大咒語。我不確定我是否該說。卡札爾的追隨者想在達亞瓦爾"
"站穩腳跟。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_52
msgid "The ritual of the nocturnus, should it be performed under Luna's watchful eye ..."
msgstr "夜之儀式，若在露娜的注視下進行……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_54
msgid "... Ego dubito, whether the offerings still hold power, or are but relics of a bygone era ..."
msgstr "... 我懷疑，這些供品是否仍具力量，抑或僅是過去時代的遺物 ..."

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_54:0
msgid "Not again - Kazaul Est!"
msgstr "又來了——卡札爾·艾斯特！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_60
msgid "Yes. This piece of the ritual is of Kazaul. Along with the first part, one can raise Kazaul monsters, use in sacrifices, make defensive walls, impenetrable barriers ... dangerous rites."
msgstr ""
"是的。這段儀式屬於卡札爾。配合第一部分，可以召喚卡札爾怪物，用於祭祀，築起防"
"禦牆，無法穿透的屏障……危險的儀式。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_60:0
msgid "I just came from such an impenetrable barrier in the south of Stoutford."
msgstr "我剛從斯托福德南方那道無法穿透的屏障來。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_70
msgid "An impenetrable barrier? That's no good. If Kazaul gains a foothold in Dhayavar, strong monsters will roam in Dhayavar."
msgstr ""
"一道無法穿透的屏障？那可不行。如果卡札爾在達亞瓦立足，強大的怪物將在達亞瓦橫"
"行。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_72
msgid "... Is the tempus ripe for the reawakening of Kazaul, or is it but an illusion ..."
msgstr "... 現在是卡札爾重生的時機，還是僅僅一場幻象 ..."

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_74
msgid "... Must find the correct verba, the sacred words that summon the divine ..."
msgstr "... 必須找到正確的 verba，召喚神聖的神諭之語 ..."

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_78
msgid "... Kazaul's essence, hidden within the arcana of the old scrolls, waiting to be uncovered ..."
msgstr "... 卡札爾的精華，隱藏在古卷的奧秘中，等待被揭示 ..."

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_78:0
msgid "Kazaul Est!!"
msgstr "卡札爾來了！！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_80
msgid "Eh, yes. The barrier. One has to use the two pieces of the ritual and a chant of passage to go through the barrier."
msgstr "嗯，是的。結界。必須使用兩塊儀式物和通行咒語才能穿越結界。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_80:0
msgid "What is the chant of passage?"
msgstr "通過咒語是什麼？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_90
msgid "That is something I do not know."
msgstr "那是我不知道的事。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_90:0
msgid "So, nothing to be done?"
msgstr "那麼，無計可施嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_100
msgid "I didn't say that! There was a traveler a long time back - he wrote a book Calomyran Secrets. It has the chant of passage, among other things to counter Kazaul dangers. Find it, if you can."
msgstr ""
"我沒那麼說過！很久以前有個旅人——他寫了一本書《卡洛米蘭秘辛》。裡面有通行咒語"
"，還有其他對抗卡札爾危險的東西。能找到就去找吧。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_100:0
msgid "Calomyran Secrets? That rings a bell. Thanks!"
msgstr "卡洛米蘭秘辛？聽起來有印象，謝謝！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_throdna_102
msgid "... Ah, the anciente scriptura, perhaps it reveals the secret to rekindling the divine ..."
msgstr "……啊，古老的經文，也許它揭示了重燃神性的秘密……"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest_2
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest_4
msgid "How dare you stop my spell?"
msgstr "你竟敢阻止我的魔法？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest_2:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest_4:0
msgid "It is best for Dhayavar."
msgstr "這對達亞瓦爾最有利。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest_10
msgid "I have no time for this."
msgstr "我沒時間理這個。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest_10:0
msgid "Oh, you are running away?"
msgstr "哦，你要逃跑嗎？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2
msgid "You again? This must end now."
msgstr "又是你？這次必須結束了。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2:1
msgid "I completely agree."
msgstr "我完全同意。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_10
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_110
msgid "You're no priest!"
msgstr "你不是牧師！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_10:0
msgid "Miri! How did you get here?"
msgstr "米莉！你怎麼來到這裡的？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_20
msgid "I could not let you go alone."
msgstr "我不能讓你獨自前行。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_20:0
msgid "You made me fight alone all the way here."
msgstr "你讓我一路孤身作戰到這裡。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_30
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_130
msgid "Don't worry - it's worth it."
msgstr "別擔心──絕對值得。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_30:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_130:0
msgid "But it's unfair to ..."
msgstr "但這對...不公平"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_40
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_140
msgid "Are we going to do this now, or are you two going to talk all day?"
msgstr "我們現在要開始，還是你們兩個要聊一整天？"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_40:0
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_140:0
msgid "Ah, sorry: KAZAUL EST!"
msgstr "啊，抱歉：卡札爾東方！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_50
#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_150
msgid "That's its true form! A monster masquerading as a priest! Attack!"
msgstr "那才是它的真面目！偽裝成牧師的怪物！攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_110:0
msgid "Borvis! At last!"
msgstr "博維斯！終於見到你了！"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_120
msgid "My legs are not as young as yours anymore."
msgstr "我的腿已不如你年輕。"

#: conversationlist_darknessanddaylight.json:dds_dark_priest2_120:0
msgid "You made me fight alone all way here."
msgstr "你讓我一路獨自作戰到這裡。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_prompt
msgid ""
"The air around it feels heavy, pressing on your chest. Whispers you can't quite hear seem to emanate from the mark, tugging at the edges of your mind.\n"
"Do you dare to touch it?"
msgstr ""
"周圍的空氣沉重，壓迫著你的胸口。你隱約聽見從符記中傳來的低語，牽扯著你心靈的"
"邊緣。\n"
"你敢觸摸它嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_prompt:0
msgid "[Touch the stone.]"
msgstr "[觸摸石頭。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_prompt:1
msgid "[Leave it alone.]"
msgstr "[別管它。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_10
msgid ""
"The moment your hand meets the mark, an icy jolt shoots through your body. A voice echoes in your mind, low and venomous, yet pleading:\n"
"\"You...You must help me...End this torment... Seek the one I am bound to... in the place you call Crossglen...\"\n"
"Your vision blurs, and a suffocating sense of dread wraps around your heart. For a fleeting moment, you glimpse a shadowed figure, writhing in agony, before it vanishes.\n"
"\n"
"You stagger back, your body cold and trembling. Something has changed."
msgstr ""
"當你的手觸及標記的瞬間，一股冰冷的電流穿透全身。一個低沉而毒辣，卻又帶著哀求"
"的聲音在你腦海中迴響：\n"
"「你……你必須幫我……結束這折磨……尋找我所束縛之人……在你們稱為十字谷的地方……」\n"
"你的視線模糊，一股令人窒息的恐懼感緊緊纏繞你的心。短暫一瞬間，你瞥見一個暗影"
"般的人影，在痛苦中扭動，隨即消失。\n"
"\n"
"你踉蹌後退，身體冰冷顫抖。某些事情已經改變。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_20
msgid ""
"The weight of the mark grows heavier on your mind. A strange, oppressive feeling claws at your chest, urging you to leave this place and return to Crossglen.\n"
"You can't shake the feeling that something is terribly wrong there--your father, Mikhail, needs you. You must hurry."
msgstr ""
"那印記的重量在你心頭愈發沉重。一股奇異且壓迫的感覺攫住你的胸口，催促你離開此"
"地，回到十字谷。\n"
"你無法擺脫那裡有嚴重異狀的預感——你的父親，米哈伊爾，需要你。你必須加快腳步。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_warning_1
msgid ""
"The pull of the mark is becoming harder to ignore. A sudden wave of dizziness washes over you, and the whispers grow louder. They speak of danger, of a life lost if you do not return.\n"
"You must turn back... time is running out. Crossglen calls. You cannot linger here."
msgstr ""
"標記的吸引力越來越難以忽視。突然一陣眩暈襲來，耳邊的低語聲愈發響亮。它們在警"
"告危險，若不回頭，將失去生命。\n"
"你必須回頭……時間不多了。十字谷在召喚，你不能再逗留。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_warning_2
msgid ""
"Your steps grow heavier, the air thick with oppressive energy. The pull within your chest tightens, and the whispers now sound desperate, almost frantic.\n"
"Return to Crossglen... You cannot stay here. Your father's life is in peril. Do not test fate any longer!"
msgstr ""
"你的腳步越來越沉重，空氣中瀰漫著壓迫的能量。胸口的牽引感加劇，耳邊的低語變得"
"絕望，幾乎瘋狂。\n"
"返回十字谷……你不能留在這裡。你父親的生命正處於危險中。別再試探命運了！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_warning_3
msgid ""
"You feel your breath catch in your throat, the world around you warping and twisting. The mark is burning, a cold fire coursing through your veins, clawing at your very soul.\n"
"GO NOW! Crossglen is in danger. You are too far from what matters. Return at once--before it is too late!"
msgstr ""
"你感覺呼吸卡在喉嚨，周遭世界扭曲變形。印記燃燒著，冰冷的火焰在你血脈中奔流，"
"撕扯著你的靈魂。\n"
"立刻前往！十字谷正處於危險之中。你離重要之地太遠了。立刻返回——否則為時已晚！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_mikhail
msgid "What's gotten into you? I'm fine, but the same can't be said for Leta. I've seen her pacing in that house of hers, muttering to herself like a madwoman. You might want to check on her."
msgstr ""
"你怎麼了？我沒事，但莉塔可不一樣。我看到她在家裡來回踱步，像瘋子一樣自言自語"
"。你最好去看看她。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_10
msgid "I am most certainly not in the mood to deal with you right now. Why can't Mikhail ever control his kids?"
msgstr "我現在絕對沒心情理你。米哈伊爾為什麼就管不住他的孩子們？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_10:0
msgid "Leta, are you all right? Mikhail said you've been acting strange."
msgstr "莉塔，你還好嗎？米哈伊爾說你最近行為有些奇怪。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_30
msgid "Strange? Who does he think he is, meddling in my life? I'm fine! Just...leave me alone!"
msgstr "奇怪？他以為他是誰，竟然干涉我的生活？我沒事！就……別理我！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_30:0
msgid "You don't seem fine. You've been pacing, muttering to yourself. Something isn't right."
msgstr "你看起來不太好。你一直來回踱步，自言自語。一定有什麼不對勁。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_40
msgid "Not right? Not right! What would you know about it? You don't know what I've seen, what I've felt!"
msgstr "不對吧？不對！你知道什麼？你不知道我看過什麼，感受過什麼！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_50
msgid "You want to know? You want to understand? Fine. You'll see...but you won't like what you find."
msgstr "你想知道？你想理解？好吧。你會看到……但你不會喜歡你所發現的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_narrator
msgid "A dark aura surrounds Leta as a spirit begins its manifestation. Leta lets out a cry and vanishes as the spirit rises."
msgstr "莉塔周圍籠罩著黑暗氣息，靈體開始顯現。莉塔發出一聲呼喊，隨著靈體升起而消失。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_spirit
msgid "[taunting] You shouldn't have meddled, little one. This vessel belongs to me now, and so does its anger!"
msgstr "[嘲諷] 你不該多管閒事，小子。這具軀體現在屬於我，憤怒也是！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:crossglen_dark_spirit_defeated_1
msgid "The Dark spirit has been defeated, but you feel as if this issue is unresolved. Something is telling you that it has fled back to the devastated lands south of Stoutford."
msgstr ""
"黑暗靈魂已被擊敗，但你感覺此事尚未了結。某種聲音告訴你，它已逃回斯托福德南方"
"的荒蕪之地。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_dark_spirit_10
msgid "Destroy me? Foolish mortal! I am older than your bloodline, stronger than your resolve. You will break, just like the others. Their despair feeds me, and yours will be no different!"
msgstr ""
"要毀滅我？愚蠢的凡人！我比你的血脈更古老，比你的意志更堅強。你會崩潰，就像其"
"他人一樣。他們的絕望滋養著我，你的絕望也不會例外！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_dark_spirit_11
msgid "The spirit swirls with dark energy, causing the ground to tremble as it prepares to attack."
msgstr "靈體盤旋著黑暗能量，地面震動，準備發動攻擊。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_dark_spirit_20
msgid "Let me show you what true suffering feels like. You will know despair, and your name will be forgotten in the darkness of my power!"
msgstr "讓我來讓你體會真正的痛苦。你將感受絕望，你的名字將在我力量的黑暗中被遺忘！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_dark_spirit_20:0
msgid "Let me show you the darkness of my power!"
msgstr "讓我展現我力量的黑暗！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_dark_spirit_defeated_10
msgid "As the dark spirit fades, the suffocating darkness that had plagued this place begins to lift. The air feels lighter, though the oppressive aura of this devastated land remains, its sinister nature woven into the very ground. Yet, deep within, you feel an uneasy twinge...a faint whisper that the spirit's defeat may not be the end of its influence. Something or someone may still be tied to its lingering power."
msgstr ""
"隨著黑暗靈魂消散，籠罩此地的窒息黑暗開始消退。空氣變得清新，儘管這片荒蕪之地"
"仍帶著壓迫的氣息，其陰險本質已深植於大地。然而，在心底你感到一絲不安……那靈魂"
"的敗北或許並非其影響的終結。某物或某人仍可能與其殘留的力量相連。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:leta_child_10
msgid "I am terrified! Who are those old people upstairs?"
msgstr "我好害怕！樓上那些老人是誰？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:leta_child_10:0
msgid "Seriously? You are scared of your own parents?"
msgstr "認真的嗎？你竟然害怕自己的父母？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:leta_child_10:1
msgid "\"Those old people\" are your parents."
msgstr "「那些老人」是你的父母。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:leta_child_20
msgid "Those people? No, no, no, they are not my parents. You liar!"
msgstr "那些人？不，不，不，他們不是我的父母。你這個騙子！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:leta_child_20:0
msgid "I'm sorry to say that, but it is true...I think."
msgstr "很抱歉這麼說，但我想這是真的……我想。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_initial_phrase
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_leta_initial_phrase
msgid "[Calm, almost welcoming.] Ah, there you are. You've come back to see us, then."
msgstr "[平靜，幾乎帶著歡迎。] 啊，你來了。那麼，你是回來見我們的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_initial_phrase:0
msgid "Oromir? What happened to you two? You look...different."
msgstr "奧羅米爾？你們兩個怎麼了？你看起來……不一樣。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_initial_phrase:1
msgid "Oh, it's still so hard to see you like this. But I still have questions."
msgstr "喔，看到你這樣還是很難過。但我還有問題想問。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_leta_initial_phrase:0
msgid "Leta? What happened to you two? You look...different."
msgstr "莉塔？你們兩個怎麼了？你看起來……不一樣。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_leta_initial_phrase:1
msgid "Oh, it's still so hard to see you like this, so I should leave now."
msgstr "喔，看到你這樣還是很難過，我該走了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_10
msgid "[Thoughtful, but resolute.] Different? Yes, I suppose we are. A weight I didn't even know I carried has been lifted. I feel stronger now, more alive than ever before."
msgstr ""
"[深思熟慮，卻堅定不移。] 不同？是的，我想我們確實不同。我甚至不知道自己背負著"
"的重擔已被卸下。現在我感覺更強大，比以往任何時候都更有活力。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_leta_responds_10
msgid "[frail, but smiling warmly] Don't mind him, dear. He's always been dramatic. I may not remember everything, but I know this much--I finally feel at peace."
msgstr ""
"[虛弱但溫柔微笑] 別理他，親愛的。他一向戲劇化。我或許記不得所有事，但我知道這"
"點——我終於感到安寧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_leta_responds_10:0
msgid "Leta...this isn't normal. You look like you've aged decades overnight. How can you be so calm about this?"
msgstr "莉塔……這不正常。你看起來一夜之間老了好幾十歲。你怎麼能這麼冷靜？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_leta_responds_20n
msgid "[with a soft, almost wistful tone] Oh, time catches up to us all, doesn't it? Better to find peace than cling to what's already gone. Whatever you did, thank you. Truly."
msgstr ""
"[以柔和、幾乎帶點惆悵的語氣] 哦，時間終究會追上我們，不是嗎？與其緊抓已逝的過"
"去，不如尋得平靜。不管你做了什麼，謝謝你。真心的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_leta_responds_20n:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_leta_responds_20:0
msgid "I didn't do this to you. This doesn't feel right. What happened after the spirit was defeated?"
msgstr "我不是故意對你這樣。這感覺不對。靈魂被擊敗後發生了什麼？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_leta_responds_20
msgid "Oh, time catches up to us all, doesn't it? Better to find peace than cling to what's already gone. Whatever you did, thank you. Truly."
msgstr ""
"啊，時間終究會追上我們，不是嗎？與其緊抓已逝的過去，不如尋求內心的平靜。無論"
"你做了什麼，謝謝你。真心感謝。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_20
msgid "[Firmly, but not unkindly.] What happened doesn't matter anymore. What matters is that the darkness is gone, and we can finally live. You should do the same. Let it rest. Ease your mind and later, if you still have questions, please visit us then."
msgstr ""
"【堅定，但不失善意。】過去的事已無關緊要。重要的是黑暗已消散，我們終於能活下"
"去。你也該如此。讓它安息。放下心頭重擔，若日後仍有疑問，歡迎再來找我們。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_and_leta_narrator_10
msgid ""
"While looking between Leta and Oromir, you are unsettled by their calm acceptance. The house feels peaceful, but the air is heavy with unanswered questions.\n"
"\n"
"Leta and Oromir's transformations are undeniable. Their peace is haunting, a reminder that not all wounds leave visible scars. The spirit may be gone, but its mark remains."
msgstr ""
"在莉塔與奧羅米爾之間徘徊時，你被他們平靜的接受態度所不安。房子裡彌漫著寧靜，"
"但空氣中充滿了未解的疑問。\n"
"\n"
"莉塔與奧羅米爾的變化無可否認。他們的平和令人毛骨悚然，提醒著你並非所有傷口都"
"留有可見的疤痕。靈魂或許已逝，但痕跡依然存在。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_leta_10n
msgid "[Thoughtful, but somehow annoyed.]"
msgstr "[深思，但帶點惱怒。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_leta_10
msgid "Different? Yes, I suppose we are. Some more than others."
msgstr "不同？是的，我想我們確實不同。有些人比其他人更甚。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_leta_oromir_responds_10
msgid "[frail, but confidenty] Don't mind her. She's just not use to me being so assertive."
msgstr "[虛弱，但自信] 別理她，她只是還不習慣我這麼果斷。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_leta_oromir_responds_10:0
msgid "Oromir...this isn't normal. You look like you've aged decades overnight. How can you be so calm about this?"
msgstr "奧羅米爾……這不正常。你看起來一夜之間老了好幾十年。你怎麼能這麼冷靜？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:crossglen_farmer1_old_leta
msgid "So...you've seen them, haven't you? Leta and Oromir?"
msgstr "所以……你見過他們，對吧？莉塔和奧羅米爾？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:crossglen_farmer1_old_leta:0
msgid "Yeah, I've seen them. They're...old. What happened to them?"
msgstr "是的，我見過他們。他們……老了。他們發生了什麼事？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:farmer2_old_leta
msgid "They weren't like that yesterday. I saw Leta in the fields, tending to her garden, just as spry as ever. Then this morning...well, you've seen it yourself."
msgstr ""
"她們昨天可不是這樣的。我昨天還看到莉塔在田裡照顧她的花園，一如往常地精神奕奕"
"。可是今天早上……嗯，你自己也看到了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:farmer2_old_leta:0
msgid "Did either of them say anything to you? About what happened?"
msgstr "他們有跟你說什麼嗎？關於發生的事？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:crossglen_farmer1_old_leta_20
msgid "[more skeptical, arms crossed] Old's putt'' it lightly. They look ancient, like they lived a hundred winters in just one night."
msgstr ""
"[更加懷疑，雙臂交叉] 老這說法太輕描淡寫了。他們看起來古老，彷彿一夜之間經歷了"
"百個冬天。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:farmer2_old_leta_20
msgid "[shaking his head, grim] Not a word. Just that vacant smile of hers, like everything's fine. Oromir, though...he's got this strange look in his eye. Like he knows something we don't."
msgstr ""
"[搖頭，嚴肅] 一句話也別說。她那空洞的笑容，就像一切都好似無事。奧羅米爾倒是……"
"他眼中有種奇異的神色，好像知道我們不知道的事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_10
msgid "[With a gentle smile.] Of course. Ask what you will. We owe you that much."
msgstr "[帶著溫柔的微笑。] 當然。儘管問吧。我們欠你這份情。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_10:0
msgid "Why were you affected too? Leta was the one possessed by the spirit, not you."
msgstr "你為什麼也會受到影響？是莉塔被靈體附身，不是你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_10:1
msgid "In your basement, I talked to a man, a farmer-looking man that is. I suspect that he is your child. But he is frightened and confused..."
msgstr ""
"在你的地下室裡，我和一個看起來像農夫的男子談過。我懷疑他是你的孩子。但他感到"
"害怕且困惑……"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_10n
msgid "While sighing, his voice remains steady."
msgstr "嘆息中，他的聲音依然穩定。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_10
msgid "Well, my child, you see, once I entered into the sacred bond of marriage with Leta, I too became bound to the spirit. Our lives, our fates, were entwined by the very vows we spoke. When she was touched by its darkness, I could not help but share in the burden."
msgstr ""
"孩子啊，你看，當我與莉塔締結神聖的婚約時，我也同樣被那靈魂所束縛。我們的生命"
"與命運，因我們所發的誓言而交織。當她被黑暗侵襲時，我也無法不分擔這份重擔。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_10:0
msgid "So, the bond between you two extended even to the curse?"
msgstr "所以，你們之間的羈絆甚至延伸到了詛咒？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_20
msgid "Yes. That's the nature of true union, is it not? In love and in struggle, we are as one. Her pain became mine, just as her redemption became ours. The spirit's malice sought to age us, to wear us down. But we endure, thanks to you."
msgstr ""
"是的。這不正是真正結合的本質嗎？在愛中，在奮鬥中，我們合而為一。她的痛苦成了"
"我的，正如她的救贖成了我們的。靈魂的惡意試圖讓我們衰老，消磨我們。但多虧了你"
"，我們得以堅持。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_20:0
msgid "Do you regret it? Being tied to her curse?"
msgstr "你後悔嗎？被她的詛咒束縛著？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_30n
msgid "While shaking his head with a warm smile, Oromir continues..."
msgstr "奧羅米爾帶著溫暖的微笑搖頭，繼續說道..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_30
msgid "Never. Leta is my heart, my reason for every breath. If carrying this weight was the price of sharing my life with her, then I'd pay it a thousand times over. Love isn't just about the light, it's about standing together, even in the shadows."
msgstr ""
"絕不。莉塔是我的心，我每一次呼吸的理由。若承擔這份重擔是與她共度一生的代價，"
"那我願意付出千百倍。愛不僅是光明，更是在暗影中並肩而立。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_30:0
msgid "[pausing] That's admirable. I hope you both find some peace now."
msgstr "[暫停] 真令人敬佩。希望你們倆現在能找到些許平靜。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_40
msgid "We will. Time may have taken its toll, but the darkness is gone. Now, we can live what remains of our days in quiet gratitude. Thank you, truly."
msgstr ""
"我們會的。時間或許帶來了傷痕，但黑暗已消散。現在，我們能以平靜的感恩度過餘生"
"。真心感謝你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_bond_40:0
msgid "I still have questions."
msgstr "我還有疑問。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_10n
msgid "Oromir's voice is somber, yet a slight trember can be heard within it."
msgstr "奧羅米爾的聲音沉重，卻隱約帶著顫抖。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_10n:0
msgid "Tomas? How could this happen to him? He's a grown man now, but he acts as if he's still that frightened child."
msgstr "托馬斯？他怎麼會變成這樣？他現在已是成年人，卻還像個受驚的孩子。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_10
msgid "Our son...Yes, you are right. That is Tomas. Though, to him, he may as well be a stranger to himself."
msgstr ""
"我們的兒子……是的，你說得對。那是托馬斯。不過，對他來說，他自己也可能像個陌生"
"人。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_10:0
msgid "But he..."
msgstr "但他…"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_20n
msgid "Oromir sighs deeply while clasping his hands."
msgstr "奧羅米爾深深嘆息，雙手緊握。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_20n:0
msgid "...grew older like you both, why does he seem...stuck, mentally?"
msgstr "...像你們兩個一樣長大，為什麼他的心智似乎...停滯不前？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_20
msgid "When the spirit latched onto Leta, its curse didn't just affect her. It spread to everything close to her--her home, her family, even our boy. He was only two years old when it began...always holding her hand, always by her side. The spirit saw him as an extension of her, and so it bound him as well."
msgstr ""
"當靈體附身於莉塔時，詛咒不僅影響了她，也蔓延到她身邊的一切——她的家、她的家人"
"，甚至我們的孩子。詛咒開始時，他只有兩歲……總是牽著她的手，總是在她身邊。靈體"
"視他為她的延伸，因此也將他束縛住。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_30
msgid "The spirit didn't just age us. It fed on our memories, our sense of self. Tomas was too young to defend himself from its grasp. It stripped away his connection to who he was. Trapping him in fear and confusion, unable to grow in mind, even as his body aged."
msgstr ""
"那靈魂不僅讓我們變老。它吞噬了我們的記憶和自我意識。托馬斯太年輕，無法抵抗它"
"的控制。它剝奪了他與自我的連結，將他困在恐懼與迷惘中，心智無法成長，儘管身體"
"在老去。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_30:0
msgid "Is there any way to help him? He's terrified to leave the basement."
msgstr "有什麼辦法幫助他嗎？他害怕離開地下室。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_40
msgid "Perhaps, with time. The curse is gone, but the scars it left behind are deep. He needs patience, kindness and someone to guide him back to himself. I fear we may not have the strength to do it alone."
msgstr ""
"也許，隨著時間會好轉。詛咒已除，但留下的傷痕深刻。他需要耐心、善意和引導，幫"
"助他找回自我。我擔心我們無法獨自承擔這重任。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:old_oromir_questions_child_40:0
msgid "Yes, he needs time. I hope it works out for you three."
msgstr "是的，他需要時間。希望你們三個能順利。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_andor_10
msgid "Step lightly, wanderer. The swamp doesn't take kindly to strangers, and neither do I. What brings you to my domain?"
msgstr "輕步前行，旅人。沼澤不歡迎陌生人，我也一樣。你為何來到我的領地？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_andor_10:0
msgid "I'm searching for someone, my brother, Andor. He looks like..."
msgstr "我正在尋找一個人，我的兄弟，安多爾。他長得像..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met
msgid "So, you've returned. Tell me, do the leeches whisper their secrets to you yet? Or are you still grasping at the edges of what this swamp has to offer?"
msgstr ""
"所以，你回來了。告訴我，那些水蛭是否已開始向你低語祕密？還是你仍在摸索這片沼"
"澤所能提供的邊緣？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:0
msgid "You stated that if I helped you kill that venomous creature that you would tell more about Andor."
msgstr "你說過如果我幫你殺了那隻毒獸，你會告訴我更多關於安多爾的事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:1
msgid "That graveyard, the one directly south of here, who were those people?"
msgstr "那座墓地，就在這裡正南方，那些人是誰？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:2
msgid "Actually, I am here to give you an update on that graveyard exploration you sent me on."
msgstr "其實，我是來向你報告你派我去的那次墓地探險的最新情況。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:3
msgid "I spoke to a ghost in the Galmore encampment. His name is Eryndor..."
msgstr "我在加爾摩營地與一個幽靈交談過。他的名字是艾林多爾..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:4
msgid "No, that's old news. Try and keep up, won't you? I'm here to collect my reward?"
msgstr "不，那是舊聞了。別落後了，好嗎？我是來領獎勵的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:5
msgid "No, that's old news. Try and keep up, won't you? I'm here to inform you that I've defeted Eryndor's spirit."
msgstr "不，那是舊聞了。別落後了，好嗎？我是來告訴你，我已經擊敗了艾林多的靈魂。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:6
msgid "What do I need to give you in order for you to make those Insectbane tonics? I want some now."
msgstr "我需要給你什麼，才能讓你製作那些蟲絕解藥？我現在就想要一些。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:7
msgid "Can we talk about the Insectbane tonic?"
msgstr "我們可以談談驅蟲藥水嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met:8
msgid "I would like to see your other potions for sale."
msgstr "我想看看你其他的藥水出售。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_met_10
msgid "No, no, no. I said \"if you want my aid, you'll need to earn it\", and indeed you did receive my aid as I taught you about the leeches."
msgstr ""
"不，不，不。我說過「如果你想要我的幫助，就得先贏得它」，而你確實得到了我的幫"
"助，因為我教了你關於水蛭的知識。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_andor_20
msgid "Ah, the one with fire in his eyes and fear in his heart. He came here seeking knowledge, though knowledge often demands a price. Are you here to pay it as well?"
msgstr ""
"啊，那雙眼中燃燒著火焰、心中卻充滿恐懼的人。他來此尋求知識，然而知識往往需要"
"付出代價。你也是來付出這代價的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_andor_20:0
msgid "What did he want from you?"
msgstr "他想從你這裡得到什麼？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_andor_30
msgid "What every ambitious fool wants: power and mastery over forces that should be left alone. Your brother was in a hurry when he left, clutching what he came for. You might ask yourself why."
msgstr ""
"每個野心勃勃的傻瓜都渴望的：力量與對本該被遺忘之力的掌控。你兄弟離開時匆忙，"
"緊握著他來取的東西。你或許會想知道為什麼。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_andor_30:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_10:0
msgid "Why are you living out here alone?"
msgstr "你為什麼獨自一人住在這裡？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_10
msgid "Step lightly, wanderer. The swamp doesn't take kindly to just anyone, and neither do I. Why are you before me?"
msgstr "腳步輕盈，流浪者。沼澤不歡迎隨便的人，我也一樣。你為何來到我面前？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_20
msgid "This swamp doesn't judge me like the courts of men once did. Out here, I'm free to practice my craft and to help those bold or desperate enough to find me."
msgstr ""
"這片沼澤不像人間法庭那般審判我。在這裡，我自由施展技藝，幫助那些勇敢或絕望找"
"到我的人。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_20:0
msgid "You helped Andor, so help me. Tell me where he went."
msgstr "你幫助了安多爾，也幫幫我。告訴我他去了哪裡。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_30
msgid "You ask for much considering you are someone who has given me nothing in return. If you want my aid, you'll need to earn it. A creature stalks my property, not an ordinary beast but one corrupted by the same darkness that haunts this land. Deal with it, and we'll talk."
msgstr ""
"你要求甚多，畢竟你從未回報我任何東西。若想要我的幫助，你得先贏得它。有隻生物"
"潛伏在我的領地，不是普通的野獸，而是被這片土地的黑暗腐化的怪物。解決它，我們"
"再談。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_30:0
msgid "What kind of creature?"
msgstr "什麼生物？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_40
msgid "A swamp creature, but far from the kind you'd expect to see. This one is massive, venomous, and ravenous. It's draining the life from my medicinal pools. Strength alone won't save you. You'll need to learn the ways of the swamp."
msgstr ""
"沼澤生物，卻非你所預期見到的那種。這隻龐大、帶毒且飢餓。它正在吸取我藥用池中"
"的生命力。僅靠力量無法救你，你必須學會沼澤之道。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_10
msgid "You've proven resourceful. Perhaps you are worthy of the knowledge I carry. The swamp holds more than muck and mire, and so do the creatures that call it home."
msgstr ""
"你展現了機智。或許你配得上我所擁有的知識。沼澤不僅有泥濘，居住於此的生物亦非"
"凡俗。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_10:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_talk_leech_10:0
msgid "You mentioned leeches earlier. What did you mean by that?"
msgstr "你剛才提到水蛭。那是什麼意思？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_20
msgid "Leeches are simple creatures, but they hold incredible power. With the right knowledge, they can purge poison, stop bleeding, and heal wounds that no salve can touch. Few have the courage to learn their secrets."
msgstr ""
"水蛭是簡單的生物，但擁有驚人的力量。掌握正確知識後，它們能解毒、止流血，並療"
"癒任何藥膏無法觸及的傷口。少有人有勇氣學習它們的祕密。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_20:0
msgid "Can you teach me?"
msgstr "你能教我嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_30
msgid "I don't waste my time on fools, but you've proven yourself. Watch closely."
msgstr "我不會浪費時間在愚人身上，但你已證明自己。仔細看清楚。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_narrator
msgid "Vaelric produces a jar filled with wriggling leeches and demonstrates their use on a wounded arm."
msgstr "瓦爾里克拿出一罐蠕動的水蛭，示範如何用在受傷的手臂上。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_40
msgid "See how the leech attaches itself? It draws out the bad humors, cleansing the blood. Placement is everything. Here, take this."
msgstr "你看水蛭如何附著？它吸出壞氣，淨化血液。位置很重要。拿去吧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_40:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_40:1
msgid "[Extend my hand and take the leech.]"
msgstr "[伸出手，接住水蛭。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_50
msgid "Don't underestimate them. In skilled hands, they are as effective as any blade or potion. Use them wisely."
msgstr "別小看它們。在熟練的手中，它們和任何劍刃或藥劑一樣有效。謹慎使用。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_50:0
msgid "Thank you. Is there anything else I should know?"
msgstr "謝謝。還有什麼我需要知道的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_narrator_2
msgid "Vaelric hands you a leech."
msgstr "瓦爾里克遞給你一隻水蛭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_60
msgid "Yes. Don't waste them on minor cuts or trifling ailments. Save them for when they're truly needed. The swamp still has more to teach you, if you are willing to learn."
msgstr ""
"是的。別浪費在小傷口或瑣碎病痛上。留著在真正需要時使用。沼澤還有更多要教你，"
"只要你願意學習。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_25
msgid "Once, I was a celebrated healer. They called me a miracle worker for curing the incurable. My methods were...unconventional. Leeches, parasitic creatures, even plants most would call poisonous. I used whatever the swamp could offer."
msgstr ""
"曾經，我是備受讚譽的治療師。人們稱我為奇蹟工匠，因為我能治癒絕症。我的方法……"
"非傳統。水蛭、寄生生物，甚至多數人視為有毒的植物。我利用沼澤所能提供的一切。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_28
msgid "Innovation often breeds fear. When a Laumwill noble entrusted me with his life, I used every method I knew to save him. But he died under my care, and the courts called it murder. The Laumwills made certain there was no place for me among civilized men."
msgstr ""
"創新常伴隨恐懼。當一位勞姆威爾貴族將性命託付給我時，我用盡所有方法救他。但他"
"在我照顧下去世，法庭判我謀殺。勞姆威爾家族確保我在文明人中無立足之地。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_alone_28:0
msgid "And so you fled here?"
msgstr "所以你逃到這裡來了？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_swamp_creature_defeated_10
msgid "It's time to revisit Vaelric."
msgstr "是時候再次挑戰瓦爾里克。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:crossglen_marked_stone_warning_1
msgid ""
"The pull of the mark is becoming harder to ignore. A sudden wave of dizziness washes over you, and the whispers grow louder. They speak of danger, of a life lost if you do not return.\n"
"You must return to Mikhail...time is running out. Your father awaits. You cannot linger here."
msgstr ""
"標記的吸引力越來越難以忽視。一陣眩暈突然襲來，耳邊的低語聲變得更響亮。它們在"
"警告危險，若不回去，將會失去生命。\n"
"你必須回到米哈伊爾身邊……時間不多了。你的父親在等你。你不能再逗留於此。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:crossglen_marked_stone_warning_2
msgid ""
"Your steps grow heavier, the air thick with oppressive energy. The pull within your chest tightens, and the whispers now sound desperate, almost frantic.\n"
"Return to Mikhail...You cannot stay here. Your father's life is in peril. Do not test fate any longer!"
msgstr ""
"你的腳步越來越沉重，空氣中瀰漫著壓迫的能量。胸口的牽引感加劇，耳邊的低語變得"
"絕望，幾乎瘋狂。\n"
"回去找米哈伊爾……你不能留在這裡。你父親的生命正處於危險中。別再試探命運了！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:crossglen_marked_stone_warning_3
msgid ""
"You feel your breath catch in your throat, the world around you warping and twisting. The mark is burning, a cold fire coursing through your veins, clawing at your very soul.\n"
"TURN BACK NOW! Mikhail is in danger. You are too far from what matters. Return at once--before it is too late!"
msgstr ""
"你感覺喉嚨一陣窒息，周遭世界扭曲變形。符印灼燒著，冰冷的火焰在你血脈中奔流，"
"撕扯著你的靈魂。\n"
"現在立刻回頭！米哈伊爾有危險。你已遠離重要之地。立刻返回——否則為時已晚！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_15
msgid "You stop to admire the view. Looking down the depths of darkness off the edge of the bridge."
msgstr "你停下腳步欣賞風景。凝望橋邊深不見底的黑暗。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_dark_spirit_defeated_5
msgid "The Dark spirit collapses into a swirling vortex of shadow and rage, letting out a deafening roar as it begins to dissipate."
msgstr "黑暗靈魂化作旋轉的暗影與憤怒漩渦，發出震耳欲聾的咆哮後開始消散。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_swamp_creature_defeated_5
msgid "You've defeated the monstrous creature..."
msgstr "你已擊敗那隻怪物…"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_graveyard_10
msgid "Oh, those people? They are nobody."
msgstr "喔，那些人？他們算不了什麼。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_graveyard_10:0
msgid "Really? \"Nobody\" you say? Nobody is a \"nobody\"."
msgstr "真的嗎？你說「沒有人」？沒有人就是「無名小卒」。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_graveyard_20
msgid "Well, one or two of them may have been those that sought my aid and it was too late for them. The others? Most likely unfortunate Galmore miners who lost their lives under false promises of riches."
msgstr ""
"嗯，其中一兩個可能是那些尋求我幫助但為時已晚的人。其他的呢？大概是那些在虛假"
"的財富承諾下喪命的可憐加爾摩礦工。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_graveyard_20:0
msgid "I see. Thank you for explaining this."
msgstr "我明白了。謝謝你的說明。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_graveyard_20:1
msgid "I noticed that one of the graves looks to have been dug-up in the not-so-distant past."
msgstr "我注意到其中一座墳墓似乎在不久前被挖掘過。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_prekey
msgid "Before you stands an ancient stone, weathered and cracked, with a faintly glowing mark etched deep into its surface."
msgstr "你面前是一塊古老的石頭，風化破裂，表面深刻著微微發光的符記。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_need_to_kill_creature_10
msgid "Why are you still here? Go kill that massive, venomous, and ravenous creature for me, then we will talk!"
msgstr "你怎麼還在這？快去幫我殺了那隻龐大、劇毒又貪婪的生物，然後我們再談！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_5
msgid "Have you killed the creature that threatens my way of life?"
msgstr "你殺了威脅我生活的生物嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_5:0
msgid "Yes, and here, I have this thing that proves it. [shows the 'Corrupted swamp core' to Vaelric]"
msgstr "是的，這裡，我有這個證明。[向瓦爾里克展示「腐化沼澤核心」]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_5:1
msgid "Yes, but I can't prove it. I will return with proof."
msgstr "是的，但我無法證明。我會帶著證據回來。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_70
msgid "By the way, I'll take that 'Corrupted swamp core' now."
msgstr "順便一提，我現在要拿那個「腐化沼澤核心」。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_creature_killed_70:0
msgid "Oh, yeah, sure. I don't need that thing."
msgstr "喔，對，當然。我不需要那東西。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_10
msgid "Hey! Ho $playername!"
msgstr "嘿！嗨 $playername！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_10:0
msgid "What ...?!"
msgstr "什麼…？！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_20
msgid "What are you doing down there? I thought you would be home, catching rats?"
msgstr "你在下面做什麼？我以為你會在家抓老鼠？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_20:0
msgid "Andor! Now at last I have found you!"
msgstr "安多爾！現在終於找到你了！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_30
msgid "Who found whom here? But okay."
msgstr "誰在這裡找到誰？不過也好。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_40
msgid "Do you need my help? Like always?"
msgstr "需要我幫忙嗎？像往常一樣？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_40:0
msgid "Stop teasing. Come home, Mikhail misses you."
msgstr "別再逗了。快回家，米哈伊爾想你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_40:1
msgid "Help? You wouldn't recognize me. I've become a big, strong hero."
msgstr "幫忙？你認不出我了。我已經成為一名強壯的英雄。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_42
msgid "In fact, you no longer look like the helpless little kid you used to."
msgstr "事實上，你已不再像以前那個無助的小孩。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_50
msgid "I can't go home yet. I can't explain to you why now, but you'll understand me."
msgstr "我還不能回家。現在無法解釋原因，但你會明白我的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_50:0
msgid "Why? Let me help you!"
msgstr "為什麼？讓我幫你！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_50:1
msgid "I'll drag you behind me by your hair if you don't come with me voluntarily."
msgstr "如果你不自願跟我走，我就拉著你的頭髮拖你走。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_62
msgid "Nice try, but... [he turns his head in shock]"
msgstr "不錯的嘗試，但... [他震驚地轉頭]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_62:0
msgid "Andor? What is it?!"
msgstr "安多爾？那是什麼？！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_andor1_70
msgid "Without further words, Andor has disappeared."
msgstr "話不多說，安多爾已經消失了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:andor_ending_key1
msgid "Access to the lower levels is currently blocked. Come back later. Much later."
msgstr "通往下層的通道目前被封鎖。請稍後再來。很久以後。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_10
msgid "[Snoring]"
msgstr "[打鼾聲]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll:0
msgid "Hey, ugly brute - wake up!"
msgstr "嘿，醜陋的野獸——醒醒！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll:1
msgid "MOVE!!"
msgstr "移動!!"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll:2
msgid "Maybe I should just wait a bit?"
msgstr "也許我應該再等一下？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll:3
msgid "[singing]Troll sat alone on his seat of stone"
msgstr "[唱歌]巨魔獨自坐在他的石座上"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll:4
msgid "I think I'm going to poke you in your big fat nose."
msgstr "我想我要戳戳你那又大又胖的鼻子。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll:5
msgid "Throw a rock at the troll."
msgstr "朝巨魔丟石頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_10:0
msgid "[Singing] And munched and mumbled a bare old bone"
msgstr "[唱歌] 啃咬著一根光禿禿的老骨頭，咕噥著"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_12
msgid "Hmm? [Snoring]"
msgstr "嗯？【打鼾聲】"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_12:0
msgid "[Singing.] For many a year he had gnawed it near For meat was hard to come by."
msgstr "[唱歌中] 多年來他一直啃著它，因為肉難得得來。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_14
msgid "[Muttering] Fooood?"
msgstr "[喃喃自語] 食物？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_16
msgid "[Muttering] No. Can't be. Must be dreaming."
msgstr "[喃喃自語] 不。不可能。一定是在做夢。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_20
msgid "Ouch! OUCH! Oooh - just you wait!!"
msgstr "哎呦！哎呦！喔——你等著瞧！！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_20:0
msgid "Oops"
msgstr "哎呀"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_troll_30
msgid "Awww ... hmm, moooore ..."
msgstr "哎呀…嗯，還要多一點…"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple
msgid "Oops - you scared me!"
msgstr "哎呀——你嚇到我了！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple:0
msgid "Are you the one who is throwing rocks down there?"
msgstr "你是那個在下面丟石頭的人嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_10
msgid "Yes, no ... go away!"
msgstr "是，沒有……走開！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_10:0
msgid "Stop hurting innocent passers-by."
msgstr "別再傷害無辜的路人。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_20
msgid "I want to be left alone."
msgstr "我想一個人靜靜。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_20:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_30:0
msgid "I am leaving now."
msgstr "我現在要離開。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_20:1
msgid "Promise me to stop throwing stones, and I will let you go."
msgstr "答應我別再丟石頭，我就放你走。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_20:2
msgid "You will have peace forever now. Attack!"
msgstr "你將永享安寧。攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_22
msgid "Yes, I promise, I promise. Just go, quickly."
msgstr "是的，我答應，我答應。快走吧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_22:0
msgid "Hey, don't push."
msgstr "嘿，別推。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_22:1
msgid "I'll take your word for it."
msgstr "我就相信你了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_30
msgid "No! Please don't do anything to me! I'll promise anything you want. I just want to be left in peace."
msgstr "不！請不要對我做任何事！我答應你任何要求。我只想安靜地待著。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_30:1
msgid "Promise me to stop throwing stones, and I let you go."
msgstr "答應我別再丟石頭，我就放你走。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:ruetmaple_30:2
msgid "I don't care about your promises. Attack!"
msgstr "我不在乎你的承諾。攻擊！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_pup_1
msgid "Yelp - don't hurt us, big wolf."
msgstr "哎呀——別傷害我們，大灰狼。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_pup_1:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_1:0
msgid "Grrr, grrr"
msgstr "嗚嗚，嗚嗚"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_pup_1:1
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_1:2
msgid "Move out of my way!"
msgstr "讓開！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_pup_2
msgid "Help! It's a two-leg!"
msgstr "救命！是兩腳獸！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_pup_2:0
msgid "Kill!"
msgstr "殺！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_1
msgid "Grrr. You look like a grrreat wolf, but smell two-leggish."
msgstr "嗚嗚。你看起來像隻厲害的狼，但聞起來像兩腳獸。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_1:1
msgid "I am the big bad wolf from the stories. Fear me!"
msgstr "我是故事中的大壞狼，畏懼我吧！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_2
msgid "Grrroarrrr! It's a two-leg!"
msgstr "嗚嗚嗚！是雙腳怪！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_10
msgid "You may go thrrrough herrre. No tarrrrying."
msgstr "你可以從這裡通過。別逗留。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_10:0
msgid "Agrrreed."
msgstr "同意。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_10:1
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_10:2
msgid "I am hungrrry."
msgstr "我好餓啊。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_20
msgid "We can prrrovide you with good rrraw meat."
msgstr "我們可以提供你優質的生肉。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_20:0
msgid "Do."
msgstr "做。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_22
msgid "Much grrreat meat. Twenty fourrr bites."
msgstr "好多美味肉。二十四口。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_22:0
msgid "Tha... I mean grrr."
msgstr "那個...我是說咕嚕。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_30
msgid "We've alrrready given you. Now go."
msgstr "我們已經給過你了。現在走吧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_30:0
msgid "Grrr."
msgstr "嗚。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_30:1
msgid "That was looong ago. Long forrrgotten."
msgstr "那是很久以前的事了。早已被遺忘。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_40
msgid "Parrrasite."
msgstr "寄生蟲。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_wolves_42
msgid "Nothing. OK, look herrre."
msgstr "沒什麼。好啦，看這裡。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_2
msgid "You look thoughtfully at the ruins of this old building."
msgstr "你若有所思地凝視著這座古老建築的廢墟。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_2:0
msgid "A terribly depressing place."
msgstr "一個極度令人沮喪的地方。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_2:1
msgid "Could anyone want to live here?"
msgstr "會有人想住在這裡嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_10
msgid "I could renovate this building for myself and settle here."
msgstr "我可以自己整修這棟建築，然後定居於此。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_10:0
msgid "Oh nonsense. I should probably go."
msgstr "別傻了。我該走了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_10:1
msgid "Well, let's look for someone who is willing and able enough to make something appropriate out of this ruin."
msgstr "那麼，我們找個願意且有能力從這廢墟中打造出合適之物的人吧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_12
msgid "But it could be really nice here."
msgstr "不過這裡其實挺不錯的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_12:0
msgid "I might think later about it again."
msgstr "我可能稍後會再考慮。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_12:1
msgid "Should I really settle down?"
msgstr "我真的該安定下來嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_12:2
msgid "No. And I never want to think about it any more."
msgstr "沒有。我再也不想去想它了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_20
msgid "Hmm, If I settle here, that will be the end of my search. Mikhail would hate me."
msgstr "嗯，如果我在這裡定居，那將是我尋找的終點。米哈伊爾會討厭我的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_20:0
msgid "Whatever. I would need someone who doesn't ask questions but who will do anything for gold."
msgstr "隨便。我需要的是不問問題、只為金錢辦事的人。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_20:1
msgid "Whatever. I would need someone who doesn't ask questions. But I don't know anyone like that. Not yet."
msgstr "隨便吧。我需要一個不會多問的人。但我還沒認識這樣的人。還沒。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_20:2
msgid "Oh, this is all nonsense. I will leave this place and go back to looking for Andor."
msgstr "哦，這全是胡說。我會離開這裡，繼續尋找安多爾。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_22
msgid "Good. I'll think about it again when I've found someone rich and discreet to do it."
msgstr "好。我找到既有錢又謹慎的人來做這件事時，再考慮看看。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_30
msgid "And then I'll settle down here."
msgstr "然後我就定居在這裡。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_30:0
msgid "Yes, I want to live here in future."
msgstr "是的，我未來想住在這裡。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_32
msgid "So that's it. I'll settle down here. Andor can look for himself!"
msgstr "就是這樣了。我會在這裡安頓下來。安多爾自己去找吧！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_32:0
msgid "My decision is final. Off to Brimhaven and spend some gold there!"
msgstr "我的決定已定。前往布林哈文，花點金幣吧！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_50
msgid "You are pleasantly surprised at how the ruin has transformed."
msgstr "你驚喜地發現遺跡已經改變了模樣。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_50:0
msgid "Wow! I'm really impressed. It's exactly how I imagined it."
msgstr "哇！真讓我印象深刻。完全如我所想。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_visited_52
msgid ""
"So this is where you will live in the future. Mikhail will have to take care of the rats himself. And Andor? Whatever. I have to think about myself too.\n"
"\n"
"*** End of main quest ***"
msgstr ""
"所以這就是你未來要居住的地方。米哈伊爾得自己照顧那些老鼠了。至於安多爾？隨他"
"去吧。我也得為自己著想。 \n"
"\n"
"*** 主線任務結束 ***"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_memoirs_10
msgid "Writing memoirs ..."
msgstr "撰寫回憶錄中..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_10
msgid "Oh, I know that look on their faces. Someone here wants to order something discreet."
msgstr "喔，我看得出他們臉上的表情。有人想悄悄地下訂單。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_10:0
msgid "Indeed. I want to expand a basement."
msgstr "沒錯。我想擴建地下室。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_12
msgid "Hmm, I don't run a construction company, but you seem to have something unusual in mind. Well, I'm sure I can help you. For a reasonable amount of gold, of course."
msgstr ""
"嗯，我可不是經營建築公司的，但你似乎有些不同尋常的想法。好吧，我相信我能幫上"
"忙。當然，得付合理的金幣。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_12:0
msgid "Of course. It's about an abandoned property far in the southeast."
msgstr "當然。這是關於東南方一處被遺棄的產業。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_12b:0
msgid "Up on a mountain."
msgstr "在山上。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_12c:0
msgid "In the ice, on the summit."
msgstr "在冰層上，於山頂。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_12d:0
msgid "Of Mt.Galmore."
msgstr "關於加爾摩山。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_12e
msgid "No ... WHAT?!!"
msgstr "不... 什麼？！！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_12e:0
msgid "Of Mt.Galmore. Well, if you don't want to do it..."
msgstr "關於加爾摩山。嗯，如果你不想做的話..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_14
msgid "Not so fast. Of course I can help you. I'm just a little ... surprised."
msgstr "別那麼快下定論。我當然可以幫你。只是有點……驚訝。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_14b
msgid "And it won't be ... cheap."
msgstr "而且絕不會是……便宜的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_14c
msgid "What exactly do you have in mind?"
msgstr "你到底在想什麼？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_14c:0
msgid "Well, finally you're talking sensibly. Look, I want the following ..."
msgstr "嗯，終於說得有理了。聽著，我想要以下的東西..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_16
msgid "You give him a piece of paper with your ideas and instructions on how to build it."
msgstr "你給了他一張紙，上面寫著你的想法和建造指示。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_16:0
msgid "Now?"
msgstr "現在嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_16b
msgid "Well, that's something different for a change. It will cost you 50,000 gold pieces."
msgstr "嗯，這倒是個新鮮事。費用是五萬金幣。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_16b:0
msgid "Good. Of course I don't have the money with me. But I'll be back."
msgstr "好。當然我身上沒帶錢，但我會回來的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_16b:1
msgid "OK, here you get 50,000. Make something good out of it."
msgstr "好，這裡給你50,000。拿去做點好東西。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_16b:2
msgid "You get 25,000. Be happy, that's plenty."
msgstr "你得到25,000。開心點，這已經很多了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_18
msgid "So be it. You will be amazed how quickly we work."
msgstr "就這麼定了。你會驚訝我們的工作速度有多快。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_20
msgid "Ah, my new homeowner. Do you like the renovation?"
msgstr "啊，我的新屋主。你喜歡這次的翻修嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_richman_20:0
msgid "It's just perfect."
msgstr "真是完美。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cave_place_crystal_10
msgid "Behold - the room of the seeing stones."
msgstr "請看——觀石之室。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cave_place_crystal_10:0
msgid "Install an oegyth crystal on the table called 'Home'"
msgstr "將奧伊斯晶體安裝在名為「家」的桌上"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cave_place_crystal_10:1
msgid "Install an oegyth crystal on the table called 'Throdna'"
msgstr "將一顆名為「索羅德納」的奧伊斯晶體安裝在桌上"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cave_place_crystal_x
msgid "The crystal starts humming as you put it onto the table."
msgstr "當你將水晶放在桌上時，它開始嗡嗡作響。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_home
msgid "You are watching Mikhail at home."
msgstr "你正在家中觀看米哈伊爾。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_cavea_throdna
msgid "You are watching Throdna and his followers."
msgstr "你正在觀察索羅德納和他的追隨者。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher:0
msgid "Hello oldie."
msgstr "你好，老朋友。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher:3
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher:4
msgid "About the falling star ..."
msgstr "關於那顆流星..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_1
msgid "I'm doing adult things. Come back when you're much stronger. Then we can talk."
msgstr "我正在處理大人的事。等你變得更強再來找我，我們再談。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_1:0
msgid "Just you wait, I'll show you."
msgstr "等著瞧，我會讓你見識。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_3
msgid "A tear in the heavens. Not a star falling, but something cast down."
msgstr "天際的裂縫。不是流星墜落，而是某物被放逐。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_5
msgid "He gestured to the dark Galmore montains in the distant south."
msgstr "他指向遠方南方的黑暗加爾摩山脈。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_11:0
msgid "Kealwea, priest of Sullengard, told me so. Now go on."
msgstr "蘇倫加德的祭司凱爾維亞告訴我的。現在繼續吧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_17
msgid "Only little children could ask such a stupid question. Of course I can't go. Stoutford needs me here."
msgstr "只有小孩子才會問這種愚蠢的問題。我當然不能去。斯托福德需要我留在這裡。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_17:0
msgid "What for?"
msgstr "幹嘛？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_17b
msgid "Silence now!"
msgstr "現在安靜！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_18
msgid "'Bring these shards to me now. Before the mountain's curse draws worse than beasts to them!"
msgstr "現在把這些碎片帶給我。在山的詛咒吸引比野獸更可怕的東西之前！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_18:1
msgid "In fact I have already found some of these stars."
msgstr "事實上，我已經找到了一些這些星星。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_19
msgid "[Ominous voice] Bring The Ten Pieces ..."
msgstr "【不祥的聲音】帶來十片碎片..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_19:0
msgid "Enough, please! I can't think when you are talking like this."
msgstr "夠了，拜託！你這樣講我沒法思考。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_19:1
msgid "Forget it, do it yourself."
msgstr "算了，自己做吧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_19a
msgid "So you really don't want to help? And save the world from this disaster?"
msgstr "所以你真的不想幫忙？不想拯救世界免於這場災難？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_19a:0
msgid "Maybe later. I have to go now."
msgstr "也許以後吧。我現在得走了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_19a:1
msgid "No, I have enough other things to do."
msgstr "不，我還有其他事情要做。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_19b
msgid "Woe, woe! Then leave me. I hope you can live with the guilt."
msgstr "哀哉，哀哉！那就離開我吧。希望你能帶著這份罪惡感活下去。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_20
msgid "Kid, I have told you it wasn't a falling star."
msgstr "孩子，我已經告訴過你，那不是流星。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_20:0
msgid "Anyway, I haven't found any pieces yet."
msgstr "總之，我還沒找到任何碎片。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_20:1
msgid "Anyway, here I have some pieces already."
msgstr "總之，我這裡已經有一些碎片了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_20:4
msgid "Anyway, I have found all of the ten pieces."
msgstr "無論如何，我已找到全部十塊碎片。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_20:5
msgid "Anyway, I have found all of the ten pieces, but I have already given them to Kealwea in Sullengard."
msgstr "無論如何，我已經找齊了所有十塊碎片，但我已經交給了蘇倫加德的Kealwea。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_22
msgid "Don't waste time. Go again and find them. It is urgent!"
msgstr "別浪費時間。再去找他們。情況緊急！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_24
msgid "Good, good. But these are not all of them. It must be ten - where are the others?"
msgstr "很好，很好。但這還不是全部。應該有十個——其他的在哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_27
msgid "What???"
msgstr "什麼？？？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_27:0
msgid "Nothing. Bye."
msgstr "沒什麼。再見。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_30:1
msgid "But I have already given them to Kealwea in Sullengard."
msgstr "但我已經把它們交給蘇倫加德的Kealwea了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_32
msgid "You fool!"
msgstr "你這笨蛋！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_32:0
msgid "It was the right thing to do."
msgstr "這是正確的選擇。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_34
msgid "It is bad. But I won't talk about it anymore."
msgstr "很糟。但我不想再提了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_42
msgid "NOOOOO!!"
msgstr "不～～～～！！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_42:0
msgid "Now you're exaggerating. I'll go then."
msgstr "你現在是在誇張。我這就走。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_56
msgid "I have no gold to give..."
msgstr "我沒有黃金可給..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_starwatcher_60
msgid "But this necklace with a medal on it will remind you of your heroic deed at any time."
msgstr "但這條掛著獎章的項鍊，隨時會提醒你那英勇的事蹟。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_exploded_star_give
msgid "You have found a brightly shining piece of a crystal."
msgstr "你找到了一塊閃耀的水晶碎片。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_exploded_star_give_10
msgid "If you haven't miscounted, you should have found all ten pieces by now."
msgstr "如果你沒數錯，現在應該已經找到全部十塊了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_exploded_star_give_21
msgid "Best bring them to Teccow and ask him what to do with the shining pieces."
msgstr "最好帶他們去找特考，問問他該怎麼處理這些閃亮的碎片。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_exploded_star_give_22
msgid "Best bring them to Kealwea and ask him what to do with the shining pieces."
msgstr "最好帶他們去找Kealwea，問他該如何處理這些閃亮的碎片。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg2_exploded_star_give_23
msgid "Best bring them to Kealwea or to Teccow and ask what to do with the shining pieces."
msgstr "最好帶他們去Kealwea或Teccow，問問該如何處理這些閃亮的碎片。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_prompt_default
msgid "This deserves further investigation, but not now."
msgstr "這值得進一步調查，但現在不是時候。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_prompt_default:0
msgid "I will return later."
msgstr "我稍後會回來。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:sutdover_sign
msgid ""
"Here: Sutdover River\n"
"East: Sullengard\n"
"South: Galmore Mountain"
msgstr ""
"這裡：蘇多弗河\n"
"東方：蘇倫加德\n"
"南方：加爾摩山"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_mt_sign_warning
msgid "Warning: The path ahead leads to the lands of Galmore Mountain. Danger and death await the unprepared. Proceed at your own risk!"
msgstr "警告：前方道路通往加爾摩山脈。未準備者將面臨危險與死亡。請自行承擔風險！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore68_door_10
msgid "As you press your hand against the door, the ancient wood groans under the pressure. With a firm push, the entire structure collapses in a loud crack."
msgstr "當你將手壓在門上，古老的木頭在壓力下呻吟。用力一推，整個結構伴隨著巨響崩塌。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore68_door_20
msgid "The hinges snap free, and the brittle wood shatters as the door comes loose in your grip. You instinctively hurl it to the side, where it hits the ground and crumbles into a pile of splintered wood and dust."
msgstr ""
"鉸鏈啪地斷裂，脆弱的木頭在你手中碎裂。你本能地將門扔到一旁，門撞擊地面，化作"
"一堆破碎的木屑與塵埃。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore68_door_30
msgid "The way forward is now clear, though the remains of the door serve as a testament to its decay."
msgstr "前路已明，唯門扉殘骸證其腐朽。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mt_galmore_tropics_10
msgid "Your jaw drops in amazement..."
msgstr "你的下巴驚訝地掉了下來..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mt_galmore_tropics_10:0
msgid "[Thinking to yourself] What is this place?"
msgstr "[心想] 這是什麼地方？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mt_galmore_tropics_10:1
msgid "[Thinking to yourself] What just happened?"
msgstr "[心想] 剛剛發生了什麼？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_10
msgid "So, what did you think of my work?"
msgstr "那麼，你覺得我的作品如何？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_10:0
msgid "What was that back there?"
msgstr "剛才那是什麼？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_10:1
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_what_was_that_20:1
msgid "You did that? How?"
msgstr "你做到了？怎麼做到的？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_10:2
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_you_did_that_10:0
msgid "Why did you build that here?"
msgstr "你為什麼要在這裡建造那個？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_10:3
msgid "We've already discussed it. Don't you remember?"
msgstr "我們已經討論過了。你不記得嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_10:4
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_vaelric_5:1
msgid "I'm wondering if you could help me? I'm looking for something."
msgstr "我想請你幫個忙？我在找一樣東西。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_what_was_that_20
msgid "Ah, my finest creation! A scene to dazzle the senses, to remind even the most weary traveler of life's beauty. I call it \"Tropical Bliss.\" But enough about what it is. What did it make you feel? Awe? Peace? Perhaps a longing for adventure?"
msgstr ""
"啊，我最傑出的創作！一幕令人目眩神迷的景象，提醒即使是最疲憊的旅人也能感受到"
"生命的美麗。我稱它為「熱帶樂園」。但說這些都不重要，你感受到什麼了？敬畏？寧"
"靜？還是對冒險的渴望？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_what_was_that_20:0
msgid "I liked it!"
msgstr "我喜歡！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_you_did_that_10
msgid "No, no, no. An artist never reveals the \"how.\" The methods are nothing compared to the grandeur of the art itself. Let's not tarnish the magic by pulling back the curtain, shall we?"
msgstr ""
"不，不，不。藝術家從不透露「方法」。技巧比不上藝術本身的壯麗。我們還是別揭開"
"幕後，免得破壞了魔法，好嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_why_build_that_10
msgid "Let me tell you a little story. Long ago, I was an indentured servant, toiling away as a miner here in Galmore. This place was a prison to my spirit, a bleak and joyless pit. When I was freed, I swore I would transform it. I wanted to create something that could transport others to a place of happiness and light, even if just for a moment. That beach is the opposite of this wretched place."
msgstr ""
"讓我告訴你一個小故事。很久以前，我是個契約奴隸，在加爾摩這裡當礦工。這地方囚"
"禁了我的靈魂，是個陰暗無光的深淵。當我獲得自由時，我發誓要改變它。我想創造一"
"個能帶給人們片刻幸福與光明的地方。那片海灘，正是這個可憐之地的對立面。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_why_build_that_10:0
msgid "I see. Thank you for telling me your story."
msgstr "我明白了。謝謝你告訴我你的故事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_illusion_why_build_that_10:1
msgid "Interesting! Very, but I have another question."
msgstr "有趣！非常有趣，但我還有另一個問題。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_vaelric_10
msgid "Sure, ask away."
msgstr "當然，請問吧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_vaelric_10:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_vaelric_5:0
msgid "Do you know of Vaelric, the healer?"
msgstr "你知道治療師瓦爾里克嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_vaelric_20
msgid "Vaelric... Hmm, the name does tickle a memory, but I can't place it. I've heard whispers, perhaps, or seen his name scrawled in some dusty tome. Why do you ask? Is he another artist, or just someone you are curious about?"
msgstr ""
"瓦爾里克……嗯，這名字似乎有點印象，但我想不起來。我可能聽過些耳語，或是在某本"
"塵封的古書上見過他的名字。你為什麼問？他是另一位藝術家，還是你只是好奇他？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_vaelric_20:0
msgid "Oh, never mind. I was just wondering."
msgstr "喔，沒事。我只是好奇而已。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_vaelric_5
msgid "Sorry. You see, ghosts sometimes have bad memories. Or is it just me? Anyway, if we already talked, then why are you back here?"
msgstr ""
"抱歉。你知道，鬼魂有時記性不好。還是只有我這樣？不管怎樣，如果我們已經談過了"
"，那你為什麼又回來了？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore47_vine_10
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore24_vine_10
msgid "As you move your hands up the vine, you begin to hear the vine snapping..."
msgstr "當你雙手沿著藤蔓向上移動時，開始聽到藤蔓斷裂的聲音..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore47_vine_20
msgid "The brittle vines and you go tumbling to the ground."
msgstr "脆弱的藤蔓與你一同跌落地面。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_graveyard_30
msgid "What?! Which one?"
msgstr "什麼？！哪一個？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_graveyard_30:0
msgid "The northwest one near the river."
msgstr "西北方靠近河邊的那個。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_10
msgid "Vaelric pauses, his expression tense as if piecing something together."
msgstr "瓦爾里克停頓，神情緊繃，彷彿在拼湊什麼。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_11
msgid "That's... unsettling. If what you say is true, we need to understand what happened there. Something doesn't sit right with this. Please go back to the graveyard and search for clues."
msgstr ""
"那真是……令人不安。如果你說的是真的，我們需要弄清那裡發生了什麼。這件事總覺得"
"怪怪的。請回到墓地尋找線索。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_11:0
msgid "No, I don't think so. Not this time. I'm tired of helping the pathetic with their problems."
msgstr "不，我不這麼認為。這次不行。我厭倦了幫助那些可憐人解決問題。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_11:1
msgid "OK, but this better be worth my time."
msgstr "好，但這最好值得我花時間。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_11:2
msgid "Actually, I found some clues already."
msgstr "其實，我已經找到一些線索了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_11:3
msgid "I found this bell in the graveyard. [Show Vaelric]"
msgstr "我在墓地裡找到這個鈴鐺。[顯示瓦爾里克]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_11:4
msgid "I found this music box in the graveyard. [Show Vaelric]"
msgstr "我在墓地裡找到這個音樂盒。[顯示瓦爾里克]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_end
msgid "Well that's unfortunate...for you."
msgstr "那可真不幸……對你來說。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_15
msgid "Look for anything that might tell us more about who was buried there and why the grave was disturbed."
msgstr "尋找任何可能告訴我們被埋者身份及墓地被擾原因的線索。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_bell_10
msgid "As you wander around the outskirts of the overgrown graveyard, your eye is drawn to a faint glimmer of metal partially buried beneath the dirt."
msgstr ""
"當你在雜草叢生的墓地邊緣徘徊時，眼前映入一絲隱約的金屬光澤，部分埋藏在泥土中"
"。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_bell_10:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_musicbox_10:0
msgid "[Investigate.]"
msgstr "[調查。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_bell_20
msgid "Kneeling down, you brush aside the thick grass to uncover what appears to be a small, rusted bell, almost entirely concealed by the earth. You dig carefully with your hands, pulling away stubborn roots and clumps of soil. The bell feels unexpectedly heavy in your grasp, as if it holds more than its physical weight, perhaps a story or purpose yet to be uncovered."
msgstr ""
"跪下，你撥開濃密的草叢，發現一個幾乎被土壤完全掩蓋的小鐵鏽鈴鐺。你小心地用手"
"挖掘，拉開頑固的根莖和土塊。鈴鐺在手中出乎意料地沉重，彷彿承載著不只是重量，"
"或許還有尚未揭露的故事與使命。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_musicbox_10
msgid "As you near the disturbed burial plot, a faint outline catches your eye, something small and angular sticking out from the soil a few feet away."
msgstr ""
"當你接近被擾亂的墓穴時，眼前隱約出現一個輪廓，一個小而有棱角的物體從幾步外的"
"土壤中露出。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_musicbox_20
msgid "Kneeling down, you push aside loose dirt and grass with your fingers. Bit by bit, you uncover a weathered music box, its edges worn smooth by time. Though dirt clings to its surface, you can see delicate carvings etched into the wood. Gently lifting it from the ground, you feel an eerie chill, as if the box has been waiting here, forgotten but not entirely at rest."
msgstr ""
"跪下，用手指撥開鬆散的泥土和草叢。你一點一滴地挖掘出一個風化的音樂盒，邊緣因"
"歲月磨得光滑。雖然表面沾滿泥土，但你能看見木頭上細緻的雕刻。輕輕將它從地上拾"
"起，感受到一股詭異的寒意，彷彿這盒子一直在此等待，被遺忘卻未完全安息。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_skeleton_10
msgid "Beneath your feet, under a think layer of grass, you notice what looks to be human bones."
msgstr "在你腳下，厚厚的草層下，你發現疑似人類的骨骸。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_skeleton_10:0
msgid "[Take a closer look.]"
msgstr "[仔細看看。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_skeleton_20
msgid "You kneel down and brush the blades aside, revealing the unmistakable curve of a bone partially buried in the soil. Carefully clearing away more dirt, you uncover fragments of what appears to be a human skeleton. Judging by its position and proximity to the disturbed grave, it seems likely these remains belong to whoever was once buried here."
msgstr ""
"你跪下撥開刀刃，露出部分埋在土中的骨頭彎曲形狀。小心清理更多泥土後，你發現疑"
"似人類骸骨的碎片。根據位置及靠近被擾動的墳墓，這些遺骸很可能屬於曾被埋葬於此"
"者。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_10
msgid "Oh, a human? A human, indeed. How surprising. Yes, surprising indeed, but useful. Yes, useful indeed."
msgstr ""
"哦，是人類？確實是人類。真令人驚訝。是的，確實驚訝，但很有用。是的，確實有用"
"。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_rg_ghost_spawn
msgid "A chill runs down your spine as you step back, leaving the bones undisturbed and pondering what might have led to their unearthing."
msgstr ""
"一陣寒意沿脊椎蔓延，你後退一步，未動這些骸骨，心中思索著是什麼原因讓它們被挖"
"掘出土。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_20
msgid "No, no, no. I ask the questions."
msgstr "不，不，不。該我問問題。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_25
msgid "The graveyard west of here, have you been there?"
msgstr "這裡西邊的墓地，你去過嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_30
msgid "Did you find anything on your way from there to here?"
msgstr "你從那裡到這裡的路上有找到什麼嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_has_qs_thirty_and_fourty_10
msgid "Let me see what you found."
msgstr "讓我看看你找到了什麼。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_has_qs_thirty_and_fourty_10:0
msgid "Yes, but I didn't keep them."
msgstr "是的，但我沒有留著。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_has_qs_thirty_and_fourty_10:1
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_has_qs_thirty_and_fourty_10:2
msgid "Yes, but I didn't keep both."
msgstr "是的，但我沒有兩樣都留著。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_has_qs_thirty_and_fourty_10:3
msgid "Why should I give them to you when I think I need them?"
msgstr "我覺得我需要它們，為什麼要給你？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_has_qs_thirty_and_fourty_dropped_tems
msgid "Bring both of them to me."
msgstr "把他們兩個都帶來給我。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_has_qs_thirty_and_fourty_dropped_tems:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_missing_qs_thirty_or_fourty_20:0
msgid "Is there anything else I should know?"
msgstr "還有什麼我應該知道的嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_missing_qs_thirty_or_fourty_10
msgid "Wait! Don't answer that. I can already tell from the expression on your face that you have not found all that I desire."
msgstr "等等！別回答。我已從你臉上的表情看出，你還沒找到我所渴望的一切。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_ask_for_items_pc_missing_qs_thirty_or_fourty_20
msgid "There are two items that I desire located somewhere between here and the graveyard. Find them and return them to me."
msgstr "我渴望的兩件物品就在這裡和墓地之間的某處。找到它們並帶回給我。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_items_10
msgid "Yes, you need to give me my things or we are not friends."
msgstr "是的，你得把我的東西還給我，否則我們就不是朋友。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_items_10:0
msgid "I already did."
msgstr "我已經做過了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_items_10:1
msgid "What does that mean, \"friends\"?"
msgstr "「朋友」是什麼意思？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_items_10:2
msgid "Umm, I guess so. Here. [You hand over the broken bell and the mysterious music box.]"
msgstr "嗯，我想是吧。給你。[你遞上破損的鈴鐺和神秘的音樂盒。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_10
msgid "I came to Vaelric in my hour of greatest need, bearing little but a token of my past. A ring of no great value to anyone but myself. I was desperate, suffering, and he agreed to help me for a price. Not gold, not silver, but my ring. I was too weak to refuse, too lost to question his demand."
msgstr ""
"我在最需要的時刻來到瓦爾里克身邊，帶著的只有過去的象徵。一枚對他人毫無價值，"
"唯獨對我重要的戒指。我絕望痛苦，他答應幫助我，但要付出代價。不是金銀，而是我"
"的戒指。我太虛弱無力拒絕，太迷茫無法質疑他的要求。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_items_20
msgid "I have a story to tell only to \"friends\". So being my \"friend\" means giving me those two items you found."
msgstr ""
"我有個故事只想告訴「朋友」。所以成為我的「朋友」就得把你找到的那兩樣物品給我"
"。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_steal_ghost_ring_already_stolen
msgid "There's nothing else of value or interest in this drawer as you've already stolen the ring."
msgstr "這個抽屜裡沒有其他有價值或有趣的東西，因為你已經偷走了戒指。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_steal_ghost_ring_10
msgid "Various trinkets and vials clutter the space, but your eyes are drawn to a small, unassuming pouch tucked toward the back. It feels too light for coins, too solid for herbs. Loosening the drawstrings, you reveal a ring, simple yet striking, just as Eryndor described."
msgstr ""
"各種小飾品與藥瓶散落一地，但你的目光被一個隱藏在後方的小袋子吸引。它感覺太輕"
"，不像裝硬幣，也太實，不像裝草藥。鬆開束繩後，你露出一枚戒指，簡單卻引人注目"
"，正如艾林多所描述。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_steal_ghost_ring_5
msgid "As you slide open the wide drawer, its wooden frame creaks loudly, echoing through the quiet house. You freeze, heart pounding, listening for any sign that Vaelric may have heard from downstairs. After a tense moment of silence, you refocus and scan the contents. "
msgstr ""
"當你滑開寬大的抽屜，木框發出嘎吱聲，在寂靜的屋內迴盪。你僵住，心跳加速，傾聽"
"樓下是否有瓦爾里克的動靜。緊張的沉默過後，你重新集中注意力，掃視裡面的物品。 "

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_lie_to_vaelric_10:0
msgid "I wasn't able to find any clues surrounding the grave site. Is there something you're not telling me?"
msgstr "我無法在墓地周圍找到任何線索。你是不是有什麼沒告訴我？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_lie_to_vaelric_20
msgid "No, just a suspicion I had. In any event, thanks for looking into it for me. Good luck on your search for Andor."
msgstr "不，只是我的一個猜測。無論如何，謝謝你幫我調查這件事。祝你尋找安多爾順利。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_10
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_10
msgid "So, you return with my ring?"
msgstr "那麼，你帶回我的戒指了？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_10:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_10:0
msgid "Yes, here it is. [Hand it over]"
msgstr "是的，給你。[交出]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_10:1
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_10:1
msgid "Yes, here it is. [Take it off and hand it over.]"
msgstr "是的，在這裡。[脫下來交出來。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_20
msgid "Eryndor's ghost flickers with anticipation as you hold out the ring. His spectral fingers pass through it at first, but he quickly pulls back, composing himself."
msgstr ""
"艾林多的幽靈因你遞出戒指而閃爍著期待。他的幽靈手指起初穿過戒指，但很快便收回"
"，恢復鎮定。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_20:0
msgid "Now where is my reward?"
msgstr "我的獎勵在哪裡？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_30
msgid "You really did it? You took it from him? Hah... good. Maybe now he will understand what it is to have something stolen away."
msgstr "你真的做到了？你從他那裡搶走了？哈……好。也許現在他會明白被奪走的感受。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_10
msgid "Vaelric's expression darkens, his fingers tightening around his staff. He turns away for a moment, exhaling slowly before speaking."
msgstr "瓦爾里克的表情變得陰沉，手指緊握法杖。他轉過身，緩緩吐氣後開口。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_10:0
msgid "He says you treated him once, but you buried him alive. That's why he haunts you. He wants his ring back, or the hauntings will continue."
msgstr ""
"他說你曾救過他，但你活埋了他。這就是他纏著你的原因。他想要回他的戒指，否則鬼"
"魂將持續作祟。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_10:1
msgid "Please tell me more about Eryndor."
msgstr "請告訴我更多關於艾林多的事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_20
msgid "Eryndor... Yes, I remember. He came to me alone, desperate, barely able to stand. His condition was severe, far beyond anything my tinctures and poultices could mend. I did everything I knew. I bled out the sickness, cooled his fever, forced broth past his lips. But it wasn't enough. One morning, I found him still as death. No breath, no warmth. His skin had gone pale and lifeless."
msgstr ""
"艾林多爾……是的，我記得。他孤身來找我，絕望至極，幾乎站立不穩。他的狀況非常嚴"
"重，遠超過我藥劑和敷料能治癒的範圍。我盡了全力，放血驅病，退燒，強迫他喝湯。"
"但這還不夠。有一天早晨，我發現他已無生命跡象。無呼吸，無溫度，皮膚蒼白無生氣"
"。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_30
msgid "He rubs his temple, his voice quieter now."
msgstr "他揉了揉太陽穴，聲音變得輕柔。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_40
msgid "I had no choice but to lay him to rest. There was no kin to claim him, no priest to see to his rites. So I carried him to the graveyard myself, dug the earth with my own hands, and gave him what peace I could. It was the right thing to do... or so I thought."
msgstr ""
"我別無選擇，只能將他安葬。沒有人認領他，沒神父為他主持儀式。於是我親自將他帶"
"到墓地，用雙手掘土，給予他我能給的安寧。我以為這是正確的事……至少我是這麼想的"
"。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_50
msgid "His jaw tightens, regret flashing in his eyes."
msgstr "他的下巴緊繃，眼中閃過悔恨。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_60
msgid "But I was wrong. I was wrong. Somehow, he still lived. I don't know if it was some illness that mimicked death or if I simply failed to see the life still in him. Either way, my hands put him in that grave, and now his suffering is on me."
msgstr ""
"但我錯了。我錯了。不知怎的，他還活著。我不知道是什麼疾病模擬了死亡，還是我根"
"本沒察覺他仍有生命。不管怎樣，是我親手把他埋進那墓穴，現在他的痛苦由我承擔。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_70
msgid "He hesitates, then steps toward a cabinet, opening a drawer with a sigh."
msgstr "他猶豫了一下，然後走向櫃子，嘆了口氣打開抽屜。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_story_80
msgid "If his spirit will rest with this ring, take it. If that will end this curse, then let it be done."
msgstr "如果他的靈魂會因這枚戒指安息，就拿去吧。若這能終結詛咒，那就讓它成真。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_10:2
msgid "I already gave it to you."
msgstr "我已經給你了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_10:3
msgid "I have it, but I've decided to keep it for myself."
msgstr "我有，但我決定留給自己。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_10:4
msgid "I'm wearing it, and you can't have it."
msgstr "我戴著它，你拿不到。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_10:5
msgid "Yes, but I forgot to bring it with me. I will have to come back later."
msgstr "是的，但我忘了帶來。我得晚點再回來。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_20
msgid "Eryndor's ghost reaches out, his translucent fingers trembling as they hover over the ring in your hand."
msgstr "艾林多的幽靈伸出手，他那透明的手指顫抖著，懸在你手中的戒指上方。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_30
msgid "You... you actually found it? After all this time?"
msgstr "你……你真的找到了？經過這麼久？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_40
msgid "His voice is softer now, no longer laced with bitterness. He takes the ring, though it merely passes through his spectral palm. For a long moment, he stares at it, lost in thought."
msgstr ""
"他的聲音變得柔和，不再帶有苦澀。他接過戒指，儘管它只是穿過他那幽靈般的手掌。"
"良久，他凝視著戒指，陷入沉思。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_50
msgid "When I came to that swamp, I still had my bell, my music box, and this. But this ring was the only thing of real worth. The only thing I had left to bargain with when my body failed me."
msgstr ""
"當我來到那片沼澤時，我還帶著我的鈴鐺、音樂盒，還有這個。但這枚戒指是唯一真正"
"有價值的東西。當我的身體不支時，這是我唯一能用來交換的東西。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_60
msgid "He exhales a slow, weightless sigh, the glow of his form dimming slightly."
msgstr "他緩緩吐出一聲輕盈的嘆息，身形的光芒微微暗淡。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_70
msgid "Vaelric took it as payment, believing he had done all he could for me. And I hated him for it. Hated him for leaving me in the dark, for shoveling earth over me when I still had breath in my lungs."
msgstr ""
"瓦爾里克把它當作報酬，認為他已經盡力幫助我。我因此恨他。恨他讓我陷入黑暗，恨"
"他在我還有氣息時就把土掩埋在我身上。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_80
msgid "He clenches his fist, as if testing the solidity of his fading presence."
msgstr "他緊握拳頭，彷彿在試探自己逐漸消逝的存在感。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_90
msgid "But now... now I see things clearer than I did in life. He was wrong, but not cruel. He truly thought I was beyond saving. And perhaps, in a way, I was."
msgstr ""
"但現在……現在我比生前看得更清楚。他錯了，但並不殘忍。他真的以為我無法救贖。或"
"許，在某種程度上，我確實如此。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_100
msgid "He lifts his gaze to you, his expression unreadable, yet calm."
msgstr "他抬頭望向你，表情難以捉摸，卻平靜自若。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_ring_110
msgid ""
"I have been bound to this world by resentment, by the belief that my suffering was without meaning. But now, with my ring returned, I feel... lighter. It's time to let go.\n"
"\n"
"[With a final, grateful nod, Eryndor begins to fade, his form unraveling like mist in the wind. A whisper lingers in the air before vanishing entirely.]"
msgstr ""
"我被怨恨束縛於此世，深信我的痛苦毫無意義。但如今，戒指歸還，我感覺……輕盈了。"
"是時候放手了。\n"
"\n"
"【帶著最後的感激點頭，艾林多開始消散，身形如風中霧氣般解體。一絲低語在空氣中"
"盤旋，隨即完全消失。】"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_40
msgid "He stares at the ring for a long moment, the glow of his form pulsing unevenly."
msgstr "他凝視著戒指良久，他的身形光芒忽明忽暗。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_50
msgid ""
"This was mine. My last possession, my last choice. He had no right to claim it when my body still had breath. And now? Now it is back in the hands it belongs in.\n"
"\n"
"[Turning the ring in his hand, lost in thought.]\n"
""
msgstr ""
"這是我的。我的最後財產，我的最後選擇。他無權在我尚有一息之時奪走它。現在呢？"
"現在它回到了應屬的手中。\n"
"\n"
"[手中轉動戒指，陷入沉思。]\n"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_give_stolen_ring_60
msgid "But don't think this is over. No... he will still know my presence. He will still feel my breath in the dark. This was never just about the ring. It was about what he did. About what he took from me that I can never get back."
msgstr ""
"但別以為這就結束了。不……他仍會感知我的存在。黑暗中，他仍會感受到我的氣息。這"
"從來不只是關於戒指，而是關於他所做的事。關於他奪走了我永遠無法取回的東西。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eyndor_give_stolen_ring_70
msgid "His expression shifts, something unreadable in his flickering gaze. A strange hesitation. He looks away for a moment before turning back to you."
msgstr ""
"他的表情變了，閃爍的目光中帶著難以捉摸的情緒。奇異的遲疑。他移開視線片刻，然"
"後又轉回看著你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eyndor_give_stolen_ring_70:0
msgid "You're scaring me now."
msgstr "你現在嚇到我了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eyndor_give_stolen_ring_80
msgid "You have done me a service, and for that, I am grateful. But there is something else I need from you. Something unfinished. A debt of my own that I must see repaid."
msgstr ""
"你幫了我一個忙，為此我心存感激。但我還有另一件事需要你幫忙。未完成的事。我必"
"須償還的債務。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_10
msgid "There was one rival who stood above the rest. A relic hunter like myself, relentless and cunning. Her name is Celdar. We crossed paths often, always chasing the same artifacts, always trying to outmaneuver one another. And when it came to one particular prize, I won. The music box. It was something she sought desperately, something she believed should have been hers. I held onto it, not just for its rarity, but because I had bested her."
msgstr ""
"有一位對手高出眾人。她和我一樣是個遺跡獵人，無情且狡猾。她叫賽爾達。我們經常"
"交鋒，總是追逐同樣的神器，互相較勁。在一件特定的獎品上，我贏了——音樂盒。那是"
"她極力尋找的東西，她認為那本該屬於她。我將它緊握，不僅因為它的稀有，更因為我"
"擊敗了她。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_10
msgid "You did it? You were able to help me? You have prevented the future hauntings?"
msgstr "你做到了？你幫助我了？你阻止了未來的纏身？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_10:0
msgid "Yes. Hence my being here with my hand out."
msgstr "是的。所以我才會在這裡伸出手。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_20
msgid "Well, let me start by saying that you have done me a great service, and for that, I will offer you something few others could. I am no merchant, but I do have remedies, ones you will not find elsewhere. One in particular may prove invaluable to you: the Insectbane tonic."
msgstr ""
"嗯，讓我先說，你幫了我大忙，為此我將給你少有人能及的東西。我不是商人，但我有"
"些藥劑，是你別處找不到的。其中一種對你尤其有用：驅蟲藥水。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_30
msgid "This tonic does more than ease a fever or numb the pain of a bite. It eliminates the infection entirely. If you have already fallen victim to the Insect contagion poison, one dose will purge it from your body. But more than that, it grants temporary immunity against reinfection. For a time, no swamp vermin, no festering bite, no tainted sting will take hold of you."
msgstr ""
"這種補藥不僅能退燒或麻痺咬傷的疼痛，還能徹底消除感染。如果你已中昆蟲傳染毒素"
"，一劑即可清除體內毒素。更重要的是，它能暫時免疫再感染。暫時之間，無論是沼澤"
"害蟲、腐爛咬傷或受污染的螫刺，都無法侵襲你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_40
msgid ""
"But such a remedy does not come cheaply. If you wish for me to prepare this tonic, you must gather the necessary ingredients yourself. Here is what I require:\n"
"\n"
"Five Duskbloom flowers. These rare blossoms can be found in the deepest parts of the swamp, but the creatures there tend to be attracted to them. Their properties are delicate, so bring them fresh.\n"
"\n"
"Five Mosquito proboscises. Harvested from the swamp mosquitoes. You will find no shortage of these creatures near stagnant waters, but mind their bites.\n"
"\n"
"Ten bottles of swamp water. You will find plenty just outside my home. Surface water won't do. You'll need to reach deep, past the filth floating on top. The best stuff is settled at the bottom. Dark, thick, and rich with what gives the swamp its potency. Fill the bottles with that. Take these empty bottles and fill them yourself.\n"
"\n"
"One sample of Mudfiend goo. A secretion found in the depths of mines and tunnels along the Duleian Road. It is the key component that binds the other ingredients together."
msgstr ""
"但這樣的療方代價不菲。若你希望我調製此藥水，必須親自收集所需材料。以下是我需"
"要的：\n"
"\n"
"五朵暮花。這種稀有花朵生長於沼澤最深處，但那裡的生物會被它們吸引。花朵性質脆"
"弱，請帶來新鮮的。\n"
"\n"
"五根蚊子口器。採自沼澤蚊子。你在停滯水域附近會發現大量這些生物，但要小心牠們"
"的叮咬。\n"
"\n"
"十瓶沼澤水。你可在我家外找到許多。表面水不可用，需深入水中，越過漂浮的污物。"
"最好的水沉澱於底部，黑暗、濃稠，富含賦予沼澤力量的精華。用這些空瓶自行裝取"
"。\n"
"\n"
"一份泥魔分泌物。來自杜雷安路礦坑與隧道深處的分泌物。它是結合其他材料的關鍵成"
"分。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_40:0
msgid "Great, more work for me."
msgstr "太好了，又有更多工作了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_45
msgid ""
"I require:\n"
"Five Duskbloom flowers. These rare blossoms can be found in the deepest parts of the swamp, but the creatures there tend to be attracted to them. Their properties are delicate, so bring them fresh.\n"
"\n"
"Five Mosquito proboscises. Harvested from the swamp mosquitoes. You will find no shortage of these creatures near stagnant waters, but mind their bites.\n"
"\n"
"Ten bottles of swamp water. You will find plenty just outside my home. Surface water won't do. You'll need to reach deep, past the filth floating on top. The best stuff is settled at the bottom. Dark, thick, and rich with what gives the swamp its potency. Fill the bottles with that. Take these empty bottles and fill them yourself."
msgstr ""
"我需要：\n"
"五朵暮花。這些稀有的花朵生長在沼澤最深處，但那裡的生物會被它們吸引。花朵性質"
"脆弱，請帶來新鮮的。\n"
"\n"
"五根蚊子口器。從沼澤蚊子身上採集。你在停滯的水域附近會發現大量這些生物，但要"
"小心牠們的叮咬。\n"
"\n"
"十瓶沼澤水。你在我家外面就能找到很多。表面水不行，你得深入水底，越過漂浮的污"
"物。最好的水沉澱在底部。黑暗、濃稠，富含賦予沼澤力量的精華。用這些空瓶自己裝"
"滿。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_50
msgid "Bring me these, and I shall prepare ten vials of the tonic for you. But understand this: my craft is no charity. If you seek to replenish your supply, you must pay the price. Four hundred and eighty gold per vial. A steep price, perhaps, but a fair one for something that could mean the difference between life and death."
msgstr ""
"把這些帶給我，我將為你準備十瓶補藥。但請明白：我的手藝不是慈善。如果你想補充"
"庫存，必須付出代價。每瓶四百八十金幣。或許價格不菲，但對於生死攸關之物，這是"
"合理的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_60
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_buy_insectbance_10
msgid "I'll take all of the ingredients and your 4800 gold now and I will mix you up a batch of ten tonics"
msgstr "我現在收下所有材料和你的4800金幣，幫你調配十瓶藥劑。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_60:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_buy_insectbance_10:0
msgid "Here, take them, please."
msgstr "請收下這些。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_Not_enough_gold
msgid "You see, I have to make ten tonics at a time and because I refuse to waste any of them, you must buy all ten at a cost of 4800 gold. Do you have the gold?"
msgstr ""
"你看，我一次得做十瓶藥水，因為我不願浪費，所以你必須一次買十瓶，總價4800金幣"
"。你有足夠的金幣嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_70
msgid "Here you go, ten Insectbane tonics."
msgstr "給你，十瓶蟲絕藥劑。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_other_potions_10
msgid "I also have other potions for sale. Would you like to take a look?"
msgstr "我這裡還有其他藥水出售。要不要看看？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_fill_bottles_10
msgid "This must be where Vaelric suggested that you collect the swamp water from. Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr "這裡應該就是瓦爾里克建議你收集沼澤水的地方。要繼續嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_fill_bottles_10:0
msgid "No way. That stuff looks nasty! Plus, there could be something in there that might badly hurt me."
msgstr "不可能。那東西看起來很噁心！而且裡面可能有會嚴重傷害我的東西。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_fill_bottles_20
msgid "You kneel by the swamp's edge and roll up your sleeve. Surface water will not do. Bracing yourself, you plunge your arm in up to the elbow, feeling the thick, murky liquid seep between your fingers. With a slow, steady motion, you fill each bottle, ensuring they contain the dense, dark water Vaelric requires."
msgstr ""
"你跪在沼澤邊緣，捲起袖子。表層水不夠用。你深吸一口氣，將手臂伸入水中至肘部，"
"感受濃稠混濁的液體滲入指縫。你緩慢而穩定地裝滿每個瓶子，確保裡面裝的是瓦爾里"
"克所需的濃黑水。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_keep_ring_10
msgid "You dare? That ring is mine by right! It was stolen from me in death, just as my life was stolen before its time. I will not suffer another thief to profit from my misery."
msgstr ""
"你竟敢？那枚戒指本是我的！它在我死後被偷走，就如同我的生命被提前奪走。我絕不"
"容許另一個小偷從我的痛苦中獲利。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_keep_ring_20
msgid "Eryndor's spectral form flickers violently, the air around him growing thick with a bitter chill."
msgstr "艾林多的幽靈形態劇烈閃爍，周圍空氣瀰漫著刺骨寒意。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_keep_ring_30
msgid "You may hold it now, but I promise you, it will not remain in your grasp for long. I will tear it from your fingers, along with the flesh that clings to it!"
msgstr ""
"你現在或許握著它，但我保證，它不會在你手中停留太久。我會連同附著的肉一起，從"
"你指間撕下它！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_keep_ring_30:0
msgid "I just hope I don't die for this."
msgstr "我只希望我不會因此喪命。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_defeated_10
msgid "As Eryndor's spectral form wavers, his anguished cry echoes through the Galmore encampment before fading into the night. His essence shatters like mist caught in the wind, dissolving into nothing, but the air remains heavy, charged with an unseen weight. The encampment is silent, yet the silence is not one of peace."
msgstr ""
"當艾林多的幽靈形體動搖時，他痛苦的呼喊在加爾摩營地迴盪，隨後消逝於夜色中。他"
"的靈魂如風中迷霧般破碎，化為虛無，但空氣依舊沉重，帶著無形的壓力。營地寂靜無"
"聲，卻非和平的寂靜。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_10
msgid "So, it is done? You struck him down, ended his torment by force?"
msgstr "那麼，事情結束了？你擊倒了他，用武力終結了他的痛苦？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_20
msgid "I suppose I should have expected as much."
msgstr "我想我早該料到會這樣。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_30
msgid "His gaze lingers on you, his expression hard to read. Somewhere between frustration and resignation."
msgstr "他的目光停留在你身上，表情難以捉摸。介於挫折與無奈之間。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_40
msgid "And what of the hauntings? Is it over?"
msgstr "那幽靈事件呢？結束了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_50
msgid "With your hesitation preventing you from getting a word in..."
msgstr "你的猶豫讓你無法插話..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_60
msgid "I see. You took the ring for yourself and left his spirit unfulfilled. That was your choice."
msgstr "我明白了。你奪走了戒指，讓他的靈魂無法安息。那是你的選擇。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_60:0
msgid "But, but..."
msgstr "但、但是…"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_70
msgid "He lets out a slow breath, his voice quieter now, laced with disappointment."
msgstr "他緩緩吐出一口氣，聲音變得輕柔，帶著失望。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_80
msgid "Andor would have done better."
msgstr "安多爾本可以做得更好。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_90
msgid "[Turning away, he mutters:] I will take what peace I can, while it lasts. But do not expect my gratitude."
msgstr "[轉身低語：] 我會在和平尚存時，盡量享受。但別指望我感激你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_20
msgid ""
"He worked his craft, took his payment, and let me rest. But I never awoke under his roof. I awoke beneath the earth, buried like a thing to be discarded. I clawed my way free, but the world had already moved on without me. My body failed, my breath faltered, and I perished alone.\n"
"\n"
"And now, even in death, I remain. I am left with nothing while Vaelric hoards the last piece of my past. That ring was mine, and it was never his to take."
msgstr ""
"他施展手藝，收取報酬，讓我得以安歇。但我從未在他屋簷下醒來。我是在地下醒來，"
"被埋葬如同棄物。我掙扎著爬出，但世界早已沒有我的存在。我的身體衰敗，呼吸微弱"
"，孤獨中死去。\n"
"\n"
"如今，即使死去，我依然存在。我一無所有，而瓦爾里克卻囤積著我過去的最後一塊碎"
"片。那枚戒指是我的，從未屬於他。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_30
msgid "Return my ring, and this torment ends for both of us. Vaelric can go on with his life, and I will trouble him no more. That is my offer."
msgstr ""
"還我戒指，這折磨便可結束。我們都能解脫。瓦爾里克可以繼續他的生活，而我不會再"
"打擾他。這是我的條件。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_30:0
msgid "You have been wronged, and I will not let that stand. I will get your ring back, one way or another."
msgstr "你受了委屈，我絕不容忍。我會想盡辦法幫你奪回戒指。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_30:1
msgid "If what you say is true, then this should not be settled with more deceit. I will speak to Vaelric. Maybe there is a way to resolve this fairly."
msgstr ""
"如果你說的是真的，那麼不該再用欺瞞來解決。我會去找瓦爾里克談談，也許能找到公"
"平解決的方法。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_jump_to30
msgid "We were in the middle of my story..."
msgstr "我們正說到一半..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_side_with_eryndor_10
msgid "Then you see the truth. Vaelric took from me when I had nothing, and now he clings to what is not his. I will be waiting, but not always here in this spot. I will not forget this, friend."
msgstr ""
"然後你看見了真相。瓦爾里克在我一無所有時奪走了我的東西，現在他卻緊抓著不屬於"
"他的東西。我會等待，但不會永遠待在這個地方。我不會忘記這一切，朋友。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_help_both_10
msgid "Fair? What was fair about what he did to me? Do you think words will undo my suffering? I have lingered here too long for empty promises. But... if you truly mean to help, then do not return with excuses. Only with my ring."
msgstr ""
"公平？他對我所做的事哪裡公平？你以為言語能抹去我的痛苦？我在這裡逗留太久，聽"
"夠了空洞的承諾。但……如果你真心想幫忙，就別帶著藉口回來。只帶著我的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_vaelric_help_both_10:0
msgid "I will come back with answers."
msgstr "我會帶著答案回來。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_20
msgid "Eryndor looks down at the music box, his expression unreadable."
msgstr "艾林多凝視著音樂盒，表情難以捉摸。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_30
msgid "But now? What does a dead man need with a relic? It is time to put an old contest to rest. I want you to find Celdar and give this to her. Not as a gesture of kindness, but because it is right."
msgstr ""
"但現在呢？死人還需要聖物做什麼？是時候結束這場舊日的爭鬥了。我想讓你去找賽爾"
"達，把這個交給她。不是出於善意，而是因為這是正確的。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_30:0
msgid "\"Celdar\", you say? I think I met her."
msgstr "你說「賽爾達」？我想我見過她。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_30:1
msgid "\"Celdar\"? Where can I find her?"
msgstr "「賽爾達」？我在哪裡能找到她？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_40
msgid ""
"Celdar is from Sullengard. If you don't recall speaking with her, that would be the place to start. But I suspect you have met her before. She is not one easily forgotten. She does not tolerate fools, nor those who waste her time with petty sales or empty words. Always clad in that garish purple dress of hers, standing out as if daring the world to challenge her. And she has never taken a loss lightly.\n"
"\n"
"[He holds out the music box, waiting for you to take it.]"
msgstr ""
"賽爾達來自蘇倫加德。如果你不記得和她談過，那就從那裡開始。但我懷疑你以前見過"
"她。她令人難以忘懷。她不容忍愚人，也不接受浪費她時間的瑣碎銷售或空洞言語。她"
"總穿著那件刺眼的紫色洋裝，彷彿在挑戰世界。她從不輕易認輸。\n"
"\n"
"[他遞出音樂盒，等你接過。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_default_10
msgid "Have you brought the music box to Celdar yet?"
msgstr "你把音樂盒帶給賽爾達了嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_music_box_default_15
msgid "What are you waiting for? Get going!"
msgstr "你還在等什麼？快出發吧！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:sullengard_citizen_celdar
msgid "I thought you were looking for your brother? What's the matter, you couldn't find Andor, so you gave up and are now looking for someone new?"
msgstr "我以為你在找你哥哥？怎麼了，找不到安多爾就放棄，現在改找別人了？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:sullengard_godrey_celdar
msgid "Now there's a name I haven't heard in a long time. I don't think she's been in town for a long time."
msgstr "這名字好久沒聽過了。我想她很久沒來過鎮上。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:sullengard_godrey_celdar:0
msgid "Oh, OK, thanks."
msgstr "喔，好，謝謝。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:sullengard_town_clerk_celdar_10
msgid "Oh, how can I help you? It's not Mayor Ale is it?"
msgstr "哦，有什麼我可以幫忙的嗎？不會是市長艾爾吧？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:sullengard_town_clerk_celdar_10:0
msgid "What? No. I am looking for Celdar. I've heard she lives here. Is she around by chance?"
msgstr "什麼？不，我在找賽爾達。我聽說她住在這裡。她有在嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:sullengard_town_clerk_celdar_20
msgid "Yes she is a local, but she hasn't been seen around here for a while. Last I heard, she was headed for Brimhaven to do some shopping. Although, it is a long journey so she probably had to rest along the way."
msgstr ""
"是的，她是本地人，但最近一段時間沒人在這裡見過她。據我所知，她正前往布林哈文"
"購物。不過路途遙遠，她大概中途得休息一下。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_10
msgid "Eryndor? That scoundrel finally got what was coming to him, did he? And now you're here, dangling a prize in front of me, expecting what? Gratitude? Payment? Hah! Whatever trick you think you're playing, I'm not biting."
msgstr ""
"艾林多？那個無賴終於得到了應有的報應，是吧？現在你來了，擺出獎品在我面前，想"
"要什麼？感謝？報酬？哼！不管你耍什麼花招，我可不會上當。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_15
msgid "Celdar pauses, and narrows her eyes as she assesses you."
msgstr "賽爾達停下腳步，眯眼審視著你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_15:0
msgid "I have this music box. [Showing it to her.]"
msgstr "我有這個音樂盒。[給她看。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_20
msgid "Wait... you're serious, aren't you? He actually sent you to bring me the music box? Hmph. That doesn't sound like him. He was always the type to take, not give."
msgstr ""
"等等……你是認真的吧？他真的派你來給我這個音樂盒？哼，這不像他的作風。他一向是"
"拿不給的那種人。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_20:0
msgid "He wanted to do the right thing."
msgstr "他想做正確的事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_25
msgid "The right thing? Eryndor always did have a flair for the dramatic, but this... this is unexpected."
msgstr "正確的選擇？艾林多爾一向擅長戲劇性，但這……這真是出乎意料。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_30
msgid "While crossing her arms, she begins to study you."
msgstr "她雙臂交叉，開始打量你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_35
msgid "I spent years chasing that wretched box, only for him to snatch it out from under me. And now, after death, he decides to hand it over? What, am I supposed to be touched?"
msgstr ""
"我花了多年追尋那詛咒的盒子，結果卻被他搶走。現在，我死了，他才決定交出來？我"
"該感動嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_40
msgid "She scoffs but reaches out for the box."
msgstr "她嗤之以鼻，但還是伸手去拿盒子。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_40:0
msgid "You reach out, your hands meet with the mysterious music box held between your hands and she takes it from you."
msgstr "你伸出手，雙手觸碰到手中神秘的音樂盒，她從你手中接過。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_40:1
msgid "I can't believe this, but I forgot to bring the music box. Sorry. I will have to come back later. Stay here."
msgstr "真不敢相信，我竟然忘了帶音樂盒。抱歉，我得晚點再回來。你先留在這裡。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_40:2
msgid "I just gave you that music box..."
msgstr "我剛把那個音樂盒給你……"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_45
msgid "Hmph. Fine. If he truly meant it, then I'll take it. Not that it changes anything. Eryndor and I were never friends, and his little gesture won't rewrite history. But... at least he finally understood what was mine to begin with."
msgstr ""
"哼。好吧。如果他真心如此，那我就收下。也不會改變什麼。艾林多和我從未是朋友，"
"他那點小動作改不了歷史。但……至少他終於明白了本該屬於我的東西。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_50
msgid "She examines the box for a moment, running a hand over it before giving you a final look."
msgstr "她檢查了盒子片刻，手輕撫其上，然後最後看了你一眼。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_55
msgid "Here, take this longsword, I have no need for it. But..."
msgstr "拿去吧，這把長劍我用不著。不過..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_60
msgid "Tell me, does he rest easy now, or is he still out there, clinging to unfinished business?"
msgstr "告訴我，他現在是否安息了，還是仍在外頭，執著未了的心願？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_60:0
msgid "No, he's not at peace. He's still out there, lingering about, bound by unfinished business."
msgstr "不，他並未安息。他仍在外徘徊，被未了的心願束縛著。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_65
msgid "Celdar exhales sharply, her fingers tightening around the music box as she looks away for a brief moment."
msgstr "賽爾達急促呼氣，手指緊握音樂盒，短暫移開視線。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_70
msgid "Hmph. Figures. The stubborn fool never knew when to let go."
msgstr "哼。果然如此。那個固執的傢伙從不懂得放手。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_75
msgid "She turns the box over in her hands, her expression briefly unreadable. Then, softer, almost to herself:"
msgstr "她手中翻轉著盒子，表情短暫難以捉摸。然後，聲音柔和，幾乎自語般地說："

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_80
msgid "Chasing relics, chasing victories, chasing debts that can never be repaid... I suppose it doesn't matter now."
msgstr "追尋遺物，追逐勝利，追討永無法償還的債務……我想現在已無所謂了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_85
msgid "She shakes her head, composing herself before glancing at you once more."
msgstr "她搖了搖頭，整理情緒後再次看向你。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_90
msgid "Well, he made his choices. And I made mine. But... I wouldn't wish that kind of fate on anyone. Not even him."
msgstr ""
"嗯，他做了他的選擇。我也做了我的選擇。但……我不會希望那種命運降臨在任何人身上"
"。即使是他也不例外。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_95
msgid "With that, she straightens her posture, her usual sharpness returning, though the moment of reflection lingers in her eyes."
msgstr "說完，她挺直身姿，恢復了往日的銳利，眼中卻仍帶著一絲沉思。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:celdar_musicbox_95:0
msgid "I hope that in the future, that music box brings your happiness."
msgstr "我希望未來那個音樂盒能帶給你幸福。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_currently65
msgid "What are you waiting for? Go get my ring back from Vaelric."
msgstr "你還在等什麼？快去從瓦爾里克那裡拿回我的戒指。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_restless
msgid "I feel restless here, I was a traveler when I was alive."
msgstr "我在這裡感到不安，生前我是個旅人。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_restless:0
msgid "Umm...OK. That was random."
msgstr "嗯……好吧。真隨興。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_defeated_eryndor_15
msgid "He exhales sharply, shaking his head."
msgstr "他猛地呼出一口氣，搖了搖頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_eryndor_defeated_15
msgid ""
"The hauntings have ceased. Vaelric will know relief, at least for a time.\n"
"\n"
"And yet, a lingering unease settles in your gut. Something about the way Eryndor vanished, unfinished and unresolved, leaves you with the gnawing certainty that his story is not truly over."
msgstr ""
"鬧鬼現象已停止。瓦爾里克終於能暫時獲得安寧。\n"
"\n"
"然而，你心中仍有揮之不去的不安。艾林多的消失如此倉促且未了，讓你確信他的故事"
"尚未真正結束。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:clinging_mud_does_not_have
msgid "Sticky mud coats your fet and legs, making every motion sluggish and heavy."
msgstr "黏稠的泥巴覆蓋你的腳和腿，使每個動作都變得遲緩沉重。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore24_vine_20
msgid "The brittle vines blow off into the wind while you go tumbling to the ground."
msgstr "脆弱的藤蔓隨風飄散，而你則跌倒在地。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_prompt
msgid "As you walk by the table, in the corner of your eye, you catch a glimpse of someone's journal. Do you want to read it?"
msgstr "當你走過桌子時，眼角瞥見有人留下的日記。你想閱讀嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_prompt:0
msgid "Nah, I don't have the time or the interest."
msgstr "不，我沒時間也沒興趣。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_prompt:1
msgid "Why not? I might learn something. Let's start with the page on the bottom of the pile."
msgstr "為什麼不呢？我或許能學到些什麼。就從堆底的那頁開始吧。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_1
msgid ""
"Day 1\n"
"I don't know if I'll ever see Remgard again, but if anyone finds this, know that I tried. I ran the moment I saw a chance, slipping past the guards, through the tunnels, and into the night. I thought the mountain would be my salvation, but it has become another prison. My leg is wounded from a bad fall, and my rations were left behind in my haste. This cabin is the only thing keeping me from dying out in the cold.\n"
"\n"
"I think about you, Elira. About little Matrin and your sweet voice by the fire. I promised I would return, but now I fear I will break that promise. If only I had been stronger. If only I had never been taken to Undertell."
msgstr ""
"第1天\n"
"我不知道是否還能再見到雷姆加德，但如果有人找到這個，請知道我曾努力過。當我看"
"到機會時，我立刻逃跑，悄悄避開守衛，穿過隧道，逃入黑夜。我以為山脈會是我的救"
"贖，卻成了另一座監獄。我的腿因跌落受傷，匆忙中糧食也被落下。這間小屋是我在寒"
"冷中存活的唯一依靠。\n"
"\n"
"我想著你，艾莉拉。還有小馬特林，以及你在火旁溫柔的聲音。我曾承諾會回來，但現"
"在我怕我會違背這個承諾。要是我能更堅強些，要是我從未被帶到幽訴之境。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_1:0
msgid "Let's read the next page."
msgstr "讓我們讀下一頁。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_1:1
msgid "I've had enough."
msgstr "我受夠了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_2
msgid ""
"Day 2\n"
"I tried again tonight. The moment darkness swallowed the land, I hobbled my way to the river's edge, thinking I could follow the water down the mountain. But they were there - the river wretches. I heard them first, the awful gurgling croaks, the splashing as they slithered from the water. Their eyes glowed like dying embers, watching me, waiting.\n"
"\n"
"I barely made it back inside before one of them lunged. My leg is worse now, and I have nothing left to bind it.\n"
"\n"
"The hunger gnaws at me. I tried fishing, but the hooks in this cabin are rusted, the line too weak. There are old nets, but I do not have the strength to set them.\n"
"\n"
"Tomorrow, I will try again. I have to."
msgstr ""
"第 2 天\n"
"今晚我又試了。黑暗吞噬大地的瞬間，我蹣跚地走到河邊，想沿著水流下山。但他們就"
"在那裡——河流惡鬼。我先聽到他們，那可怕的咕嚕聲和他們從水中滑出時的濺水聲。他"
"們的眼睛像將熄滅的餘燼般發光，注視著我，等待著。\n"
"\n"
"我勉強在其中一個衝過來前回到屋內。我的腿更糟了，繃帶也用完了。\n"
"\n"
"飢餓在折磨我。我試著釣魚，但小屋裡的魚鉤都生鏽了，魚線也太脆弱。還有舊網，但"
"我沒有力氣設置。\n"
"\n"
"明天，我會再試一次。我必須這麼做。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_2:0
msgid "This is mildly interesting. Let's read the next page."
msgstr "這還算有趣。讓我們讀下一頁。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_2:1
msgid "I've had enough. Time to go kill something."
msgstr "我受夠了。該去殺點東西了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_3
msgid ""
"Day 3\n"
"The cold seeped into my bones last night. It is colder here than in the mines, though there we had fire - if we dug enough, if we obeyed. My hands shake too much to write properly. I tore the floorboards loose, hoping for dry wood, but it does little to warm this place.\n"
"\n"
"I dreamed of the Heartstone. Of its glow deep in the dark, pulsing like a dying heart. We bled for it, all of us. Bent our backs, broke our bodies. They say it fuels the forges of kings, but to us, it was nothing but suffering. I wonder if the others still dig, still rot in the depths of Undertell. Or if they, too, have tried to flee and perished in the dark."
msgstr ""
"第三天\n"
"昨夜寒氣滲入骨髓。這裡比礦坑還冷，雖然那裡有火——只要我們挖得夠深，只要我們服"
"從。我的手抖得太厲害，無法好好書寫。我撬開地板，希望找到乾木頭，但這對暖和這"
"地方幫助不大。\n"
"\n"
"我夢見了心石。它在黑暗深處發光，脈動如垂死的心臟。我們為它流血，所有人。彎腰"
"勞作，身體破碎。他們說它是王者熔爐的燃料，但對我們來說，只有痛苦。我想知道其"
"他人是否仍在挖掘，仍在幽訴之境的深處腐朽。或者他們也試圖逃離，卻在黑暗中喪生"
"。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_3:0
msgid "This is getting better. Let's read the next page."
msgstr "情況越來越好。讓我們讀下一頁。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_3:1
msgid "Reading is difficult. Killing is easy. I'm out of here."
msgstr "閱讀很難。殺人很簡單。我走了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_4
msgid ""
"Day 4?\n"
"I lost track of time. The hunger dulls everything. My wound festers, and I am too weak to move. I hear the wretches outside every night now, closer than before. As if they can smell my weakness.\n"
"\n"
"I wrote a letter to you, Elira. It's tucked beneath the heartstone. If anyone finds this journal, please... please bring it to Remgard. Let her know I never stopped trying to return.\n"
"\n"
"I will rest now. Perhaps in dreams, I will walk home at last."
msgstr ""
"第四天？\n"
"我已忘了時間。飢餓使一切變得遲鈍。傷口潰爛，我虛弱得無法動彈。現在每晚我都聽"
"見外頭那些可憐鬼的聲音，比以前更近了。彷彿他們能嗅出我的虛弱。\n"
"\n"
"我寫了一封信給你，艾莉拉。它藏在心石下方。如果有人找到這本日記，請……請帶到雷"
"姆加德。讓她知道我從未停止想要回家的努力。\n"
"\n"
"我現在要休息了。也許在夢中，我終能踏上回家的路。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_4:0
msgid "Wow. This is awful to read."
msgstr "哇，這真讓人難以忍受。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_4:1
msgid "What a weak creature this guy was."
msgstr "這傢伙真是個弱不禁風的生物。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_66_house_journal_4:2
msgid "This journal is so ancient looking that there's no way this Elira person is in Remgard or even still alive."
msgstr "這本日誌看起來如此古老，根本不可能是這個艾莉拉人在雷姆加德，甚至還活著。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_down
msgid "With a deafening noise, the floor collapses and you fall through, along with stones and floorboards, into the basement."
msgstr "伴隨震耳欲聾的巨響，地板坍塌，你與石塊和地板一同墜入地下室。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_key
msgid "The remains of the ladder are too high for you to reach."
msgstr "梯子的殘骸太高，無法觸及。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop
msgid "Here is a good place to drop some rocks."
msgstr "這裡是丟石頭的好地方。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1:0
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1:7
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_41:0
msgid "Drop a rock."
msgstr "丟下一塊石頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop:1
msgid "I have no rocks to drop."
msgstr "我沒有石頭可丟。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1
msgid "Plop."
msgstr "啪嗒。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1:1
msgid "Ten. Phew. Drop another rock."
msgstr "十。呼。再丟一塊石頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1:2
msgid "Twenty. I'm getting hot. Anyway - drop a rock."
msgstr "二十。我開始發熱了。總之——丟一塊石頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1:3
msgid "Thirty. Drop another rock."
msgstr "三十。再丟一塊石頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1:4
msgid "Forty. Keep going! Drop a rock."
msgstr "四十。繼續！丟一塊石頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1:5
msgid "Fifty. Things are moving forward. Drop a rock."
msgstr "五十。事情正在推進。丟一塊石頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_1:6
msgid "Sixty. Looks almost ready. Come on, drop a rock."
msgstr "六十。看起來差不多準備好了。來，丟塊石頭。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_41
msgid "Wow, the pile is rising at last."
msgstr "哇，堆積終於開始升高了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_drop_42
msgid "Now the pile of stones looks high enough for me to reach the ladder."
msgstr "現在這堆石頭看起來夠高，可以讓我夠到梯子。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_climb1
msgid "Maybe I could climb these crates to get to the remains of the ladder somehow?"
msgstr "也許我可以爬上這些箱子，設法到達梯子的殘骸？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_climb2_10
msgid "Could this chest work as an improvised staircase?"
msgstr "這個箱子能當臨時樓梯用嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_climb2_10:0
msgid "Let's try to push the chest next to the barrels."
msgstr "試著把箱子推到桶子旁邊。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_58_h1_climb2_20
msgid "With a lot of force you push the box forward."
msgstr "你用很大的力氣將箱子推向前方。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_15_shield_10
msgid "You feel something hard beneath your feet. When you instinctively look down you notice some metal. Do you want to explore it?"
msgstr "你感覺腳下有硬物。下意識地低頭一看，發現了金屬。要探索看看嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_15_shield_10:0
msgid "It's time to get dirty...well, even more dirty."
msgstr "是時候弄髒了……嗯，更髒一點。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_15_shield_20
msgid "Kneeling down, you push aside loose dirt and rocks with your fingers. Bit by bit, you uncover a wooden shield braced with metal, its dirty and wet, but otherwise it's in great condition."
msgstr ""
"跪下，用手指撥開鬆散的泥土和石塊。你逐漸挖出一面木製盾牌，鐵箍加固，雖然骯髒"
"且潮濕，但狀況良好。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore33_vine_10
msgid "As you near the top, a streaking shadow crosses overhead. A hawk, sharp-eyed and swift, releases a piercing screech. The sound jolts you, fear sparks in your chest, and your grip gives way."
msgstr ""
"當你接近頂端時，一道暗影掠過頭頂。一隻銳利迅捷的鷹發出刺耳的尖叫聲。這聲音讓"
"你震驚，胸中湧起恐懼，你的握力隨之鬆開。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore33_vine_20
msgid "As you fall, you watch the hawk fly off out of sight."
msgstr "當你墜落時，你看著老鷹飛離視線。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_23_unknown_book_10
msgid "You brush aside the branches and find an old chest tucked behind the tree. Inside lies a weathered tome, bound in cracked leather. It's an unknown book on the art of fighting. You open it and begin to read, flipping through dense pages until a chapter catches your eye, \"Striking by Rhythm and Force\". It speaks of precision and control, of mastering your strikes. As you finish reading, knowledge sharpens your mind and your weapon feels steadier in your grasp. Just then, a hawk screeches overhead and dives. It snatches the book from your hands and vanishes into the sky. But in your grip remains a single page, torn free in the scuffle. Somehow you instantly feel like a better fighter."
msgstr ""
"你撥開樹枝，發現一個舊箱子藏在樹後。裡面有一本破舊的書，封面是龜裂的皮革。這"
"是一本不知名的戰鬥藝術書籍。你翻開它，開始閱讀，翻過密密麻麻的頁面，直到一章"
"吸引了你的目光：「節奏與力量的打擊」。書中談及精準與控制，教你掌握攻擊技巧。"
"讀完後，知識使你的思緒更敏銳，武器在手中也更穩固。就在此時，一隻鷹在頭頂尖叫"
"並俯衝而下，從你手中搶走了書本，消失在天空中。但你手中仍握著一頁，在混亂中被"
"撕下。你立刻感覺自己成為了更好的戰士。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler1_10
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler3_10
msgid "You spot a glint of crimson feathers and a golden beak in the distance, unlike any bird you've seen before..."
msgstr "你遠處瞥見一抹猩紅羽毛和金色鳥喙，與你見過的任何鳥類都不同……"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler2_spawn_somewhere_else
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler3_spawn_somewhere_else
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler3_2_spawn_somewhere_else
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler4_spawn_somewhere_else
msgid "...but it sees you and runs away. Maybe you will see it somewhere else?"
msgstr "...但它看到你就逃走了。也許你會在別處遇見它？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:0
msgid "Huh, it ran away from me? That's never happened to me before."
msgstr "咦，它竟然從我這逃走了？我以前從沒遇過這種事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:1
msgid "What, it ran away again?"
msgstr "什麼，又跑掉了？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:2
msgid "Maybe it's the sound of my boots that's scaring it off...I should try taking them off and moving quieter."
msgstr "也許是我的靴子聲嚇跑了牠……我應該試著脫掉靴子，輕聲移動。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:3
msgid "Oh, I have an idea. Let's leave some corn for it. Yeah, that should work to gain its trust."
msgstr "喔，我有個主意。留些玉米給它。對，這樣應該能取得它的信任。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:4
msgid "Hey, maybe I could leave a red apple. It might help it warm up to me."
msgstr "嘿，也許我可以留個紅蘋果。這可能會讓它對我更親近。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:5
msgid "How about I set out a green apple? That could be enough to earn its trust."
msgstr "要不要我放一顆青蘋果？這或許足以贏得它的信任。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:6
msgid "What if I leave an orchard apple from Deebo's farm behind? That might gain its trust."
msgstr "如果我留下迪博農場的一顆果園蘋果呢？那或許能贏得它的信任。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:7
msgid "I know, I'll drop a rosethorn apple on the ground. Let's see if that gets me on its good side."
msgstr "我知道了，我會把玫棘蘋果丟在地上。看看這能不能讓它對我好一點。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flees:8
msgid "What am I doing wrong here?"
msgstr "我到底哪裡做錯了？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler_no_flee
msgid "It does not see you!"
msgstr "它沒看到你！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler2_10
msgid "Just over there on the hill, a creature with obsidian feathers and a gleaming golden beak watches from afar..."
msgstr "就在那座小丘上，有一隻擁有黑曜石羽毛和閃亮金喙的生物在遠處注視著……"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler3_2_10
msgid "There's a glimpse of something rare ahead, dark feathers and a vivid red crest catching the light as it turns its head..."
msgstr "前方隱約可見罕見之物，黑色羽毛與鮮紅冠羽隨轉頭閃耀光芒…"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_flee_stoutford_filler4_10
msgid "You see a rare bird in the distance, its form striking against the wild - red-crested, golden-beaked, almost like a story come to life..."
msgstr ""
"你遠處看到一隻稀有的鳥，身形在荒野中格外醒目——紅冠、金喙，彷彿故事中的生物活"
"現眼前……"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:rubycrest_strider_killed_10
msgid "You've just killed the Rubycrest strider bird, but for an unexplainable reason, you feel as if you've done the wrong thing."
msgstr "你剛剛殺死了紅冠長足鳥，但不知為何，心中卻覺得自己做錯了事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_not_welcome
msgid "Leave! You are not welcome here."
msgstr "離開！你不受歡迎。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_10
msgid "Oh, a visitor? Welcome! Come, come. Sit down."
msgstr "喔，有訪客？歡迎！請進，請坐。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_10:0
msgid "No, thanks, I have to go."
msgstr "不用了，謝謝，我得走了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_10:2
msgid "Why are you up here alone?"
msgstr "你怎麼會獨自一人待在這裡？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_player_killed_rubycrest_10
msgid "...wait a second. Hold that thought. [while leaning in...] Please come closer. [He sniffs your hands]"
msgstr "...等一下。先別急。［身體前傾……］請靠近一點。［他聞了聞你的手］"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_20
msgid "You killed my friend!"
msgstr "你殺了我的朋友！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_20:0
msgid "Well, he probably deserived it. Whoever this person is."
msgstr "嗯，他大概是活該。不管這人是誰。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_20:1
msgid "Me? Nah. Not me. [Lie] I've never killed anybody."
msgstr "我？不，不是我。[謊言] 我從未殺過任何人。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_30
msgid "Yes, yes you most certainly killed him. His scent is all over your hands."
msgstr "是的，你確實殺了他。他的氣味全沾在你的手上。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_30:0
msgid "His scent?"
msgstr "他的氣味？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_40
msgid "You killed my best friend! You killed the only thing I have to talk to up here on these hills."
msgstr "你殺了我最好的朋友！你殺了我在這山丘上唯一能說話的對象。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_40:0
msgid "Who did I kill? You are the only person up here that I've encountered."
msgstr "我殺了誰？你是我在這裡唯一遭遇過的人。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_50
msgid "You killed the unique and exotic bird that calls these hills \"home\". My best friend! So I am now asking you to leave. [pointing his finger towards the door.]"
msgstr "你殺死了這片山丘的獨特珍稀鳥類，我最好的朋友！所以我現在請你離開。[指向門口]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_50:0
msgid "Oh, but I can stay."
msgstr "喔，但我可以留下。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_50:1
msgid "I will stay. You are not the boss of me."
msgstr "我會留下。你不是我的老闆。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_15
msgid "Just a man with a brush and a view. I spend my days painting what others overlook."
msgstr "只是一個拿著畫筆、擁有遠景的男子。我用日子描繪他人忽略的風景。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_15:0
msgid "Oh, but what about..."
msgstr "喔，那..."

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_15:1
msgid "Well, I'm just an explorer with a weapon."
msgstr "嗯，我只是個帶著武器的探險者。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_16
msgid "Peace and perspective. Down there, it's noise and trade. Up here, I see everything more clearly."
msgstr "和平與遠見。那下面是喧囂與交易。站在這裡，我看得更清楚。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_16:0
msgid "Are you from..."
msgstr "你是來自...嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_welcome_16:1
msgid "I understand that."
msgstr "我明白。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_found_clues_10:0
msgid "I found this broken bell and a music box. [Show Vaelric.]"
msgstr "我找到這個破損的鐘和一個音樂盒。[展示給瓦爾里克看。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_found_clues_20
msgid "I see. Interesting, but not very helpful. Go explore the Galmore encampment east of the graveyard and report back to me when you find something helpful."
msgstr ""
"我明白了。有趣，但幫助不大。去東邊墓地的加爾摩營地探查，找到有用的線索後回報"
"我。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:vaelric_restless_grave_found_clue_10
msgid "Interesting, but not helpful. Go back and search for something useful. It makes sense if you search close by to where you found this other item. And don't keep running back to me every time you find something so mundane."
msgstr ""
"有趣，但沒幫助。回去找些有用的東西。如果你在發現這個物品附近搜尋會比較合理。"
"別每次找到這種平凡東西就跑來找我。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_47_graveyard_sh_completed
#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_47_graveyard_sh_not_completed
msgid "You notice that one of the graves looks to have been dug-up in the not-so-distant past."
msgstr "你注意到其中一座墳墓似乎在不久前被挖掘過。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_5
msgid "Clearly more agitated than usual, pacing and muttering."
msgstr "明顯比平常更焦躁，不停踱步並喃喃自語。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_40n
msgid "[Voice trembling but defensive.]"
msgstr "[聲音顫抖但防禦性強。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_40n2
msgid "Leta pauses, clutching her head as if in pain. Her voice shifting, darker and more guttural."
msgstr "莉塔停頓，緊捂著頭，彷彿痛苦難耐。她的聲音變得低沉沙啞。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_marked_stone_leta_40n2:0
msgid "Leta, talk to me. What's going on?"
msgstr "莉塔，跟我說說。發生什麼事了？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_47_graveyard_sh_reward_10
msgid "You wonder if Vaelric knows anything about this."
msgstr "你在想瓦爾里克是否知道些什麼。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_47_graveyard_sh_reward_15
msgid "But you really don't know what to think about it."
msgstr "但你真的不知道該怎麼看待這件事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_undertell_10:0
msgid "I'm looking for something called \"Undertell\", do you know where it is?"
msgstr "我在找一個叫做幽訴之境的東西，你知道在哪裡嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_undertell_10:1
msgid "I'm looking for my brother. His name is Andor and he looks a lot like me."
msgstr "我在找我的兄弟。他叫安多爾，長得很像我。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_undertell_20
msgid "With a terrified expression on his face, Myrelis slowly raises his arm and points you to the southwest."
msgstr "麥瑞利斯臉上帶著驚恐的表情，緩緩舉起手臂，指向西南方。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_undertell_30
msgid "Over there, but it looks like it's blocked."
msgstr "就在那邊，但看起來被阻擋了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_myrelis_andor
msgid "No, I'm sorry, but you are the first human that I've seen in...geez, I can't even remember how long."
msgstr "不，抱歉，你是我見過的第一個人類……天啊，我甚至不記得多久了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_60
msgid "You are to leave now. [pointing his finger towards the door.]"
msgstr "你現在必須離開。[用手指指向門口。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:stoutford_artist_palyer_killed_rubycrest_gow
msgid "There's sorrow in you...maybe even regret. Perhaps you're not the monster I feared. Very well. You may stay, but only because I sense \"warmth\" in your heart and we won't speak of the bird again."
msgstr ""
"你心中有悲傷……甚至可能有悔恨。或許你並非我所懼怕的怪物。好吧。你可以留下，但"
"僅因我感受到你心中的「溫暖」，我們不再提那隻鳥。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_15_bridge_fear
msgid "As you cross the bridge, it begins to sway side to side which instills an element of dread in you as you fear toppling over the railing into that water will most certainly pull you over the cliff's edge and down into the abyss."
msgstr ""
"當你穿過橋時，橋開始左右搖晃，讓你感到恐懼，害怕跌落欄杆進入水中，這肯定會將"
"你拉過懸崖邊緣，墜入深淵。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_77_stink
msgid "There's a really strong stink of a decomposing animal emanating out from under the trees."
msgstr "樹下散發出一股強烈的腐爛動物臭味。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_77_stink:0
msgid "I guess one of the many aroughcuns on this mountain will enjoy that later."
msgstr "我想這座山上的某個荒野人稍後會喜歡這個。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:galmore_77_stink:1
msgid "Oh, that is nasty. I need to escape this stink now."
msgstr "噁心死了，我得趕快逃離這股臭味。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_10
msgid "This gold will really help me rebuild my life. Now I just need to decide where to do that."
msgstr "這筆金子真的能幫我重建生活。現在我只需要決定在哪裡開始。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_10:0
msgid "May I suggest Feygard?"
msgstr "我建議去妖境如何？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_10:1
msgid "May I suggest Nor City?"
msgstr "我可以建議諾爾城嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_20
msgid "Feygard? Why would I ever want to live there?"
msgstr "妖境？我為什麼會想住那裡？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_20:0
msgid "Well, I've heard such wonderful things about that glorious city. There's so many opportunities for almost anyone."
msgstr "嗯，我聽過那座光輝城市的美好傳聞。幾乎人人都有無限機會。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_30
msgid "Feygard? I don't know, maybe. But thank you for your suggestion."
msgstr "妖境？我不清楚，也許吧。但謝謝你的建議。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_15
msgid "Nor City? Why would I ever want to live there?"
msgstr "諾爾城？我為什麼會想住那裡？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_15:0
msgid "I'm really not sure why except that I've met so many Shadow folk that rave about that place."
msgstr "我真的不太確定，只知道我遇過很多暗影族人都狂讚那個地方。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_already_given_gold_25
msgid "Nor City? I don't know, maybe. But thank you for your suggestion."
msgstr "諾爾城？我不確定，也許吧。但謝謝你的建議。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_10
msgid "That gold you're holding... it belonged to my family. Stolen from us not long ago, taken by hands no better than yours."
msgstr "你手上的那筆金子……是我家族的。不久前被偷走，落入和你一樣卑劣的手中。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_narrator_1
msgid "She takes a cautious step forward."
msgstr "她小心翼翼地向前踏出一步。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_20
msgid "You can do right and give it back. Or you can learn what happens to those who carry what's not theirs."
msgstr ""
"你可以做對的事，把它還回去。或者你可以學學那些帶著不屬於他們的東西會發生什麼"
"事。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_20:0
msgid "If it's truly yours, then take it. [Hand over the recently looted gold.]"
msgstr "如果真的是你的，那就拿去吧。[交出剛剛獲得的金幣。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_20:1
msgid "Oh, you mean that gold that now belongs to me? It's now mine."
msgstr "哦，你是說那筆現在屬於我的金子？現在是我的了。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_20:2
msgid "[Lie] Oh, you mean the 500 gold pieces that I found back there? [Pointing west.]"
msgstr "[說謊] 哦，你是說我剛才在那邊找到的500金幣嗎？[指向西方。]"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_fight
msgid "Egrinda lunges at you."
msgstr "埃格琳達向你撲來。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_fight:0
msgid "You will not survive this!"
msgstr "你活不過這一戰！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:egrinda_wants_gold_lier
msgid "Liar!"
msgstr "說謊者！"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_missing_ing_10
msgid "You don't have what I require in order to make them."
msgstr "你沒有我製作它們所需的材料。"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_missing_ing_10:0
msgid "I don't?"
msgstr "我沒有嗎？"

#: conversationlist_mt_galmore2.json:mg_vaelric_reward_missing_ing_20
msgid ""
"No, you don't. I already told you, if you wish for me to prepare this tonic, you must gather the necessary ingredients yourself. Here is what I require:\n"
"\n"
"Five Duskbloom flowers. These rare blossoms can be found in the deepest parts of the swamp, but the creatures there tend to be attracted to them. Their properties are delicate, so bring them fresh.\n"
"\n"
"Five Mosquito proboscises. Harvested from the swamp mosquitoes. You will find no shortage of these creatures near stagnant waters, but mind their bites.\n"
"\n"
"Ten bottles of swamp water. You will find plenty just outside my home. Surface water won't do. You'll need to reach deep, past the filth floating on top. The best stuff is settled at the bottom. Dark, thick, and rich with what gives the swamp its potency. Fill the bottles with that. Take these empty bottles and fill them yourself.\n"
"\n"
"One sample of Mudfiend goo. A secretion found in the depths of mines and tunnels along the Duleian Road. It is the key component that binds the other ingredients together."
msgstr ""
"不，你不需要。我已經告訴過你，如果你希望我調製這種藥劑，你必須自己收集所需的"
"材料。以下是我需要的：\n"
"\n"
"五朵暮花。這些稀有的花朵生長在沼澤最深處，但那裡的生物會被它們吸引。它們的特"
"性很脆弱，請帶來新鮮的。\n"
"\n"
"五根蚊子口器。從沼澤蚊子身上採集。你在停滯的水域附近會發現不少這種生物，但要"
"小心牠們的叮咬。\n"
"\n"
"十瓶沼澤水。你在我家外面就能找到很多。表層水不行，你需要深入，越過漂浮的污垢"
"。最好的水沉澱在底部。黑暗、濃稠，富含賦予沼澤力量的成分。用這些空瓶自己裝滿"
"。\n"
"\n"
"一份泥魔分泌物樣本。這種分泌物存在於杜雷安路沿線的礦坑和隧道深處。它是將其他"
"材料結合的關鍵成分。"

#: conversationlist_next_release.json:galmore_rg_musicbox_found_first
#: conversationlist_next_release.json:galmore_rg_bell_found_first
msgid "For some reason, you strongly suspect that this item is just the beginning."
msgstr "不知為何，你強烈懷疑這件物品只是個開始。"

#: conversationlist_next_release.json:galmore_rg_both_items_found
msgid "You begin to wonder why these items have been dropped."
msgstr "你開始懷疑為何這些物品會被丟棄。"

