#: itemlist_gison.json:gison_cookbook
msgid "Fabulous cookings"
msgstr "絕妙料理"

#: itemlist_gison.json:gison_cookbook:description
msgid ""
"Fabulous recipes gathered by the Bogsten family\n"
"\n"
"(1) Ed's pancakes\n"
"\n"
"7 oz wheat flour\n"
"1 packet of baking powder\n"
"2 oz powdered sugar\n"
"2 eggs\n"
"1 quart of milk\n"
"2 oz butter\n"
"\n"
"(2) Parmigiana alle Melanzane\n"
"\n"
"Tomato sauce\n"
"Basil, garlic\n"
"Extra virgin olive oil\n"
"Mozzarella, Parmesan aged\n"
"Eggplant\n"
"\n"
"(3) Mushroom soup\n"
"\n"
"Fresh Bogsten mushrooms\n"
"2 pints snake broth\n"
"3.5 fl oz cream\n"
"Herbs to taste\n"
"\n"
"(4) Onde-onde\n"
"\n"
"4 oz rice flour\n"
"2 oz tapioca flour\n"
"1.5 oz sugar\n"
"2.5 fl oz pandan leaf extract\n"
"1 piece palm sugar, chopped fine\n"
"Shredded coconut, dried\n"
"\n"
"(5) Rabbit stew\n"
"1 rabbit, cut into pieces\n"
"1 potato, cubed\n"
"1 turnip, cubed\n"
"2 carrots, sliced\n"
"2 parsnips, sliced\n"
" 5 oz Bogsten or portobello mushrooms\n"
"4 cloves garlic, crushed\n"
"4 fl oz wine\n"
"Water to cover\n"
"Salt\n"
"Pepper\n"
"1 tsp beef base\n"
"0.5 cup rosemary, finely chopped\n"
"0.5 cup thyme, finely chopped\n"
"Cook slowly, add starch at end to thicken\n"
""
msgstr ""
"博格斯頓家族珍藏食譜\n"
"\n"
"(1) 艾德的鬆餅\n"
"\n"
"7 盎司小麥粉\n"
"1 包泡打粉\n"
"2 盎司糖粉\n"
"2 顆蛋\n"
"1 夸脫牛奶\n"
"2 盎司奶油\n"
"\n"
"(2) 茄子帕爾瑪\n"
"\n"
"番茄醬\n"
"羅勒、大蒜\n"
"特級初榨橄欖油\n"
"莫札瑞拉、熟成帕瑪森起司\n"
"茄子\n"
"\n"
"(3) 蘑菇湯\n"
"\n"
"新鮮博格斯頓蘑菇\n"
"2 品脫蛇湯\n"
"3.5 液盎司鮮奶油\n"
"適量香草\n"
"\n"
"(4) 椰絲糯米球\n"
"\n"
"4 盎司米粉\n"
"2 盎司木薯粉\n"
"1.5 盎司糖\n"
"2.5 液盎司香蘭葉萃取液\n"
"1 塊棕櫚糖，切細\n"
"乾椰絲\n"
"\n"
"(5) 兔肉燉菜\n"
"1 隻兔子，切塊\n"
"1 顆馬鈴薯，切丁\n"
"1 顆蕪菁，切丁\n"
"2 根胡蘿蔔，切片\n"
"2 根歐防風，切片\n"
"5 盎司博格斯頓或波多貝羅蘑菇\n"
"4 瓣大蒜，壓碎\n"
"4 液盎司葡萄酒\n"
"水，淹過材料\n"
"鹽\n"
"胡椒\n"
"1 茶匙牛肉高湯粉\n"
"0.5 杯迷迭香，切細\n"
"0.5 杯百里香，切細\n"
"慢火燉煮，最後加入澱粉勾芡\n"

#: itemlist_gison.json:gison_cookbook_2
msgid "Fabulous cookings (copy)"
