msgid ""
"'Proud Striker: By Rhythm and Force' \n"
"\n"
"...'never swing with mere hope. The edge must be an extension of intention. Feel the weight in your stance, the rhythm in your breath. Let your eyes guide your hand, not your haste. If you strike before the moment is ready, you strike only air. When the gap reveals itself, do not hesitate. Commit, and follow through...'"
